(((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1)) - (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p))) + 1 : ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1))) + 1)])) | (tag_hit2x4 & sbuf_entry_in[(data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1)-:(((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1)) >= (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) ? (((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1)) - (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p))) + 1 : ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1))) + 1)]);
	bsg_mux_segmented #(
		._sv2v_width_segments_p(_sv2v_width_data_width_p),
		.segments_p(data_width_p >> 3),
		._sv2v_width_segment_width_p(32),
		.segment_width_p(8)
	) mux_segmented_merge0(
		.data0_i(el1[data_width_p + ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1))-:((data_width_p + ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1))) >= ((data_width_p >> 3) + (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p))) ? ((data_width_p + ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1))) - ((data_width_p >> 3) + (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)))) + 1 : (((data_width_p >> 3) + (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p))) - (data_width_p + ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1)))) + 1)]),
		.data1_i(el0[data_width_p + ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1))-:((data_width_p + ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1))) >= ((data_width_p >> 3) + (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p))) ? ((data_width_p + ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1))) - ((data_width_p >> 3) + (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)))) + 1 : (((data_width_p >> 3) + (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p))) - (data_width_p + ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1)))) + 1)]),
		.sel_i(tag_hit0x4 & el0[(data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1)-:(((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1)) >= (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) ? (((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1)) - (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p))) + 1 : ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1))) + 1)]),
		.data_o(el0or1_data)
	);
	bsg_mux_segmented #(
		._sv2v_width_segments_p(_sv2v_width_data_width_p),
		.segments_p(data_width_p >> 3),
		._sv2v_width_segment_width_p(32),
		.segment_width_p(8)
	) mux_segmented_merge1(
		.data0_i(el0or1_data),
		.data1_i(sbuf_entry_in[data_width_p + ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1))-:((data_width_p + ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1))) >= ((data_width_p >> 3) + (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p))) ? ((data_width_p + ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1))) - ((data_width_p >> 3) + (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)))) + 1 : (((data_width_p >> 3) + (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p))) - (data_width_p + ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1)))) + 1)]),
		.sel_i(tag_hit2x4 & sbuf_entry_in[(data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1)-:(((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1)) >= (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) ? (((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1)) - (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p))) + 1 : ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - ((data_width_p >> 3) + ((ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p)) - 1))) + 1)]),
		.data_o(bypass_data_n)
	);
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i) begin
			bypass_mask_o <= {data_mask_width_lp {1'sb0}};
			bypass_data_o <= {data_width_p {1'sb0}};
		end
		else if (bypass_v_i) begin
			bypass_mask_o <= bypass_mask_n;
			bypass_data_o <= bypass_data_n;
		end
	always @(negedge clk_i)
		if (~reset_i & (num_els_r !== 2'bxx))
			;
endmodule
module bsg_cache_sbuf_queue (
	clk_i,
	data_i,
	el0_en_i,
	el1_en_i,
	mux0_sel_i,
	mux1_sel_i,
	el0_snoop_o,
	el1_snoop_o,
	data_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	input clk_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input el0_en_i;
	input el1_en_i;
	input mux0_sel_i;
	input mux1_sel_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] el0_snoop_o;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] el1_snoop_o;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	reg [width_p - 1:0] el0_r;
	reg [width_p - 1:0] el1_r;
	always @(posedge clk_i) begin
		if (el0_en_i)
			el0_r <= data_i;
		if (el1_en_i)
			el1_r <= (mux0_sel_i ? el0_r : data_i);
	end
	assign data_o = (mux1_sel_i ? el1_r : data_i);
	assign el0_snoop_o = el0_r;
	assign el1_snoop_o = el1_r;
endmodule
module bsg_channel_tunnel (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	multi_data_i,
	multi_v_i,
	multi_yumi_o,
	multi_data_o,
	multi_v_o,
	multi_yumi_i,
	data_i,
	v_i,
	yumi_o,
	data_o,
	v_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter width_p = 1;
	parameter _sv2v_width_num_in_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_num_in_p - 1:0] num_in_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_remote_credits_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_remote_credits_p - 1:0] remote_credits_p = "inv";
	parameter use_pseudo_large_fifo_p = 0;
	parameter lg_remote_credits_lp = $clog2(remote_credits_p + 1);
	parameter lg_credit_decimation_p = (lg_remote_credits_lp < 4 ? lg_remote_credits_lp : 4);
	parameter tag_width_lp = $clog2(num_in_p + 1);
	parameter tagged_width_lp = tag_width_lp + width_p;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [tagged_width_lp - 1:0] multi_data_i;
	input multi_v_i;
	output multi_yumi_o;
	output [tagged_width_lp - 1:0] multi_data_o;
	output multi_v_o;
	input multi_yumi_i;
	input [(num_in_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_i;
	input [num_in_p - 1:0] v_i;
	output [num_in_p - 1:0] yumi_o;
	output [(num_in_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_o;
	output [num_in_p - 1:0] v_o;
	input [num_in_p - 1:0] yumi_i;
	wire [(num_in_p * lg_remote_credits_lp) - 1:0] credit_local_return_data_oi;
	wire credit_local_return_v_oi;
	wire [(num_in_p * lg_remote_credits_lp) - 1:0] credit_remote_return_data_oi;
	wire credit_remote_return_yumi_io;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	wire multi_v_o;
	wire multi_yumi_i;
	bsg_channel_tunnel_out #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		._sv2v_width_num_in_p(_sv2v_width_num_in_p),
		.num_in_p(num_in_p),
		._sv2v_width_remote_credits_p(_sv2v_width_remote_credits_p),
		.remote_credits_p(remote_credits_p),
		.lg_credit_decimation_p(lg_credit_decimation_p)
	) bcto(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i(data_i),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.yumi_o(yumi_o),
		.data_o(multi_data_o),
		.v_o(multi_v_o),
		.yumi_i(multi_yumi_i),
		.credit_local_return_data_i(credit_local_return_data_oi),
		.credit_local_return_v_i(credit_local_return_v_oi),
		.credit_remote_return_data_i(credit_remote_return_data_oi),
		.credit_remote_return_yumi_o(credit_remote_return_yumi_io)
	);
	wire multi_v_i;
	wire multi_yumi_o;
	bsg_channel_tunnel_in #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		._sv2v_width_num_in_p(_sv2v_width_num_in_p),
		.num_in_p(num_in_p),
		._sv2v_width_remote_credits_p(_sv2v_width_remote_credits_p),
		.remote_credits_p(remote_credits_p),
		.use_pseudo_large_fifo_p(use_pseudo_large_fifo_p),
		.lg_credit_decimation_p(lg_credit_decimation_p)
	) bcti(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i(multi_data_i),
		.v_i(multi_v_i),
		.yumi_o(multi_yumi_o),
		.data_o(data_o),
		.v_o(v_o),
		.yumi_i(yumi_i),
		.credit_local_return_data_o(credit_local_return_data_oi),
		.credit_local_return_v_o(credit_local_return_v_oi),
		.credit_remote_return_data_o(credit_remote_return_data_oi),
		.credit_remote_return_yumi_i(credit_remote_return_yumi_io)
	);
endmodule
module bsg_channel_tunnel_in (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	data_i,
	v_i,
	yumi_o,
	data_o,
	v_o,
	yumi_i,
	credit_local_return_data_o,
	credit_local_return_v_o,
	credit_remote_return_data_o,
	credit_remote_return_yumi_i
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter _sv2v_width_num_in_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_num_in_p - 1:0] num_in_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_remote_credits_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_remote_credits_p - 1:0] remote_credits_p = "inv";
	parameter use_pseudo_large_fifo_p = 0;
	parameter lg_credit_decimation_p = 4;
	parameter tag_width_lp = $clog2(num_in_p + 1);
	parameter tagged_width_lp = tag_width_lp + width_p;
	parameter lg_remote_credits_lp = $clog2(remote_credits_p + 1);
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [tagged_width_lp - 1:0] data_i;
	input v_i;
	output yumi_o;
	output [(num_in_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_o;
	output [num_in_p - 1:0] v_o;
	input [num_in_p - 1:0] yumi_i;
	output [(num_in_p * lg_remote_credits_lp) - 1:0] credit_local_return_data_o;
	output credit_local_return_v_o;
	output [(num_in_p * lg_remote_credits_lp) - 1:0] credit_remote_return_data_o;
	input credit_remote_return_yumi_i;
	wire credit_v_lo;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] credit_data_lo;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	wire v_i;
	wire yumi_o;
	bsg_1_to_n_tagged_fifo #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(width_p),
		.num_out_p(num_in_p + 1),
		._sv2v_width_els_p(_sv2v_width_remote_credits_p),
		.els_p(remote_credits_p),
		.unbuffered_mask_p(1 << num_in_p),
		.use_pseudo_large_fifo_p(use_pseudo_large_fifo_p)
	) b1_ntf(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.tag_i(data_i[width_p+:tag_width_lp]),
		.data_i(data_i[0+:width_p]),
		.yumi_o(yumi_o),
		.v_o({credit_v_lo, v_o}),
		.data_o({credit_data_lo, data_o}),
		.yumi_i({1'b0, yumi_i})
	);
	assign credit_local_return_data_o = credit_data_lo[0+:num_in_p * lg_remote_credits_lp];
	wire credit_local_return_v_o;
	assign credit_local_return_v_o = credit_v_lo;
	wire [num_in_p - 1:0] sent = v_o & yumi_i;
	genvar i;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < num_in_p; i = i + 1) begin : rof
			wire credit_remote_return_yumi_i;
			bsg_counter_clear_up #(
				.max_val_p(remote_credits_p),
				.init_val_p(0)
			) ctr(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.clear_i(credit_remote_return_yumi_i),
				.up_i(sent[i]),
				.count_o(credit_remote_return_data_o[i * lg_remote_credits_lp+:lg_remote_credits_lp])
			);
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_channel_tunnel_out (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	data_i,
	v_i,
	yumi_o,
	data_o,
	v_o,
	yumi_i,
	credit_local_return_data_i,
	credit_local_return_v_i,
	credit_remote_return_data_i,
	credit_remote_return_yumi_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter _sv2v_width_num_in_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_num_in_p - 1:0] num_in_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_remote_credits_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_remote_credits_p - 1:0] remote_credits_p = "inv";
	parameter lg_credit_decimation_p = 4;
	parameter tag_width_lp = $clog2(num_in_p + 1);
	parameter tagged_width_lp = tag_width_lp + width_p;
	parameter lg_remote_credits_lp = $clog2(remote_credits_p + 1);
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [(num_in_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_i;
	input [num_in_p - 1:0] v_i;
	output [num_in_p - 1:0] yumi_o;
	output [tagged_width_lp - 1:0] data_o;
	output v_o;
	input yumi_i;
	input [(num_in_p * lg_remote_credits_lp) - 1:0] credit_local_return_data_i;
	input credit_local_return_v_i;
	input [(num_in_p * lg_remote_credits_lp) - 1:0] credit_remote_return_data_i;
	output credit_remote_return_yumi_o;
	genvar i;
	wire [(num_in_p * lg_remote_credits_lp) - 1:0] local_credits;
	wire [num_in_p - 1:0] local_credits_avail;
	wire [num_in_p - 1:0] remote_credits_avail;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < num_in_p; i = i + 1) begin : rof
			function automatic [lg_remote_credits_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_7A0A6;
				input reg [lg_remote_credits_lp - 1:0] inp;
				sv2v_cast_7A0A6 = inp;
			endfunction
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			bsg_counter_up_down_variable #(
				.max_val_p(remote_credits_p),
				.init_val_p(remote_credits_p),
				.max_step_p(remote_credits_p)
			) bcudv(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.up_i((credit_local_return_v_i ? credit_local_return_data_i[i * lg_remote_credits_lp+:lg_remote_credits_lp] : sv2v_cast_7A0A6(0))),
				.down_i(sv2v_cast_7A0A6(yumi_o[i])),
				.count_o(local_credits[i * lg_remote_credits_lp+:lg_remote_credits_lp])
			);
			assign local_credits_avail[i] = |local_credits[i * lg_remote_credits_lp+:lg_remote_credits_lp];
			assign remote_credits_avail[i] = |credit_remote_return_data_i[(i * lg_remote_credits_lp) + ((lg_remote_credits_lp - 1) >= lg_credit_decimation_p ? lg_remote_credits_lp - 1 : ((lg_remote_credits_lp - 1) + ((lg_remote_credits_lp - 1) >= lg_credit_decimation_p ? ((lg_remote_credits_lp - 1) - lg_credit_decimation_p) + 1 : (lg_credit_decimation_p - (lg_remote_credits_lp - 1)) + 1)) - 1)-:((lg_remote_credits_lp - 1) >= lg_credit_decimation_p ? ((lg_remote_credits_lp - 1) - lg_credit_decimation_p) + 1 : (lg_credit_decimation_p - (lg_remote_credits_lp - 1)) + 1)];
		end
	endgenerate
	wire credit_v_li = |remote_credits_avail;
	function automatic [width_p - 1:0] sv2v_cast_89401;
		input reg [width_p - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_89401 = inp;
	endfunction
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	wire v_o;
	wire yumi_i;
	bsg_round_robin_n_to_1 #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.num_in_p(num_in_p + 1),
		._sv2v_width_strict_p(32),
		.strict_p(0)
	) rr(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i({sv2v_cast_89401(credit_remote_return_data_i), data_i}),
		.v_i({credit_v_li, v_i & local_credits_avail}),
		.yumi_o({credit_remote_return_yumi_o, yumi_o}),
		.data_o(data_o[0+:width_p]),
		.tag_o(data_o[width_p+:tag_width_lp]),
		.v_o(v_o),
		.yumi_i(yumi_i)
	);
endmodule
module bsg_1_to_n_tagged_fifo (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	v_i,
	tag_i,
	data_i,
	yumi_o,
	v_o,
	yumi_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter num_out_p = -1;
	parameter _sv2v_width_els_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_els_p - 1:0] els_p = "inv";
	parameter unbuffered_mask_p = 0;
	parameter use_pseudo_large_fifo_p = 0;
	parameter tag_width_lp = (num_out_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(num_out_p));
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input v_i;
	input [tag_width_lp - 1:0] tag_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	output yumi_o;
	output [num_out_p - 1:0] v_o;
	input [num_out_p - 1:0] yumi_i;
	output [(num_out_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_o;
	wire [num_out_p - 1:0] valid_lo;
	wire [num_out_p - 1:0] ready_li;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	wire v_i;
	wire yumi_o;
	bsg_1_to_n_tagged #(.num_out_p(num_out_p)) _1_to_n(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.tag_i(tag_i),
		.yumi_o(yumi_o),
		.v_o(valid_lo),
		.ready_i(ready_li)
	);
	genvar i;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < num_out_p; i = i + 1) begin : rof
			if (unbuffered_mask_p[i]) begin : unbuf
				assign v_o[i] = valid_lo[i];
				assign data_o[i * width_p+:width_p] = data_i;
				assign ready_li[i] = 1'b1;
			end
			else if (use_pseudo_large_fifo_p) begin : psdlrg
				bsg_fifo_1r1w_pseudo_large #(
					.width_p(width_p),
					.els_p(els_p)
				) fifo(
					.clk_i(clk_i),
					.reset_i(reset_i),
					.v_i(valid_lo[i]),
					.data_i(data_i),
					.ready_o(ready_li[i]),
					.v_o(v_o[i]),
					.data_o(data_o[i * width_p+:width_p]),
					.yumi_i(yumi_i[i])
				);
			end
			else begin : buff
				bsg_fifo_1r1w_small #(
					.width_p(width_p),
					.els_p(els_p)
				) fifo(
					.clk_i(clk_i),
					.reset_i(reset_i),
					.v_i(valid_lo[i]),
					.data_i(data_i),
					.ready_o(ready_li[i]),
					.v_o(v_o[i]),
					.data_o(data_o[i * width_p+:width_p]),
					.yumi_i(yumi_i[i])
				);
			end
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_1_to_n_tagged (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	v_i,
	tag_i,
	yumi_o,
	v_o,
	ready_i
);
	parameter num_out_p = -1;
	parameter tag_width_lp = (num_out_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(num_out_p));
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input v_i;
	input [tag_width_lp - 1:0] tag_i;
	output yumi_o;
	output [num_out_p - 1:0] v_o;
	input [num_out_p - 1:0] ready_i;
	wire unused0 = clk_i;
	wire unused1 = reset_i;
	generate
		if (num_out_p == 1) begin : one
			assign v_o = v_i;
			wire yumi_o;
			assign yumi_o = ready_i & v_i;
		end
		else begin : many
			genvar i;
			wire v_i;
			bsg_decode_with_v #(.num_out_p(num_out_p)) bdv(
				.i(tag_i),
				.v_i(v_i),
				.o(v_o)
			);
			wire yumi_o;
			assign yumi_o = ready_i[tag_i] & v_i;
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_fifo_1r1w_large (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	data_i,
	v_i,
	ready_o,
	v_o,
	data_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input v_i;
	output ready_o;
	output v_o;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	input yumi_i;
	wire [(width_p * 2) - 1:0] data_sipo;
	wire [1:0] valid_sipo;
	wire [1:0] yumi_cnt_sipo;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	wire v_i;
	wire ready_o;
	bsg_serial_in_parallel_out #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.els_p(3),
		.out_els_p(2)
	) sipo(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.valid_i(v_i),
		.data_i(data_i),
		.ready_o(ready_o),
		.valid_o(valid_sipo),
		.data_o(data_sipo),
		.yumi_cnt_i(yumi_cnt_sipo)
	);
	wire [(2 * width_p) - 1:0] big_data_lo;
	wire big_valid;
	wire big_full_lo;
	wire big_empty_lo;
	wire big_enq;
	wire big_deq;
	reg big_deq_r;
	always @(posedge clk_i) big_deq_r <= big_deq;
	bsg_fifo_1rw_large #(
		.width_p(width_p * 2),
		.els_p(els_p >> 1)
	) big1p(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i(data_sipo),
		.v_i(big_valid),
		.enq_not_deq_i(big_enq),
		.full_o(big_full_lo),
		.empty_o(big_empty_lo),
		.data_o(big_data_lo)
	);
	wire [(2 * width_p) - 1:0] little_data_rot;
	wire [1:0] little_valid;
	wire [1:0] little_ready;
	wire [1:0] little_ready_rot;
	wire [1:0] little_valid_rot;
	wire [1:0] valid_int;
	wire bypass_mode = (~big_deq_r & little_ready[0]) & big_empty_lo;
	wire can_spill = ~big_full_lo & ~bypass_mode;
	wire emergency = (&little_ready_rot & ~big_empty_lo) & ~big_deq_r;
	wire will_spill = (can_spill & &valid_sipo) & ~emergency;
	assign big_deq = (~will_spill & ~big_empty_lo) & (big_deq_r ? ~|valid_int : &little_ready_rot);
	assign big_valid = will_spill | big_deq;
	assign big_enq = will_spill;
	wire [(2 * width_p) - 1:0] little_data = (big_deq_r ? big_data_lo : data_sipo);
	wire [1:0] bypass_vector = valid_sipo & {bypass_mode, bypass_mode};
	assign little_valid = (big_deq_r ? 2'b11 : bypass_vector);
	wire [1:0] cnt;
	bsg_thermometer_count #(.width_p(2)) thermo(
		.i(little_ready & bypass_vector),
		.o(cnt)
	);
	assign yumi_cnt_sipo = (will_spill ? 2'b10 : cnt);
	bsg_round_robin_2_to_2 #(.width_p(width_p)) rr222(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i(little_data),
		.v_i(little_valid),
		.ready_o(little_ready),
		.data_o(little_data_rot),
		.v_o(little_valid_rot),
		.ready_i(little_ready_rot)
	);
	wire [(2 * width_p) - 1:0] data_int;
	wire [1:0] yumi_int;
	genvar i;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < 2; i = i + 1) begin : twofer
			bsg_two_fifo #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
				.width_p(width_p)
			) little(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.ready_o(little_ready_rot[i]),
				.data_i(little_data_rot[i * width_p+:width_p]),
				.v_i(little_valid_rot[i]),
				.v_o(valid_int[i]),
				.data_o(data_int[i * width_p+:width_p]),
				.yumi_i(yumi_int[i])
			);
		end
	endgenerate
	wire v_o;
	wire yumi_i;
	bsg_round_robin_n_to_1 #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.num_in_p(2),
		._sv2v_width_strict_p(32),
		.strict_p(1)
	) round_robin_n_to_1(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i(data_int),
		.v_i(valid_int),
		.yumi_o(yumi_int),
		.data_o(data_o),
		.v_o(v_o),
		.tag_o(),
		.yumi_i(yumi_i)
	);
	wire [31:0] num_elements_debug = ((((((2 * big1p.num_elements_debug) + valid_int[0]) + valid_int[1]) + sipo.valid_r[0]) + sipo.valid_r[1]) + !little_ready_rot[0]) + !little_ready_rot[1];
endmodule
module bsg_fifo_1r1w_pseudo_large (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	data_i,
	v_i,
	ready_o,
	v_o,
	data_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter early_yumi_p = 1;
	parameter verbose_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input v_i;
	output ready_o;
	output v_o;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	input yumi_i;
	wire big_full_lo;
	wire big_empty_lo;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] big_data_lo;
	reg big_enq;
	reg big_deq;
	reg big_deq_r;
	wire little_ready_lo;
	wire little_will_have_space;
	reg little_valid;
	reg big_valid;
	generate
		if (early_yumi_p) assign little_will_have_space = little_ready_lo | yumi_i;
		else assign little_will_have_space = little_ready_lo;
	endgenerate
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i)
			big_deq_r <= 1'b0;
		else
			big_deq_r <= big_deq;
	wire ready_o_int = ~big_full_lo;
	wire ready_o;
	assign ready_o = ready_o_int;
	wire bypass_mode = v_i & ~big_enq;
	wire [31:0] num_elements_debug = (big1p.num_elements_debug + big_deq_r) + little2p.num_elements_debug;
	reg big_enq_r;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i)
			big_enq_r <= 0;
		else
			big_enq_r <= big_enq_r | big_enq;
	always @(negedge clk_i)
		if ((verbose_p & (reset_i === 0)) & (~big_enq_r & big_enq))
			$display("## %L: overflowing into big fifo for the first time (%m)");
	always @(*) begin
		if (big_deq_r) begin
			little_valid = 1'b1;
			big_enq = v_i;
			big_deq = (~big_empty_lo & ~big_enq) & ~v_o;
		end
		else if (big_empty_lo) begin
			little_valid = v_i & little_will_have_space;
			big_enq = v_i & ~little_will_have_space;
			big_deq = 1'b0;
		end
		else begin
			little_valid = 1'b0;
			big_enq = v_i & ~big_full_lo;
			big_deq = ~big_enq & little_will_have_space;
		end
		big_valid = big_enq | big_deq;
	end
	wire [width_p - 1:0] little_data = (big_deq_r ? big_data_lo : data_i);
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	bsg_fifo_1rw_large #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.els_p(els_p),
		.verbose_p(verbose_p)
	) big1p(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i(data_i),
		.v_i(big_valid),
		.enq_not_deq_i(big_enq),
		.full_o(big_full_lo),
		.empty_o(big_empty_lo),
		.data_o(big_data_lo)
	);
	wire v_o;
	wire yumi_i;
	bsg_two_fifo #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(width_p),
		.verbose_p(verbose_p),
		.allow_enq_deq_on_full_p(early_yumi_p)
	) little2p(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.ready_o(little_ready_lo),
		.data_i(little_data),
		.v_i(little_valid),
		.v_o(v_o),
		.data_o(data_o),
		.yumi_i(yumi_i)
	);
endmodule
module bsg_fifo_1r1w_small (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	v_i,
	ready_o,
	data_i,
	v_o,
	data_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter harden_p = 0;
	parameter ready_THEN_valid_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input v_i;
	output ready_o;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	output v_o;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	input yumi_i;
	generate
		if (harden_p == 0) begin : unhardened
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			wire v_i;
			wire ready_o;
			wire v_o;
			wire yumi_i;
			bsg_fifo_1r1w_small_unhardened #(
				.width_p(width_p),
				.els_p(els_p),
				.ready_THEN_valid_p(ready_THEN_valid_p)
			) fifo(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.v_i(v_i),
				.ready_o(ready_o),
				.data_i(data_i),
				.v_o(v_o),
				.data_o(data_o),
				.yumi_i(yumi_i)
			);
		end
		else begin : hardened
			bsg_fifo_1r1w_small_hardened #(
				.width_p(width_p),
				.els_p(els_p),
				.ready_THEN_valid_p(ready_THEN_valid_p)
			) fifo(.*);
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_fifo_1r1w_small_unhardened (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	v_i,
	ready_o,
	data_i,
	v_o,
	data_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter ready_THEN_valid_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input v_i;
	output ready_o;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	output v_o;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	input yumi_i;
	wire deque = yumi_i;
	wire v_o_tmp;
	wire v_o;
	assign v_o = v_o_tmp;
	wire enque;
	wire ready_lo;
	generate
		if (ready_THEN_valid_p) begin : rtv
			assign enque = v_i;
		end
		else begin : rav
			assign enque = v_i & ready_lo;
		end
	endgenerate
	localparam ptr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	wire [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] rptr_r;
	wire [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] wptr_r;
	wire full;
	wire empty;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	bsg_fifo_tracker #(.els_p(els_p)) ft(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.enq_i(enque),
		.deq_i(deque),
		.wptr_r_o(wptr_r),
		.rptr_r_o(rptr_r),
		.rptr_n_o(),
		.full_o(full),
		.empty_o(empty)
	);
	bsg_mem_1r1w #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.els_p(els_p),
		.read_write_same_addr_p(0)
	) mem_1r1w(
		.w_clk_i(clk_i),
		.w_reset_i(reset_i),
		.w_v_i(enque),
		.w_addr_i(wptr_r),
		.w_data_i(data_i),
		.r_v_i(v_o_tmp),
		.r_addr_i(rptr_r),
		.r_data_o(data_o)
	);
	assign ready_lo = ~full;
	wire ready_o;
	assign ready_o = ready_lo;
	assign v_o_tmp = ~empty;
	always @(negedge clk_i) begin
		if (((ready_THEN_valid_p & full) & v_i) & ~reset_i)
			$display("%m error: enque full fifo at time %t", $time);
		if ((empty & yumi_i) & ~reset_i)
			$display("%m error: deque empty fifo at time %t", $time);
	end
endmodule
module bsg_fifo_1rw_large (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	data_i,
	v_i,
	enq_not_deq_i,
	full_o,
	empty_o,
	data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter verbose_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input v_i;
	input enq_not_deq_i;
	output full_o;
	output empty_o;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	localparam ptr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	wire [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] rd_ptr;
	wire [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] wr_ptr;
	reg last_op_is_read_r;
	wire mem_we = enq_not_deq_i & v_i;
	wire mem_re = ~enq_not_deq_i & v_i;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i)
			last_op_is_read_r <= 1;
		else if (v_i)
			last_op_is_read_r <= mem_re;
	wire fifo_empty = (rd_ptr == wr_ptr) & last_op_is_read_r;
	wire fifo_full = (rd_ptr == wr_ptr) & ~last_op_is_read_r;
	wire full_o;
	assign full_o = fifo_full;
	wire empty_o;
	assign empty_o = fifo_empty;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (verbose_p)
			if (v_i)
				if (enq_not_deq_i)
					$display("### %m enq %x onto fifo (r=%x w=%x)", data_i, rd_ptr, wr_ptr);
				else
					$display("### %m deq fifo (r=%x w=%x)", rd_ptr, wr_ptr);
	wire [31:0] num_elements_debug = (fifo_empty ? 0 : (fifo_full ? els_p : (wr_ptr > rd_ptr ? wr_ptr - rd_ptr : els_p - (rd_ptr - wr_ptr))));
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	bsg_circular_ptr #(
		.slots_p(els_p),
		.max_add_p(1)
	) rd_circ_ptr(
		.clk(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.add_i(mem_re),
		.o(rd_ptr),
		.n_o()
	);
	bsg_circular_ptr #(
		.slots_p(els_p),
		.max_add_p(1)
	) wr_circ_ptr(
		.clk(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.add_i(mem_we),
		.o(wr_ptr),
		.n_o()
	);
	wire v_i;
	bsg_mem_1rw_sync #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.els_p(els_p)
	) mem_1srw(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i(data_i),
		.addr_i((mem_we ? wr_ptr : rd_ptr)),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.w_i(mem_we),
		.data_o(data_o)
	);
endmodule
module bsg_fifo_tracker (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	enq_i,
	deq_i,
	wptr_r_o,
	rptr_r_o,
	rptr_n_o,
	full_o,
	empty_o
);
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter ptr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input enq_i;
	input deq_i;
	output [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] wptr_r_o;
	output [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] rptr_r_o;
	output [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] rptr_n_o;
	output full_o;
	output empty_o;
	wire [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] rptr_r;
	wire [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] rptr_n;
	wire [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] wptr_r;
	assign wptr_r_o = wptr_r;
	assign rptr_r_o = rptr_r;
	assign rptr_n_o = rptr_n;
	reg enq_r;
	reg deq_r;
	wire empty;
	wire full;
	wire equal_ptrs;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	wire deq_i;
	bsg_circular_ptr #(
		.slots_p(els_p),
		.max_add_p(1)
	) rptr(
		.clk(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.add_i(deq_i),
		.o(rptr_r),
		.n_o(rptr_n)
	);
	wire enq_i;
	bsg_circular_ptr #(
		.slots_p(els_p),
		.max_add_p(1)
	) wptr(
		.clk(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.add_i(enq_i),
		.o(wptr_r),
		.n_o()
	);
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i) begin
			enq_r <= 1'b0;
			deq_r <= 1'b1;
		end
		else if (enq_i | deq_i) begin
			enq_r <= enq_i;
			deq_r <= deq_i;
		end
	assign equal_ptrs = rptr_r == wptr_r;
	assign empty = equal_ptrs & deq_r;
	assign full = equal_ptrs & enq_r;
	wire full_o;
	assign full_o = full;
	wire empty_o;
	assign empty_o = empty;
endmodule
module bsg_flow_counter (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	v_i,
	ready_i,
	yumi_i,
	count_o
);
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter count_free_p = 0;
	parameter ready_THEN_valid_p = 0;
	parameter ptr_width_lp = $clog2(els_p + 1);
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input v_i;
	input ready_i;
	input yumi_i;
	output [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] count_o;
	wire enque;
	generate
		if (ready_THEN_valid_p) begin : gen_blk_protocol_select
			assign enque = v_i;
		end
		else begin : gen_blk_protocol_select
			assign enque = v_i & ready_i;
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		if (count_free_p) begin : gen_blk_0
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			wire yumi_i;
			bsg_counter_up_down #(
				.max_val_p(els_p),
				.init_val_p(els_p),
				.max_step_p(1)
			) counter(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.up_i(yumi_i),
				.down_i(enque),
				.count_o(count_o)
			);
		end
		else begin : gen_blk_0
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			wire yumi_i;
			bsg_counter_up_down #(
				.max_val_p(els_p),
				.init_val_p(0),
				.max_step_p(1)
			) counter(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.up_i(enque),
				.down_i(yumi_i),
				.count_o(count_o)
			);
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_one_fifo (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	ready_o,
	data_i,
	v_i,
	v_o,
	data_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	output ready_o;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input v_i;
	output v_o;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	input yumi_i;
	wire full_r;
	wire ready_o;
	assign ready_o = ~full_r;
	wire v_o;
	assign v_o = full_r;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	bsg_dff_reset #(.width_p(1)) dff_full(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i((full_r ? ~yumi_i : v_i)),
		.data_o(full_r)
	);
	bsg_dff_en #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
		.width_p(width_p),
		.harden_p(0)
	) dff(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.data_i(data_i),
		.en_i(v_i & ready_o),
		.data_o(data_o)
	);
endmodule
module bsg_parallel_in_serial_out (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	valid_i,
	data_i,
	ready_o,
	valid_o,
	data_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter hi_to_lo_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input valid_i;
	input [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_i;
	output ready_o;
	output valid_o;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	input yumi_i;
	localparam [0:0] eRX = 0;
	localparam [0:0] eTX = 1;
	generate
		if (els_p == 1) begin : fifo
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			wire ready_o;
			wire valid_i;
			wire valid_o;
			wire yumi_i;
			bsg_two_fifo #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
				.width_p(width_p)
			) two_fifo(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.ready_o(ready_o),
				.data_i(data_i),
				.v_i(valid_i),
				.v_o(valid_o),
				.data_o(data_o),
				.yumi_i(yumi_i)
			);
		end
		else begin : piso
			localparam clog2els_lp = $clog2(els_p);
			reg [0:0] state_r;
			reg [0:0] state_n;
			reg [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_r;
			reg [clog2els_lp - 1:0] shift_ctr_r;
			wire [clog2els_lp - 1:0] shift_ctr_n;
			wire done_tx_n;
			function automatic [clog2els_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_59467;
				input reg [clog2els_lp - 1:0] inp;
				sv2v_cast_59467 = inp;
			endfunction
			assign done_tx_n = ((state_r == eTX) && (shift_ctr_r == sv2v_cast_59467(els_p - 1))) && yumi_i;
			wire ready_o;
			assign ready_o = (state_r == eRX) || done_tx_n;
			always @(posedge clk_i)
				if (reset_i)
					state_r <= eRX;
				else
					state_r <= state_n;
			always @(*)
				if (ready_o & valid_i)
					state_n = eTX;
				else if (done_tx_n)
					state_n = eRX;
				else
					state_n = state_r;
			wire [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_li;
			if (hi_to_lo_p == 0) begin : lo2hi
				assign data_li = data_i;
			end
			else begin : hi2lo
				bsg_array_reverse #(
					.width_p(width_p),
					.els_p(els_p)
				) bar(
					.i(data_i),
					.o(data_li)
				);
			end
			always @(posedge clk_i)
				if (reset_i)
					data_r <= {els_p * width_p {1'sb0}};
				else if (ready_o & valid_i)
					data_r <= data_li;
			always @(posedge clk_i)
				if (reset_i)
					shift_ctr_r <= {clog2els_lp {1'sb0}};
				else if (ready_o & valid_i)
					shift_ctr_r <= {clog2els_lp {1'sb0}};
				else
					shift_ctr_r <= shift_ctr_n;
			assign shift_ctr_n = (((state_r == eTX) && yumi_i) && ~done_tx_n ? shift_ctr_r + 1'b1 : shift_ctr_r);
			wire valid_o;
			assign valid_o = state_r == eTX;
			assign data_o = data_r[shift_ctr_r * width_p+:width_p];
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_parallel_in_serial_out_dynamic (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	v_i,
	len_i,
	data_i,
	ready_o,
	v_o,
	len_v_o,
	data_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_max_els_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_max_els_p - 1:0] max_els_p = "inv";
	parameter lg_max_els_lp = (max_els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(max_els_p));
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input v_i;
	input [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] len_i;
	input [(max_els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_i;
	output ready_o;
	output v_o;
	output len_v_o;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	input yumi_i;
	wire go_fifo_yumi_li;
	wire [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] len_lo;
	wire [(max_els_p * width_p) - 1:0] fifo_data_lo;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	wire ready_o;
	wire v_i;
	wire v_o;
	bsg_two_fifo #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(lg_max_els_lp)
	) go_fifo(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.ready_o(ready_o),
		.data_i(len_i),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.v_o(v_o),
		.data_o(len_lo),
		.yumi_i(go_fifo_yumi_li)
	);
	bsg_two_fifo #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p((_sv2v_width_max_els_p >= _sv2v_width_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_els_p : _sv2v_width_width_p)),
		.width_p(max_els_p * width_p)
	) data_fifo(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.ready_o(),
		.data_i(data_i),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.v_o(),
		.data_o(fifo_data_lo),
		.yumi_i(go_fifo_yumi_li)
	);
	wire [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] count_r;
	wire [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] count_lo;
	wire clear_li;
	wire up_li;
	wire count_r_is_zero;
	wire count_r_is_last;
	assign count_lo = count_r;
	function automatic [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_C8F51;
		input reg [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_C8F51 = inp;
	endfunction
	assign count_r_is_zero = count_lo == sv2v_cast_C8F51(0);
	assign count_r_is_last = count_lo == len_lo;
	wire len_v_o;
	assign len_v_o = count_r_is_zero;
	assign up_li = yumi_i & ~count_r_is_last;
	assign clear_li = yumi_i & count_r_is_last;
	assign go_fifo_yumi_li = clear_li;
	bsg_counter_clear_up #(
		.max_val_p(max_els_p - 1),
		.init_val_p(0)
	) ctr(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.clear_i(clear_li),
		.up_i(up_li),
		.count_o(count_r)
	);
	bsg_mux #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
		.width_p(width_p),
		.els_p(max_els_p)
	) data_mux(
		.data_i(fifo_data_lo),
		.sel_i(count_lo),
		.data_o(data_o)
	);
endmodule
module bsg_round_robin_1_to_n (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	valid_i,
	ready_o,
	valid_o,
	ready_i
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter num_out_p = 2;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input valid_i;
	output ready_o;
	output [num_out_p - 1:0] valid_o;
	input [num_out_p - 1:0] ready_i;
	generate
		if (num_out_p == 1) begin : one_to_one
			assign valid_o = valid_i;
			wire ready_o;
			assign ready_o = ready_i;
		end
		else begin : one_to_n
			wire [(num_out_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(num_out_p)) - 1:0] ptr_r;
			wire yumi_i = valid_i & ready_o;
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			bsg_circular_ptr #(
				.slots_p(num_out_p),
				.max_add_p(1)
			) circular_ptr(
				.clk(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.add_i(yumi_i),
				.o(ptr_r),
				.n_o()
			);
			assign valid_o = valid_i << ptr_r;
			wire ready_o;
			assign ready_o = ready_i[ptr_r];
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_round_robin_2_to_2 (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	data_i,
	v_i,
	ready_o,
	data_o,
	v_o,
	ready_i
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [(width_p * 2) - 1:0] data_i;
	input [1:0] v_i;
	output [1:0] ready_o;
	output [(width_p * 2) - 1:0] data_o;
	output [1:0] v_o;
	input [1:0] ready_i;
	reg head_r;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i)
			head_r <= 0;
		else
			head_r <= ^{head_r, v_i & ready_o};
	assign data_o = (head_r ? {data_i[0+:width_p], data_i[width_p+:width_p]} : data_i);
	assign v_o = (head_r ? {v_i[0], v_i[1]} : v_i);
	assign ready_o = (head_r ? {ready_i[0], ready_i[1]} : ready_i);
endmodule
module bsg_round_robin_n_to_1 (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	data_i,
	v_i,
	yumi_o,
	v_o,
	data_o,
	tag_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter num_in_p = -1;
	parameter _sv2v_width_strict_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_strict_p - 1:0] strict_p = "inv";
	parameter tag_width_lp = (num_in_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(num_in_p));
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [(num_in_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_i;
	input [num_in_p - 1:0] v_i;
	output [num_in_p - 1:0] yumi_o;
	output v_o;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	output [tag_width_lp - 1:0] tag_o;
	input yumi_i;
	generate
		if (strict_p) begin : strict
			wire [tag_width_lp - 1:0] ptr_r;
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			wire yumi_i;
			bsg_circular_ptr #(
				.slots_p(num_in_p),
				.max_add_p(1)
			) circular_ptr(
				.clk(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.add_i(yumi_i),
				.o(ptr_r),
				.n_o()
			);
			wire v_o;
			assign v_o = v_i[ptr_r];
			assign data_o = data_i[ptr_r * width_p+:width_p];
			assign tag_o = ptr_r;
			function automatic [num_in_p - 1:0] sv2v_cast_1A36E;
				input reg [num_in_p - 1:0] inp;
				sv2v_cast_1A36E = inp;
			endfunction
			assign yumi_o = sv2v_cast_1A36E(yumi_i << tag_o);
		end
		else begin : greedy
			wire [num_in_p - 1:0] grants_lo;
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			wire v_o;
			bsg_round_robin_arb #(.inputs_p(num_in_p)) rr_arb_ctrl(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.grants_en_i(1'b1),
				.reqs_i(v_i),
				.grants_o(grants_lo),
				.sel_one_hot_o(),
				.v_o(v_o),
				.tag_o(tag_o),
				.yumi_i(yumi_i & v_o)
			);
			bsg_crossbar_o_by_i #(
				.i_els_p(num_in_p),
				.o_els_p(1),
				.width_p(width_p)
			) xbar(
				.i(data_i),
				.sel_oi_one_hot_i(grants_lo),
				.o(data_o)
			);
			assign yumi_o = grants_lo & {num_in_p {yumi_i}};
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_serial_in_parallel_out (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	valid_i,
	data_i,
	ready_o,
	valid_o,
	data_o,
	yumi_cnt_i
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter out_els_p = els_p;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input valid_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	output ready_o;
	output reg [out_els_p - 1:0] valid_o;
	output reg [(out_els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_o;
	input [$clog2(out_els_p + 1) - 1:0] yumi_cnt_i;
	localparam double_els_lp = els_p * 2;
	reg [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_r;
	reg [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_nn;
	reg [((2 * els_p) * width_p) - 1:0] data_n;
	reg [els_p - 1:0] valid_r;
	reg [els_p - 1:0] valid_nn;
	reg [double_els_lp - 1:0] valid_n;
	reg [$clog2(els_p + 1) - 1:0] num_els_r;
	wire [$clog2(els_p + 1) - 1:0] num_els_n;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i) begin
			num_els_r <= 0;
			valid_r <= 0;
		end
		else begin
			num_els_r <= num_els_n;
			valid_r <= valid_nn;
		end
	always @(posedge clk_i) data_r <= data_nn;
	wire ready_o;
	assign ready_o = ~valid_r[els_p - 1];
	assign num_els_n = (num_els_r + (valid_i & ready_o)) - yumi_cnt_i;
	function automatic [double_els_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_7E881;
		input reg [double_els_lp - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_7E881 = inp;
	endfunction
	always @(*) begin
		data_n = data_r;
		valid_n = sv2v_cast_7E881(valid_r);
		data_n[width_p * els_p+:width_p * els_p] = 0;
		data_n[num_els_r * width_p+:width_p] = data_i;
		valid_n[num_els_r] = valid_i & ready_o;
		valid_o = valid_n[out_els_p - 1:0];
		data_o = data_n[width_p * ((out_els_p - 1) - (out_els_p - 1))+:width_p * out_els_p];
		begin : sv2v_autoblock_9
			integer i;
			for (i = 0; i < els_p; i = i + 1)
				data_nn[i * width_p+:width_p] = data_n[(yumi_cnt_i + i) * width_p+:width_p];
		end
		valid_nn = valid_n[yumi_cnt_i+:els_p];
	end
endmodule
module bsg_serial_in_parallel_out_dynamic (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	v_i,
	len_i,
	data_i,
	ready_o,
	len_ready_o,
	v_o,
	data_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_max_els_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_max_els_p - 1:0] max_els_p = "inv";
	parameter lg_max_els_lp = (max_els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(max_els_p));
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input v_i;
	input [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] len_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	output ready_o;
	output len_ready_o;
	output v_o;
	output [(max_els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_o;
	input yumi_i;
	genvar i;
	wire yumi_lo;
	assign yumi_lo = v_i & ready_o;
	wire [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] count_r;
	wire [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] count_lo;
	wire [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] len_r;
	wire [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] len_lo;
	wire clear_li;
	wire up_li;
	wire dff_en_li;
	wire go_fifo_v_li;
	wire count_r_is_zero;
	wire count_r_is_last;
	assign count_lo = count_r;
	assign len_lo = (count_r_is_zero ? len_i : len_r);
	function automatic [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_C8F51;
		input reg [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_C8F51 = inp;
	endfunction
	assign count_r_is_zero = count_lo == sv2v_cast_C8F51(0);
	assign count_r_is_last = count_lo == len_lo;
	wire len_ready_o;
	assign len_ready_o = count_r_is_zero;
	assign up_li = yumi_lo & ~count_r_is_last;
	assign clear_li = yumi_lo & count_r_is_last;
	assign go_fifo_v_li = clear_li;
	assign dff_en_li = yumi_lo & count_r_is_zero;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	bsg_counter_clear_up #(
		.max_val_p(max_els_p - 1),
		.init_val_p(0)
	) ctr(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.clear_i(clear_li),
		.up_i(up_li),
		.count_o(count_r)
	);
	bsg_dff_reset_en #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(lg_max_els_lp),
		.reset_val_p(0)
	) dff_len(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.en_i(dff_en_li),
		.data_i(len_i),
		.data_o(len_r)
	);
	wire one_word_lo;
	wire v_o;
	wire yumi_i;
	bsg_two_fifo #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(1)
	) go_fifo(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.ready_o(),
		.data_i(count_r_is_zero),
		.v_i(go_fifo_v_li),
		.v_o(v_o),
		.data_o(one_word_lo),
		.yumi_i(yumi_i)
	);
	wire [max_els_p - 1:0] fifo_valid_li;
	wire [max_els_p - 1:0] fifo_ready_lo;
	wire [max_els_p - 1:0] fifo_valid_lo;
	wire [max_els_p - 1:0] fifo_yumi_li;
	wire ready_o;
	assign ready_o = fifo_ready_lo[count_lo];
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < max_els_p; i = i + 1) begin : rof0
			if (i == 0) assign fifo_yumi_li[i] = yumi_i;
			else assign fifo_yumi_li[i] = (fifo_valid_lo[i] & yumi_i) & ~one_word_lo;
		end
	endgenerate
	wire v_i;
	bsg_decode_with_v #(.num_out_p(max_els_p)) bdwv(
		.i(count_lo),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.o(fifo_valid_li)
	);
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < max_els_p; i = i + 1) begin : fifos
			if (i == 0) begin : twofifo
				bsg_two_fifo #(
					._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
					.width_p(width_p)
				) fifo(
					.clk_i(clk_i),
					.reset_i(reset_i),
					.ready_o(fifo_ready_lo[i]),
					.data_i(data_i),
					.v_i(fifo_valid_li[i]),
					.v_o(fifo_valid_lo[i]),
					.data_o(data_o[i * width_p+:width_p]),
					.yumi_i(fifo_yumi_li[i])
				);
			end
			else begin : onefifo
				bsg_one_fifo #(
					._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
					.width_p(width_p)
				) fifo(
					.clk_i(clk_i),
					.reset_i(reset_i),
					.ready_o(fifo_ready_lo[i]),
					.data_i(data_i),
					.v_i(fifo_valid_li[i]),
					.v_o(fifo_valid_lo[i]),
					.data_o(data_o[i * width_p+:width_p]),
					.yumi_i(fifo_yumi_li[i])
				);
			end
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_serial_in_parallel_out_full (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	v_i,
	ready_o,
	data_i,
	data_o,
	v_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_els_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_els_p - 1:0] els_p = "inv";
	parameter hi_to_lo_p = 0;
	parameter use_minimal_buffering_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input v_i;
	output wire ready_o;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	output wire [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_o;
	output wire v_o;
	input yumi_i;
	localparam lg_els_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	wire [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_lo;
	generate
		if (hi_to_lo_p == 0) begin : lo2hi
			assign data_o = data_lo;
		end
		else begin : hi2lo
			bsg_array_reverse #(
				.width_p(width_p),
				.els_p(els_p)
			) bar(
				.i(data_lo),
				.o(data_o)
			);
		end
	endgenerate
	wire [els_p - 1:0] fifo_valid_li;
	wire [els_p - 1:0] fifo_ready_lo;
	wire [els_p - 1:0] fifo_valid_lo;
	assign v_o = &fifo_valid_lo;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	wire v_i;
	bsg_round_robin_1_to_n #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
		.width_p(width_p),
		.num_out_p(els_p)
	) brr(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.valid_i(v_i),
		.ready_o(ready_o),
		.valid_o(fifo_valid_li),
		.ready_i(fifo_ready_lo)
	);
	genvar i;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < els_p; i = i + 1) begin : fifos
			if ((i == 0) && (use_minimal_buffering_p == 0)) begin : twofifo
				wire yumi_i;
				bsg_two_fifo #(
					._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
					.width_p(width_p)
				) fifo(
					.clk_i(clk_i),
					.reset_i(reset_i),
					.ready_o(fifo_ready_lo[i]),
					.data_i(data_i),
					.v_i(fifo_valid_li[i]),
					.v_o(fifo_valid_lo[i]),
					.data_o(data_lo[i * width_p+:width_p]),
					.yumi_i(yumi_i)
				);
			end
			else begin : onefifo
				wire yumi_i;
				bsg_one_fifo #(
					._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
					.width_p(width_p)
				) fifo(
					.clk_i(clk_i),
					.reset_i(reset_i),
					.ready_o(fifo_ready_lo[i]),
					.data_i(data_i),
					.v_i(fifo_valid_li[i]),
					.v_o(fifo_valid_lo[i]),
					.data_o(data_lo[i * width_p+:width_p]),
					.yumi_i(yumi_i)
				);
			end
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_shift_reg (
	clk,
	reset_i,
	valid_i,
	data_i,
	valid_o,
	data_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_stages_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_stages_p - 1:0] stages_p = "inv";
	input clk;
	input reset_i;
	input valid_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	output valid_o;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	reg [(width_p >= 0 ? (stages_p * (width_p + 1)) - 1 : (stages_p * (1 - width_p)) + (width_p - 1)):(width_p >= 0 ? 0 : width_p)] shift_r;
	always @(posedge clk)
		if (reset_i)
			shift_r <= {stages_p * (width_p >= 0 ? width_p + 1 : 1 - width_p) {1'sb0}};
		else begin
			shift_r[(width_p >= 0 ? 0 : width_p) + ((width_p >= 0 ? width_p + 1 : 1 - width_p) * (((stages_p - 1) >= ((stages_p - 1) < 1 ? stages_p - 1 : 1) ? stages_p - 1 : ((stages_p - 1) + ((stages_p - 1) >= ((stages_p - 1) < 1 ? stages_p - 1 : 1) ? ((stages_p - 1) - ((stages_p - 1) < 1 ? stages_p - 1 : 1)) + 1 : (((stages_p - 1) < 1 ? stages_p - 1 : 1) - (stages_p - 1)) + 1)) - 1) - (((stages_p - 1) >= ((stages_p - 1) < 1 ? stages_p - 1 : 1) ? ((stages_p - 1) - ((stages_p - 1) < 1 ? stages_p - 1 : 1)) + 1 : (((stages_p - 1) < 1 ? stages_p - 1 : 1) - (stages_p - 1)) + 1) - 1)))+:(width_p >= 0 ? width_p + 1 : 1 - width_p) * ((stages_p - 1) >= ((stages_p - 1) < 1 ? stages_p - 1 : 1) ? ((stages_p - 1) - ((stages_p - 1) < 1 ? stages_p - 1 : 1)) + 1 : (((stages_p - 1) < 1 ? stages_p - 1 : 1) - (stages_p - 1)) + 1)] <= shift_r[(width_p >= 0 ? 0 : width_p) + ((width_p >= 0 ? width_p + 1 : 1 - width_p) * ((((stages_p - 2) > 0 ? stages_p - 2 : 0) >= 0 ? ((stages_p - 2) > 0 ? stages_p - 2 : 0) : (((stages_p - 2) > 0 ? stages_p - 2 : 0) + (((stages_p - 2) > 0 ? stages_p - 2 : 0) >= 0 ? ((stages_p - 2) > 0 ? stages_p - 2 : 0) + 1 : 1 - ((stages_p - 2) > 0 ? stages_p - 2 : 0))) - 1) - ((((stages_p - 2) > 0 ? stages_p - 2 : 0) >= 0 ? ((stages_p - 2) > 0 ? stages_p - 2 : 0) + 1 : 1 - ((stages_p - 2) > 0 ? stages_p - 2 : 0)) - 1)))+:(width_p >= 0 ? width_p + 1 : 1 - width_p) * (((stages_p - 2) > 0 ? stages_p - 2 : 0) >= 0 ? ((stages_p - 2) > 0 ? stages_p - 2 : 0) + 1 : 1 - ((stages_p - 2) > 0 ? stages_p - 2 : 0))];
			shift_r[(width_p >= 0 ? 0 : width_p)+:(width_p >= 0 ? width_p + 1 : 1 - width_p)] <= {valid_i, data_i};
		end
	assign {valid_o, data_o} = shift_r[(width_p >= 0 ? 0 : width_p) + ((stages_p - 1) * (width_p >= 0 ? width_p + 1 : 1 - width_p))+:(width_p >= 0 ? width_p + 1 : 1 - width_p)];
endmodule
module bsg_two_fifo (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	ready_o,
	data_i,
	v_i,
	v_o,
	data_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter verbose_p = 0;
	parameter allow_enq_deq_on_full_p = 0;
	parameter ready_THEN_valid_p = allow_enq_deq_on_full_p;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	output ready_o;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input v_i;
	output v_o;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	input yumi_i;
	wire deq_i = yumi_i;
	wire enq_i;
	reg head_r;
	reg tail_r;
	reg empty_r;
	reg full_r;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	bsg_mem_1r1w #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.els_p(2),
		.read_write_same_addr_p(allow_enq_deq_on_full_p)
	) mem_1r1w(
		.w_clk_i(clk_i),
		.w_reset_i(reset_i),
		.w_v_i(enq_i),
		.w_addr_i(tail_r),
		.w_data_i(data_i),
		.r_v_i(~empty_r),
		.r_addr_i(head_r),
		.r_data_o(data_o)
	);
	wire v_o;
	assign v_o = ~empty_r;
	wire ready_o;
	assign ready_o = ~full_r;
	generate
		if (ready_THEN_valid_p) assign enq_i = v_i;
		else assign enq_i = v_i & ~full_r;
	endgenerate
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i) begin
			tail_r <= 1'b0;
			head_r <= 1'b0;
			empty_r <= 1'b1;
			full_r <= 1'b0;
		end
		else begin
			if (enq_i)
				tail_r <= ~tail_r;
			if (deq_i)
				head_r <= ~head_r;
			empty_r <= (empty_r & ~enq_i) | ((~full_r & deq_i) & ~enq_i);
			if (allow_enq_deq_on_full_p)
				full_r <= ((~empty_r & enq_i) & ~deq_i) | (full_r & ~(deq_i ^ enq_i));
			else
				full_r <= ((~empty_r & enq_i) & ~deq_i) | (full_r & ~deq_i);
		end
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (~reset_i)
			if (allow_enq_deq_on_full_p)
				;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (verbose_p) begin
			if (v_i)
				$display("### %m enq %x onto fifo", data_i);
			if (deq_i)
				$display("### %m deq %x from fifo", data_o);
		end
	wire [31:0] num_elements_debug = full_r + (empty_r == 0);
endmodule
module bsg_cam_1r1w (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	w_v_i,
	w_nuke_i,
	w_tag_i,
	w_data_i,
	r_v_i,
	r_tag_i,
	r_data_o,
	r_v_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_els_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_els_p - 1:0] els_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_tag_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_tag_width_p - 1:0] tag_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_data_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_data_width_p - 1:0] data_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_repl_scheme_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_repl_scheme_p - 1:0] repl_scheme_p = "lru";
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input w_v_i;
	input w_nuke_i;
	input [tag_width_p - 1:0] w_tag_i;
	input [data_width_p - 1:0] w_data_i;
	input r_v_i;
	input [tag_width_p - 1:0] r_tag_i;
	output wire [data_width_p - 1:0] r_data_o;
	output wire r_v_o;
	wire [els_p - 1:0] tag_r_match_lo;
	wire [els_p - 1:0] tag_empty_lo;
	wire [els_p - 1:0] repl_way_lo;
	wire [els_p - 1:0] tag_w_v_li = repl_way_lo | {els_p {w_nuke_i}};
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	wire r_v_i;
	bsg_cam_1r1w_tag_array #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_tag_width_p),
		.width_p(tag_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_els_p(_sv2v_width_els_p),
		.els_p(els_p)
	) cam_tag_array(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.w_v_i(tag_w_v_li),
		.w_set_not_clear_i(w_v_i & ~w_nuke_i),
		.w_tag_i(w_tag_i),
		.w_empty_o(tag_empty_lo),
		.r_v_i(r_v_i),
		.r_tag_i(r_tag_i),
		.r_match_o(tag_r_match_lo)
	);
	wire w_v_i;
	bsg_cam_1r1w_replacement #(
		.els_p(els_p),
		._sv2v_width_scheme_p(_sv2v_width_repl_scheme_p),
		.scheme_p(repl_scheme_p)
	) replacement(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.read_v_i(tag_r_match_lo),
		.alloc_v_i(w_v_i),
		.alloc_empty_i(tag_empty_lo),
		.alloc_v_o(repl_way_lo)
	);
	wire [els_p - 1:0] mem_w_v_li = repl_way_lo;
	bsg_mem_1r1w_one_hot #(
		.width_p(data_width_p),
		.els_p(els_p)
	) one_hot_mem(
		.w_clk_i(clk_i),
		.w_reset_i(reset_i),
		.w_v_i(mem_w_v_li),
		.w_data_i(w_data_i),
		.r_v_i(tag_r_match_lo),
		.r_data_o(r_data_o)
	);
	assign r_v_o = |tag_r_match_lo;
endmodule
module bsg_cam_1r1w_replacement (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	read_v_i,
	alloc_v_i,
	alloc_empty_i,
	alloc_v_o
);
	parameter els_p = 2;
	parameter _sv2v_width_scheme_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_scheme_p - 1:0] scheme_p = "lru";
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [els_p - 1:0] read_v_i;
	input alloc_v_i;
	input [els_p - 1:0] alloc_empty_i;
	output [els_p - 1:0] alloc_v_o;
	generate
		if (scheme_p == "lru") begin : lru
			localparam lg_els_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
			wire read_v_li = |read_v_i;
			wire lru_touch_li = read_v_li | alloc_v_i;
			wire [els_p - 2:0] lru_n;
			wire [els_p - 2:0] lru_r;
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			bsg_dff_reset_en #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
				.width_p(els_p - 1)
			) lru_reg(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.en_i(lru_touch_li),
				.data_i(lru_n),
				.data_o(lru_r)
			);
			wire [lg_els_lp - 1:0] lru_way_lo;
			bsg_lru_pseudo_tree_encode #(
				._sv2v_width_ways_p(32),
				.ways_p(els_p)
			) lru_encoder(
				.lru_i(lru_r),
				.way_id_o(lru_way_lo)
			);
			wire [lg_els_lp - 1:0] empty_way_lo;
			wire empty_way_v_lo;
			bsg_priority_encode #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
				.width_p(els_p),
				._sv2v_width_lo_to_hi_p(32),
				.lo_to_hi_p(1)
			) empty_encoder(
				.i(alloc_empty_i),
				.addr_o(empty_way_lo),
				.v_o(empty_way_v_lo)
			);
			wire [lg_els_lp - 1:0] way_lo = (empty_way_v_lo ? empty_way_lo : lru_way_lo);
			bsg_decode #(
				._sv2v_width_num_out_p(32),
				.num_out_p(els_p)
			) way_decoder(
				.i(way_lo),
				.o(alloc_v_o)
			);
			wire [lg_els_lp - 1:0] read_way_li;
			bsg_encode_one_hot #(.width_p(els_p)) read_way_encoder(
				.i(read_v_i),
				.addr_o(read_way_li),
				.v_o()
			);
			wire [els_p - 2:0] read_update_data_lo;
			wire [els_p - 2:0] read_update_mask_lo;
			bsg_lru_pseudo_tree_decode #(
				._sv2v_width_ways_p(32),
				.ways_p(els_p)
			) read_decoder(
				.way_id_i(read_way_li),
				.data_o(read_update_data_lo),
				.mask_o(read_update_mask_lo)
			);
			wire [els_p - 2:0] read_update_lo;
			wire [els_p - 2:0] read_sel_lo = read_update_mask_lo & {els_p - 1 {read_v_li}};
			bsg_mux_bitwise #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
				.width_p(els_p - 1)
			) read_update_mux(
				.data0_i(lru_r),
				.data1_i(read_update_data_lo),
				.sel_i(read_sel_lo),
				.data_o(read_update_lo)
			);
			wire [els_p - 2:0] alloc_update_data_lo;
			wire [els_p - 2:0] alloc_update_mask_lo;
			bsg_lru_pseudo_tree_decode #(
				._sv2v_width_ways_p(32),
				.ways_p(els_p)
			) alloc_decoder(
				.way_id_i(way_lo),
				.data_o(alloc_update_data_lo),
				.mask_o(alloc_update_mask_lo)
			);
			wire [els_p - 2:0] alloc_update_lo;
			wire [els_p - 2:0] alloc_sel_lo = alloc_update_mask_lo & {els_p - 1 {alloc_v_i}};
			bsg_mux_bitwise #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
				.width_p(els_p - 1)
			) alloc_update_mux(
				.data0_i(read_update_lo),
				.data1_i(alloc_update_data_lo),
				.sel_i(alloc_sel_lo),
				.data_o(alloc_update_lo)
			);
			assign lru_n = alloc_update_lo;
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_cam_1r1w_sync (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	w_v_i,
	w_nuke_i,
	w_tag_i,
	w_data_i,
	r_v_i,
	r_tag_i,
	r_data_o,
	r_v_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_els_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_els_p - 1:0] els_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_tag_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_tag_width_p - 1:0] tag_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_data_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_data_width_p - 1:0] data_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_repl_scheme_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_repl_scheme_p - 1:0] repl_scheme_p = "lru";
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input w_v_i;
	input w_nuke_i;
	input [tag_width_p - 1:0] w_tag_i;
	input [data_width_p - 1:0] w_data_i;
	input r_v_i;
	input [tag_width_p - 1:0] r_tag_i;
	output wire [data_width_p - 1:0] r_data_o;
	output wire r_v_o;
	wire [tag_width_p - 1:0] r_tag_r;
	wire r_v_r;
	wire clk_i;
	bsg_dff #(.width_p(1 + tag_width_p)) r_tag_reg(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.data_i({r_v_i, r_tag_i}),
		.data_o({r_v_r, r_tag_r})
	);
	wire reset_i;
	wire w_v_i;
	wire w_nuke_i;
	bsg_cam_1r1w #(
		._sv2v_width_els_p(_sv2v_width_els_p),
		.els_p(els_p),
		._sv2v_width_tag_width_p(_sv2v_width_tag_width_p),
		.tag_width_p(tag_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_data_width_p(_sv2v_width_data_width_p),
		.data_width_p(data_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_repl_scheme_p(_sv2v_width_repl_scheme_p),
		.repl_scheme_p(repl_scheme_p)
	) cam(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.w_v_i(w_v_i),
		.w_nuke_i(w_nuke_i),
		.w_tag_i(w_tag_i),
		.w_data_i(w_data_i),
		.r_v_i(r_v_r),
		.r_tag_i(r_tag_r),
		.r_data_o(r_data_o),
		.r_v_o(r_v_o)
	);
endmodule
module bsg_cam_1r1w_tag_array (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	w_v_i,
	w_set_not_clear_i,
	w_tag_i,
	w_empty_o,
	r_v_i,
	r_tag_i,
	r_match_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_els_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_els_p - 1:0] els_p = "inv";
	parameter multiple_entries_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [els_p - 1:0] w_v_i;
	input w_set_not_clear_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] w_tag_i;
	output wire [els_p - 1:0] w_empty_o;
	input r_v_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] r_tag_i;
	output wire [els_p - 1:0] r_match_o;
	wire [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] tag_r;
	wire [els_p - 1:0] v_r;
	generate
		genvar i;
		for (i = 0; i < els_p; i = i + 1) begin : tag_array
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			wire w_set_not_clear_i;
			bsg_dff_reset_en #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
				.width_p(1)
			) v_reg(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.en_i(w_v_i[i]),
				.data_i(w_set_not_clear_i),
				.data_o(v_r[i])
			);
			bsg_dff_en #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
				.width_p(width_p)
			) tag_r_reg(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.en_i(w_v_i[i] & w_set_not_clear_i),
				.data_i(w_tag_i),
				.data_o(tag_r[i * width_p+:width_p])
			);
			assign r_match_o[i] = (r_v_i & v_r[i]) & (tag_r[i * width_p+:width_p] == r_tag_i);
			assign w_empty_o[i] = ~v_r[i];
		end
	endgenerate
	always @(negedge clk_i)
		;
endmodule
module bsg_mem_1r1w (
	w_clk_i,
	w_reset_i,
	w_v_i,
	w_addr_i,
	w_data_i,
	r_v_i,
	r_addr_i,
	r_data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter read_write_same_addr_p = 0;
	parameter addr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	parameter harden_p = 0;
	input w_clk_i;
	input w_reset_i;
	input w_v_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] w_addr_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] w_data_i;
	input r_v_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] r_addr_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] r_data_o;
	wire w_clk_i;
	wire w_reset_i;
	wire w_v_i;
	wire r_v_i;
	bsg_mem_1r1w_synth #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.els_p(els_p),
		.read_write_same_addr_p(read_write_same_addr_p),
		.harden_p(harden_p)
	) synth(
		.w_clk_i(w_clk_i),
		.w_reset_i(w_reset_i),
		.w_v_i(w_v_i),
		.w_addr_i(w_addr_i),
		.w_data_i(w_data_i),
		.r_v_i(r_v_i),
		.r_addr_i(r_addr_i),
		.r_data_o(r_data_o)
	);
	initial if (read_write_same_addr_p || ((width_p * els_p) >= 64))
		$display("## %L: instantiating width_p=%d, els_p=%d, read_write_same_addr_p=%d, harden_p=%d (%m)", width_p, els_p, read_write_same_addr_p, harden_p);
	always @(negedge w_clk_i)
		if (w_v_i === 1'b1)
			;
endmodule
module bsg_mem_1r1w_one_hot (
	w_clk_i,
	w_reset_i,
	w_v_i,
	w_data_i,
	r_v_i,
	r_data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	input w_clk_i;
	input w_reset_i;
	input [els_p - 1:0] w_v_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] w_data_i;
	input [els_p - 1:0] r_v_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] r_data_o;
	wire [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_r;
	wire unused0 = w_reset_i;
	generate
		genvar i;
		for (i = 0; i < els_p; i = i + 1) begin : mem_array
			wire w_clk_i;
			bsg_dff_en #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
				.width_p(width_p)
			) mem_reg(
				.clk_i(w_clk_i),
				.en_i(w_v_i[i]),
				.data_i(w_data_i),
				.data_o(data_r[i * width_p+:width_p])
			);
		end
	endgenerate
	bsg_mux_one_hot #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(width_p),
		.els_p(els_p)
	) one_hot_sel(
		.data_i(data_r),
		.sel_one_hot_i(r_v_i),
		.data_o(r_data_o)
	);
	initial if ((width_p * els_p) >= 64)
		$display("## %L: instantiating width_p=%d, els_p=%d (%m)", width_p, els_p);
	always @(negedge w_clk_i)
		;
endmodule
module bsg_mem_1r1w_sync (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	w_v_i,
	w_addr_i,
	w_data_i,
	r_v_i,
	r_addr_i,
	r_data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter read_write_same_addr_p = 0;
	parameter addr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	parameter harden_p = 0;
	parameter disable_collision_warning_p = 1;
	parameter enable_clock_gating_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input w_v_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] w_addr_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] w_data_i;
	input r_v_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] r_addr_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] r_data_o;
	wire clk_lo;
	generate
		if (enable_clock_gating_p) begin
			wire clk_i;
			bsg_clkgate_optional icg(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.en_i(w_v_i | r_v_i),
				.bypass_i(1'b0),
				.gated_clock_o(clk_lo)
			);
		end
		else assign clk_lo = clk_i;
	endgenerate
	wire reset_i;
	wire w_v_i;
	wire r_v_i;
	bsg_mem_1r1w_sync_synth #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.els_p(els_p),
		.read_write_same_addr_p(read_write_same_addr_p),
		.harden_p(harden_p)
	) synth(
		.clk_i(clk_lo),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.w_v_i(w_v_i),
		.w_addr_i(w_addr_i),
		.w_data_i(w_data_i),
		.r_v_i(r_v_i),
		.r_addr_i(r_addr_i),
		.r_data_o(r_data_o)
	);
	initial $display("## %L: instantiating width_p=%d, els_p=%d, read_write_same_addr_p=%d, harden_p=%d (%m)", width_p, els_p, read_write_same_addr_p, harden_p);
	always @(posedge clk_lo)
		if (w_v_i)
			;
endmodule
module bsg_mem_1r1w_sync_synth (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	w_v_i,
	w_addr_i,
	w_data_i,
	r_v_i,
	r_addr_i,
	r_data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter read_write_same_addr_p = 0;
	parameter addr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	parameter harden_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input w_v_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] w_addr_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] w_data_i;
	input r_v_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] r_addr_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] r_data_o;
	reg [width_p - 1:0] mem [els_p - 1:0];
	wire unused = reset_i;
	reg [addr_width_lp - 1:0] r_addr_r;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (r_v_i)
			r_addr_r <= r_addr_i;
		else
			r_addr_r <= {addr_width_lp {1'sbx}};
	assign r_data_o = mem[r_addr_r];
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (w_v_i)
			mem[w_addr_i] <= w_data_i;
endmodule
module bsg_mem_1r1w_synth (
	w_clk_i,
	w_reset_i,
	w_v_i,
	w_addr_i,
	w_data_i,
	r_v_i,
	r_addr_i,
	r_data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter read_write_same_addr_p = 0;
	parameter addr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	parameter harden_p = 0;
	input w_clk_i;
	input w_reset_i;
	input w_v_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] w_addr_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] w_data_i;
	input r_v_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] r_addr_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] r_data_o;
	reg [width_p - 1:0] mem [els_p - 1:0];
	wire unused0 = w_reset_i;
	wire unused1 = r_v_i;
	assign r_data_o = mem[r_addr_i];
	always @(posedge w_clk_i)
		if (w_v_i)
			mem[w_addr_i] <= w_data_i;
endmodule
module bsg_mem_1rw_sync (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	data_i,
	addr_i,
	v_i,
	w_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter latch_last_read_p = 0;
	parameter addr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	parameter enable_clock_gating_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] addr_i;
	input v_i;
	input w_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	wire clk_lo;
	generate
		if (enable_clock_gating_p) begin
			wire clk_i;
			wire v_i;
			bsg_clkgate_optional icg(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.en_i(v_i),
				.bypass_i(1'b0),
				.gated_clock_o(clk_lo)
			);
		end
		else assign clk_lo = clk_i;
	endgenerate
	wire reset_i;
	wire v_i;
	wire w_i;
	bsg_mem_1rw_sync_synth #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.els_p(els_p),
		.latch_last_read_p(latch_last_read_p)
	) synth(
		.clk_i(clk_lo),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i(data_i),
		.addr_i(addr_i),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.w_i(w_i),
		.data_o(data_o)
	);
endmodule
module bsg_mem_1rw_sync_mask_write_bit (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	data_i,
	addr_i,
	v_i,
	w_mask_i,
	w_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter latch_last_read_p = 0;
	parameter enable_clock_gating_p = 0;
	parameter addr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] addr_i;
	input v_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] w_mask_i;
	input w_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	wire clk_lo;
	generate
		if (enable_clock_gating_p) begin
			wire clk_i;
			wire v_i;
			bsg_clkgate_optional icg(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.en_i(v_i),
				.bypass_i(1'b0),
				.gated_clock_o(clk_lo)
			);
		end
		else assign clk_lo = clk_i;
	endgenerate
	wire reset_i;
	wire v_i;
	wire w_i;
	bsg_mem_1rw_sync_mask_write_bit_synth #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.els_p(els_p),
		.latch_last_read_p(latch_last_read_p)
	) synth(
		.clk_i(clk_lo),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i(data_i),
		.addr_i(addr_i),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.w_mask_i(w_mask_i),
		.w_i(w_i),
		.data_o(data_o)
	);
	always @(negedge clk_lo)
		if (v_i === 1)
			;
	initial $display("## %L: instantiating width_p=%d, els_p=%d (%m)", width_p, els_p);
endmodule
module bsg_mem_1rw_sync_mask_write_bit_banked (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	v_i,
	w_i,
	addr_i,
	data_i,
	w_mask_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_els_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_els_p - 1:0] els_p = "inv";
	parameter latch_last_read_p = 0;
	parameter num_width_bank_p = 1;
	parameter num_depth_bank_p = 1;
	parameter addr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	parameter bank_depth_lp = els_p / num_depth_bank_p;
	parameter bank_addr_width_lp = (bank_depth_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(bank_depth_lp));
	parameter depth_bank_idx_width_lp = (num_depth_bank_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(num_depth_bank_p));
	parameter bank_width_lp = width_p / num_width_bank_p;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input v_i;
	input w_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] addr_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] w_mask_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	generate
		if (num_depth_bank_p == 1) begin : db1
			genvar i;
			for (i = 0; i < num_width_bank_p; i = i + 1) begin : wb
				wire clk_i;
				wire reset_i;
				wire v_i;
				wire w_i;
				bsg_mem_1rw_sync_mask_write_bit #(
					.width_p(bank_width_lp),
					.els_p(bank_depth_lp),
					.latch_last_read_p(latch_last_read_p)
				) bank(
					.clk_i(clk_i),
					.reset_i(reset_i),
					.v_i(v_i),
					.w_i(w_i),
					.addr_i(addr_i),
					.data_i(data_i[bank_width_lp * i+:bank_width_lp]),
					.w_mask_i(w_mask_i[bank_width_lp * i+:bank_width_lp]),
					.data_o(data_o[bank_width_lp * i+:bank_width_lp])
				);
			end
		end
		else begin : dbn
			wire [depth_bank_idx_width_lp - 1:0] depth_bank_idx_li = addr_i[0+:depth_bank_idx_width_lp];
			wire [bank_addr_width_lp - 1:0] bank_addr_li = addr_i[depth_bank_idx_width_lp+:bank_addr_width_lp];
			wire [num_depth_bank_p - 1:0] bank_v_li;
			wire [(num_depth_bank_p * width_p) - 1:0] bank_data_lo;
			wire v_i;
			bsg_decode_with_v #(.num_out_p(num_depth_bank_p)) demux_v(
				.i(depth_bank_idx_li),
				.v_i(v_i),
				.o(bank_v_li)
			);
			genvar i;
			for (i = 0; i < num_width_bank_p; i = i + 1) begin : wb
				genvar j;
				for (j = 0; j < num_depth_bank_p; j = j + 1) begin : db
					wire clk_i;
					wire reset_i;
					wire w_i;
					bsg_mem_1rw_sync_mask_write_bit #(
						.width_p(bank_width_lp),
						.els_p(bank_depth_lp),
						.latch_last_read_p(latch_last_read_p)
					) bank(
						.clk_i(clk_i),
						.reset_i(reset_i),
						.v_i(bank_v_li[j]),
						.w_i(w_i),
						.addr_i(bank_addr_li),
						.data_i(data_i[i * bank_width_lp+:bank_width_lp]),
						.w_mask_i(w_mask_i[i * bank_width_lp+:bank_width_lp]),
						.data_o(bank_data_lo[(j * width_p) + (i * bank_width_lp)+:bank_width_lp])
					);
				end
			end
			wire [depth_bank_idx_width_lp - 1:0] depth_bank_idx_r;
			wire clk_i;
			bsg_dff_en #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
				.width_p(depth_bank_idx_width_lp)
			) depth_bank_idx_dff(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.en_i(v_i & ~w_i),
				.data_i(depth_bank_idx_li),
				.data_o(depth_bank_idx_r)
			);
			bsg_mux #(
				.els_p(num_depth_bank_p),
				._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
				.width_p(width_p)
			) data_out_mux(
				.data_i(bank_data_lo),
				.sel_i(depth_bank_idx_r),
				.data_o(data_o)
			);
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_mem_1rw_sync_mask_write_bit_synth (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	data_i,
	addr_i,
	v_i,
	w_mask_i,
	w_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter latch_last_read_p = 0;
	parameter addr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] addr_i;
	input v_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] w_mask_i;
	input w_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	wire unused = reset_i;
	reg [addr_width_lp - 1:0] addr_r;
	reg [width_p - 1:0] mem [els_p - 1:0];
	wire read_en;
	assign read_en = v_i & ~w_i;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (read_en)
			addr_r <= addr_i;
		else
			addr_r <= {addr_width_lp {1'sbx}};
	wire [width_p - 1:0] data_out;
	assign data_out = mem[addr_r];
	generate
		if (latch_last_read_p) begin : llr
			wire read_en_r;
			wire clk_i;
			bsg_dff #(.width_p(1)) read_en_dff(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.data_i(read_en),
				.data_o(read_en_r)
			);
			bsg_dff_en_bypass #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
				.width_p(width_p)
			) dff_bypass(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.en_i(read_en_r),
				.data_i(data_out),
				.data_o(data_o)
			);
		end
		else begin : no_llr
			assign data_o = data_out;
		end
	endgenerate
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (v_i & w_i) begin : sv2v_autoblock_10
			integer i;
			for (i = 0; i < width_p; i = i + 1)
				if (w_mask_i[i])
					mem[addr_i][i] <= data_i[i];
		end
endmodule
module bsg_mem_1rw_sync_mask_write_byte (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	v_i,
	w_i,
	addr_i,
	data_i,
	write_mask_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter addr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	parameter data_width_p = -1;
	parameter latch_last_read_p = 0;
	parameter write_mask_width_lp = data_width_p >> 3;
	parameter enable_clock_gating_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input v_i;
	input w_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] addr_i;
	input [data_width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input [write_mask_width_lp - 1:0] write_mask_i;
	output wire [data_width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	wire clk_lo;
	generate
		if (enable_clock_gating_p) begin
			wire clk_i;
			wire v_i;
			bsg_clkgate_optional icg(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.en_i(v_i),
				.bypass_i(1'b0),
				.gated_clock_o(clk_lo)
			);
		end
		else assign clk_lo = clk_i;
	endgenerate
	wire reset_i;
	wire v_i;
	wire w_i;
	bsg_mem_1rw_sync_mask_write_byte_synth #(
		.els_p(els_p),
		.data_width_p(data_width_p),
		.latch_last_read_p(latch_last_read_p)
	) synth(
		.clk_i(clk_lo),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.w_i(w_i),
		.addr_i(addr_i),
		.data_i(data_i),
		.write_mask_i(write_mask_i),
		.data_o(data_o)
	);
	always @(*)
		;
	initial $display("## %L: instantiating data_width_p=%d, els_p=%d (%m)", data_width_p, els_p);
endmodule
module bsg_mem_1rw_sync_mask_write_byte_synth (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	v_i,
	w_i,
	addr_i,
	data_i,
	write_mask_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter addr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	parameter latch_last_read_p = 0;
	parameter data_width_p = -1;
	parameter write_mask_width_lp = data_width_p >> 3;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input v_i;
	input w_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] addr_i;
	input [data_width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input [write_mask_width_lp - 1:0] write_mask_i;
	output [data_width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	genvar i;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < write_mask_width_lp; i = i + 1) begin : bk
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			bsg_mem_1rw_sync #(
				.width_p(8),
				.els_p(els_p),
				.addr_width_lp(addr_width_lp),
				.latch_last_read_p(latch_last_read_p)
			) mem_1rw_sync(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.data_i(data_i[i * 8+:8]),
				.addr_i(addr_i),
				.v_i(v_i & (w_i ? write_mask_i[i] : 1'b1)),
				.w_i(w_i & write_mask_i[i]),
				.data_o(data_o[i * 8+:8])
			);
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_mem_1rw_sync_synth (
	clk_i,
	v_i,
	reset_i,
	data_i,
	addr_i,
	w_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter latch_last_read_p = 0;
	parameter addr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	input clk_i;
	input v_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] addr_i;
	input w_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	wire unused = reset_i;
	reg [addr_width_lp - 1:0] addr_r;
	reg [width_p - 1:0] mem [els_p - 1:0];
	wire read_en;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] data_out;
	assign read_en = v_i & ~w_i;
	assign data_out = mem[addr_r];
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (read_en)
			addr_r <= addr_i;
		else
			addr_r <= {addr_width_lp {1'sbx}};
	generate
		if (latch_last_read_p) begin : llr
			wire read_en_r;
			wire clk_i;
			bsg_dff #(.width_p(1)) read_en_dff(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.data_i(read_en),
				.data_o(read_en_r)
			);
			bsg_dff_en_bypass #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
				.width_p(width_p)
			) dff_bypass(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.en_i(read_en_r),
				.data_i(data_out),
				.data_o(data_o)
			);
		end
		else begin : no_llr
			assign data_o = data_out;
		end
	endgenerate
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (v_i & w_i)
			mem[addr_i] <= data_i;
	initial $display("## %L: instantiating width_p=%d, els_p=%d (%m)", width_p, els_p);
	always @(negedge clk_i)
		if (v_i)
			;
endmodule
module bsg_mem_2r1w_sync (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	w_v_i,
	w_addr_i,
	w_data_i,
	r0_v_i,
	r0_addr_i,
	r0_data_o,
	r1_v_i,
	r1_addr_i,
	r1_data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter read_write_same_addr_p = 0;
	parameter addr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	parameter harden_p = 0;
	parameter enable_clock_gating_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input w_v_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] w_addr_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] w_data_i;
	input r0_v_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] r0_addr_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] r0_data_o;
	input r1_v_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] r1_addr_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] r1_data_o;
	wire clk_lo;
	generate
		if (enable_clock_gating_p) begin
			wire clk_i;
			bsg_clkgate_optional icg(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.en_i((w_v_i | r0_v_i) | r1_v_i),
				.bypass_i(1'b0),
				.gated_clock_o(clk_lo)
			);
		end
		else assign clk_lo = clk_i;
	endgenerate
	wire reset_i;
	wire w_v_i;
	wire r0_v_i;
	wire r1_v_i;
	bsg_mem_2r1w_sync_synth #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.els_p(els_p),
		.read_write_same_addr_p(read_write_same_addr_p),
		.harden_p(harden_p)
	) synth(
		.clk_i(clk_lo),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.w_v_i(w_v_i),
		.w_addr_i(w_addr_i),
		.w_data_i(w_data_i),
		.r0_v_i(r0_v_i),
		.r0_addr_i(r0_addr_i),
		.r0_data_o(r0_data_o),
		.r1_v_i(r1_v_i),
		.r1_addr_i(r1_addr_i),
		.r1_data_o(r1_data_o)
	);
	always @(negedge clk_lo)
		if (w_v_i)
			;
	initial $display("## %L: instantiating width_p=%d, els_p=%d, read_write_same_addr_p=%d, harden_p=%d (%m)", width_p, els_p, read_write_same_addr_p, harden_p);
endmodule
module bsg_mem_2r1w_sync_synth (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	w_v_i,
	w_addr_i,
	w_data_i,
	r0_v_i,
	r0_addr_i,
	r0_data_o,
	r1_v_i,
	r1_addr_i,
	r1_data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter read_write_same_addr_p = 0;
	parameter addr_width_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	parameter harden_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input w_v_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] w_addr_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] w_data_i;
	input r0_v_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] r0_addr_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] r0_data_o;
	input r1_v_i;
	input [addr_width_lp - 1:0] r1_addr_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] r1_data_o;
	reg [width_p - 1:0] mem [els_p - 1:0];
	wire unused = reset_i;
	reg [addr_width_lp - 1:0] r0_addr_r;
	reg [addr_width_lp - 1:0] r1_addr_r;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (r0_v_i)
			r0_addr_r <= r0_addr_i;
		else
			r0_addr_r <= {addr_width_lp {1'sbx}};
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (r1_v_i)
			r1_addr_r <= r1_addr_i;
		else
			r1_addr_r <= {addr_width_lp {1'sbx}};
	assign r0_data_o = mem[r0_addr_r];
	assign r1_data_o = mem[r1_addr_r];
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (w_v_i)
			mem[w_addr_i] <= w_data_i;
endmodule
module bsg_adder_ripple_carry (
	a_i,
	b_i,
	s_o,
	c_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	input [width_p - 1:0] a_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] b_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] s_o;
	output wire c_o;
	assign {c_o, s_o} = a_i + b_i;
endmodule
module bsg_arb_fixed (
	ready_i,
	reqs_i,
	grants_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_inputs_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_inputs_p - 1:0] inputs_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_lo_to_hi_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_lo_to_hi_p - 1:0] lo_to_hi_p = "inv";
	input ready_i;
	input [inputs_p - 1:0] reqs_i;
	output [inputs_p - 1:0] grants_o;
	wire [inputs_p - 1:0] grants_unmasked_lo;
	bsg_priority_encode_one_hot_out #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_inputs_p),
		.width_p(inputs_p),
		._sv2v_width_lo_to_hi_p(_sv2v_width_lo_to_hi_p),
		.lo_to_hi_p(lo_to_hi_p)
	) enc(
		.i(reqs_i),
		.o(grants_unmasked_lo),
		.v_o()
	);
	assign grants_o = grants_unmasked_lo & {inputs_p {ready_i}};
endmodule

module bsg_circular_ptr (
	clk,
	reset_i,
	add_i,
	o,
	n_o
);
	parameter slots_p = -1;
	parameter max_add_p = -1;
	parameter ptr_width_lp = (slots_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(slots_p));
	input clk;
	input reset_i;
	input [$clog2(max_add_p + 1) - 1:0] add_i;
	output [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] o;
	output [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] n_o;
	reg [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] ptr_r;
	wire [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] ptr_n;
	wire [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] ptr_nowrap;
	wire [ptr_width_lp:0] ptr_wrap;
	assign o = ptr_r;
	assign n_o = ptr_n;
	always @(posedge clk)
		if (reset_i)
			ptr_r <= 0;
		else
			ptr_r <= ptr_n;
	generate
		if (slots_p == 1) begin
			assign ptr_n = 1'b0;
			wire ignore = |add_i;
		end
		else if ((1 << $clog2(slots_p)) == slots_p) if (max_add_p == 1) begin
			wire [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] ptr_r_p1 = ptr_r + 1'b1;
			assign ptr_n = (add_i ? ptr_r_p1 : ptr_r);
		end
		else begin
			function automatic [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_7EC17;
				input reg [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] inp;
				sv2v_cast_7EC17 = inp;
			endfunction
			assign ptr_n = sv2v_cast_7EC17(ptr_r + add_i);
		end
		else begin : notpow2
			function automatic [ptr_width_lp:0] sv2v_cast_AB5D9;
				input reg [ptr_width_lp:0] inp;
				sv2v_cast_AB5D9 = inp;
			endfunction
			assign ptr_wrap = sv2v_cast_AB5D9(({1'b0, ptr_r} - slots_p) + add_i);
			assign ptr_nowrap = ptr_r + add_i;
			assign ptr_n = (~ptr_wrap[ptr_width_lp] ? ptr_wrap[0+:ptr_width_lp] : ptr_nowrap);
			always @(*)
				;
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
