module bsg_counter_clear_up (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	clear_i,
	up_i,
	count_o
);
	parameter max_val_p = -1;
	parameter init_val_p = 1'sbx;
	parameter ptr_width_lp = ((max_val_p + 1) == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(max_val_p + 1));
	parameter disable_overflow_warning_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input clear_i;
	input up_i;
	output reg [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] count_o;
	function automatic [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_7EC17;
		input reg [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_7EC17 = inp;
	endfunction
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i)
			count_o <= init_val_p;
		else
			count_o <= (clear_i ? sv2v_cast_7EC17(up_i) : count_o + sv2v_cast_7EC17(up_i));
	always @(negedge clk_i)
		if ((((count_o == sv2v_cast_7EC17(max_val_p)) && up_i) && (reset_i === 0)) && !disable_overflow_warning_p)
			$display("%m error: counter overflow at time %t", $time);
endmodule
module bsg_counter_set_down (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	set_i,
	val_i,
	down_i,
	count_r_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter init_val_p = 1'sb0;
	parameter set_and_down_exclusive_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input set_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] val_i;
	input down_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] count_r_o;
	reg [width_p - 1:0] ctr_r;
	reg [width_p - 1:0] ctr_n;
	function automatic [width_p - 1:0] sv2v_cast_89401;
		input reg [width_p - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_89401 = inp;
	endfunction
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i)
			ctr_r <= sv2v_cast_89401(init_val_p);
		else
			ctr_r <= ctr_n;
	generate
		if (set_and_down_exclusive_p) begin : excl
			always @(*) begin
				ctr_n = ctr_r;
				if (set_i)
					ctr_n = val_i;
				else if (down_i)
					ctr_n = ctr_n - 1;
			end
		end
		else begin : non_excl
			always @(*) begin
				ctr_n = ctr_r;
				if (set_i)
					ctr_n = val_i;
				if (down_i)
					ctr_n = ctr_n - 1;
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	assign count_r_o = ctr_r;
	always @(negedge clk_i) begin
		if ((!reset_i && down_i) && (ctr_n == {width_p {1'sb1}}))
			$display("%m error: counter underflow at time %t", $time);
		if (((~reset_i & set_and_down_exclusive_p) & set_i) & down_i)
			$display("%m error: set and down non-exclusive at time %t", $time);
	end
endmodule
module bsg_counter_set_en (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	set_i,
	en_i,
	val_i,
	count_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_max_val_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_max_val_p - 1:0] max_val_p = "inv";
	parameter lg_max_val_lp = $clog2(max_val_p + 1);
	parameter reset_val_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input set_i;
	input en_i;
	input [lg_max_val_lp - 1:0] val_i;
	output reg [lg_max_val_lp - 1:0] count_o;
	function automatic [lg_max_val_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_516D0;
		input reg [lg_max_val_lp - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_516D0 = inp;
	endfunction
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i)
			count_o <= sv2v_cast_516D0(reset_val_p);
		else if (set_i)
			count_o <= val_i;
		else if (en_i)
			count_o <= count_o + 1'b1;
endmodule
module bsg_counter_up_down (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	up_i,
	down_i,
	count_o
);
	parameter max_val_p = -1;
	parameter init_val_p = -1;
	parameter max_step_p = -1;
	parameter step_width_lp = $clog2(max_step_p + 1);
	parameter ptr_width_lp = $clog2(max_val_p + 1);
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [step_width_lp - 1:0] up_i;
	input [step_width_lp - 1:0] down_i;
	output reg [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] count_o;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i)
			count_o <= init_val_p;
		else
			count_o <= (count_o - down_i) + up_i;
	always @(negedge clk_i) begin
		if (((count_o == max_val_p) & up_i) & (reset_i === 1'b0))
			$display("%m error: counter overflow at time %t", $time);
		if (((count_o == 0) & down_i) & (reset_i === 1'b0))
			$display("%m error: counter underflow at time %t", $time);
	end
endmodule
module bsg_counter_up_down_variable (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	up_i,
	down_i,
	count_o
);
	parameter max_val_p = -1;
	parameter init_val_p = -1;
	parameter max_step_p = -1;
	parameter step_width_lp = $clog2(max_step_p + 1);
	parameter ptr_width_lp = $clog2(max_val_p + 1);
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [step_width_lp - 1:0] up_i;
	input [step_width_lp - 1:0] down_i;
	output reg [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] count_o;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i)
			count_o <= init_val_p;
		else
			count_o <= (count_o - down_i) + up_i;
	always @(posedge clk_i) begin
		if (((count_o == max_val_p) & up_i) & (reset_i === 0))
			$display("%m error: counter overflow at time %t", $time);
		if (((count_o == 0) & down_i) & (reset_i === 0))
			$display("%m error: counter underflow at time %t", $time);
	end
endmodule
module bsg_crossbar_o_by_i (
	i,
	sel_oi_one_hot_i,
	o
);
	parameter i_els_p = -1;
	parameter o_els_p = -1;
	parameter width_p = -1;
	input [(i_els_p * width_p) - 1:0] i;
	input [(o_els_p * i_els_p) - 1:0] sel_oi_one_hot_i;
	output [(o_els_p * width_p) - 1:0] o;
	genvar lineout;
	generate
		for (lineout = 0; lineout < o_els_p; lineout = lineout + 1) bsg_mux_one_hot #(
			._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
			.width_p(width_p),
			.els_p(i_els_p)
		) mux_one_hot(
			.data_i(i),
			.sel_one_hot_i(sel_oi_one_hot_i[lineout * i_els_p+:i_els_p]),
			.data_o(o[lineout * width_p+:width_p])
		);
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_cycle_counter (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	ctr_r_o
);
	parameter width_p = 32;
	parameter init_val_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	output reg [width_p - 1:0] ctr_r_o;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i)
			ctr_r_o <= init_val_p;
		else
			ctr_r_o <= ctr_r_o + 1;
endmodule
module bsg_decode (
	i,
	o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_num_out_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_num_out_p - 1:0] num_out_p = "inv";
	input [(num_out_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(num_out_p)) - 1:0] i;
	output wire [num_out_p - 1:0] o;
	generate
		if (num_out_p == 1) begin
			wire unused = i;
			assign o = 1'b1;
		end
		else begin
			function automatic [num_out_p - 1:0] sv2v_cast_4BA5D;
				input reg [num_out_p - 1:0] inp;
				sv2v_cast_4BA5D = inp;
			endfunction
			assign o = sv2v_cast_4BA5D(1'b1 << i);
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_decode_with_v (
	i,
	v_i,
	o
);
	parameter num_out_p = -1;
	input [(num_out_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(num_out_p)) - 1:0] i;
	input v_i;
	output [num_out_p - 1:0] o;
	wire [num_out_p - 1:0] lo;
	bsg_decode #(
		._sv2v_width_num_out_p(32),
		.num_out_p(num_out_p)
	) bd(
		.i(i),
		.o(lo)
	);
	assign o = {num_out_p {v_i}} & lo;
endmodule
module bsg_dff (
	clk_i,
	data_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter harden_p = 0;
	parameter strength_p = 1;
	input clk_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	reg [width_p - 1:0] data_r;
	assign data_o = data_r;
	always @(posedge clk_i) data_r <= data_i;
endmodule
module bsg_dff_en_bypass (
	clk_i,
	en_i,
	data_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter harden_p = 0;
	parameter strength_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input en_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] data_r;
	wire clk_i;
	wire en_i;
	bsg_dff_en #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
		.width_p(width_p),
		.harden_p(harden_p),
		.strength_p(strength_p)
	) dff(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.en_i(en_i),
		.data_i(data_i),
		.data_o(data_r)
	);
	assign data_o = (en_i ? data_i : data_r);
endmodule
module bsg_dff_chain (
	clk_i,
	data_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter num_stages_p = 1;
	input clk_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	generate
		if (num_stages_p == 0) begin : pass_through
			assign data_o = data_i;
		end
		else begin : chained
			wire [(num_stages_p >= 0 ? ((num_stages_p + 1) * width_p) - 1 : ((1 - num_stages_p) * width_p) + ((num_stages_p * width_p) - 1)):(num_stages_p >= 0 ? 0 : num_stages_p * width_p)] data_delayed;
			assign data_delayed[(num_stages_p >= 0 ? 0 : num_stages_p) * width_p+:width_p] = data_i;
			assign data_o = data_delayed[(num_stages_p >= 0 ? num_stages_p : num_stages_p - num_stages_p) * width_p+:width_p];
			genvar i;
			for (i = 1; i <= num_stages_p; i = i + 1) begin
				wire clk_i;
				bsg_dff #(.width_p(width_p)) ch_reg(
					.clk_i(clk_i),
					.data_i(data_delayed[(num_stages_p >= 0 ? i - 1 : num_stages_p - (i - 1)) * width_p+:width_p]),
					.data_o(data_delayed[(num_stages_p >= 0 ? i : num_stages_p - i) * width_p+:width_p])
				);
			end
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_dff_en (
	clk_i,
	data_i,
	en_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter harden_p = 1;
	parameter strength_p = 1;
	input clk_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input en_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	reg [width_p - 1:0] data_r;
	assign data_o = data_r;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (en_i)
			data_r <= data_i;
endmodule
module bsg_dff_reset (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	data_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter reset_val_p = 0;
	parameter harden_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	reg [width_p - 1:0] data_r;
	assign data_o = data_r;
	function automatic [width_p - 1:0] sv2v_cast_89401;
		input reg [width_p - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_89401 = inp;
	endfunction
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i)
			data_r <= sv2v_cast_89401(reset_val_p);
		else
			data_r <= data_i;
endmodule

	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	en_i,
	data_i,

	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";

	parameter harden_p = 0;
	input clk_i;

		input reg [width_p - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_89401 = inp;
	endfunction
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i)
			data_r <= sv2v_cast_89401(reset_val_p);
		else if (en_i)
			data_r <= data_i;
endmodule
module bsg_encode_one_hot (
	i,
	addr_o,
	v_o
);
	parameter width_p = 8;
	parameter lo_to_hi_p = 1;
	parameter debug_p = 0;
	input [width_p - 1:0] i;
	output [(width_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p)) - 1:0] addr_o;
	output v_o;
	localparam levels_lp = $clog2(width_p);
	localparam aligned_width_lp = 1 << $clog2(width_p);
	genvar level;
	genvar segment;
	wire [(levels_lp >= 0 ? ((levels_lp + 1) * aligned_width_lp) - 1 : ((1 - levels_lp) * aligned_width_lp) + ((levels_lp * aligned_width_lp) - 1)):(levels_lp >= 0 ? 0 : levels_lp * aligned_width_lp)] addr;
	wire [(levels_lp >= 0 ? ((levels_lp + 1) * aligned_width_lp) - 1 : ((1 - levels_lp) * aligned_width_lp) + ((levels_lp * aligned_width_lp) - 1)):(levels_lp >= 0 ? 0 : levels_lp * aligned_width_lp)] v;
	function automatic [aligned_width_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_9FB23;
		input reg [aligned_width_lp - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_9FB23 = inp;
	endfunction
	assign v[(levels_lp >= 0 ? 0 : levels_lp) * aligned_width_lp+:aligned_width_lp] = (lo_to_hi_p ? sv2v_cast_9FB23(i) : i << (aligned_width_lp - width_p));
	assign addr[(levels_lp >= 0 ? 0 : levels_lp) * aligned_width_lp+:aligned_width_lp] = {aligned_width_lp {1'sbx}};
	generate
		for (level = 1; level < (levels_lp + 1); level = level + 1) begin : rof
			localparam segments_lp = 2 ** (levels_lp - level);
			localparam segment_slot_lp = aligned_width_lp / segments_lp;
			localparam segment_width_lp = level;
			for (segment = 0; segment < segments_lp; segment = segment + 1) begin : rof1
				wire [1:0] vs = {v[((levels_lp >= 0 ? level - 1 : levels_lp - (level - 1)) * aligned_width_lp) + ((segment * segment_slot_lp) + (segment_slot_lp >> 1))], v[((levels_lp >= 0 ? level - 1 : levels_lp - (level - 1)) * aligned_width_lp) + (segment * segment_slot_lp)]};
				assign v[((levels_lp >= 0 ? level : levels_lp - level) * aligned_width_lp) + (segment * segment_slot_lp)] = |vs;
				if (level == 1) assign addr[((levels_lp >= 0 ? level : levels_lp - level) * aligned_width_lp) + (segment * segment_slot_lp)+:segment_width_lp] = vs[lo_to_hi_p];
				else begin : fi
					assign addr[((levels_lp >= 0 ? level : levels_lp - level) * aligned_width_lp) + (segment * segment_slot_lp)+:segment_width_lp] = {vs[lo_to_hi_p], addr[((levels_lp >= 0 ? level - 1 : levels_lp - (level - 1)) * aligned_width_lp) + (segment * segment_slot_lp)+:segment_width_lp - 1] | addr[((levels_lp >= 0 ? level - 1 : levels_lp - (level - 1)) * aligned_width_lp) + ((segment * segment_slot_lp) + (segment_slot_lp >> 1))+:segment_width_lp - 1]};
				end
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	wire v_o;
	assign v_o = v[(levels_lp >= 0 ? levels_lp : levels_lp - levels_lp) * aligned_width_lp];
	assign addr_o = (((i - 1) & i) == {((width_p >= 32 ? width_p : 32) >= width_p ? (width_p >= 32 ? width_p : 32) : width_p) {1'sb0}} ? addr[((levels_lp >= 0 ? levels_lp : levels_lp - levels_lp) * aligned_width_lp) + ((width_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p)) - 1)-:(width_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p))] : {(width_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p)) {1'bx}});
	generate
		if (debug_p) always @(addr_o or v_o) begin
			#(1) begin : sv2v_autoblock_11
				integer k;
				for (k = 0; k <= $clog2(width_p); k = k + 1)
					$display("%b %b", addr[(levels_lp >= 0 ? k : levels_lp - k) * aligned_width_lp+:aligned_width_lp], v[(levels_lp >= 0 ? k : levels_lp - k) * aligned_width_lp+:aligned_width_lp]);
			end
			$display("addr_o=%b v_o=%b", addr_o, v_o);
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_expand_bitmask (
	i,
	o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_in_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_in_width_p - 1:0] in_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_expand_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_expand_p - 1:0] expand_p = "inv";
	input [in_width_p - 1:0] i;
	output reg [(in_width_p * expand_p) - 1:0] o;
	always @(*) begin : sv2v_autoblock_12
		integer k;
		for (k = 0; k < in_width_p; k = k + 1)
			o[expand_p * k+:expand_p] = {expand_p {i[k]}};
	end
endmodule
module bsg_hash_bank (
	i,
	bank_o,
	index_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_banks_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_banks_p - 1:0] banks_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter index_width_lp = $clog2((((2 ** width_p) + banks_p) - 1) / banks_p);
	parameter lg_banks_lp = (banks_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(banks_p));
	parameter debug_lp = 0;
	input [width_p - 1:0] i;
	output [lg_banks_lp - 1:0] bank_o;
	output [index_width_lp - 1:0] index_o;
	genvar j;
	generate
		if (banks_p == 1) begin : hash1
			assign index_o = i;
			assign bank_o = 1'b0;
		end
		else if (banks_p == 2) begin : hash2
			assign bank_o = i[width_p - 1];
			assign index_o = i[width_p - 2:0];
		end
		else if (~banks_p[0]) begin : hashpow2
			assign bank_o[0] = i[width_p - 1];
			bsg_hash_bank #(
				._sv2v_width_banks_p(_sv2v_width_banks_p),
				.banks_p(banks_p >> 1),
				._sv2v_width_width_p((_sv2v_width_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_width_p : 32)),
				.width_p(width_p - 1)
			) bhb(
				.i(i[width_p - 2:0]),
				.bank_o(bank_o[lg_banks_lp - 1:1]),
				.index_o(index_o)
			);
		end
		else if ((banks_p & (banks_p + 1)) == 0) begin : hash3
			if ((width_p % lg_banks_lp) != 0) begin : odd
				wire _unused;
				bsg_hash_bank #(
					._sv2v_width_banks_p(_sv2v_width_banks_p),
					.banks_p(banks_p),
					._sv2v_width_width_p((_sv2v_width_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_width_p : 32)),
					.width_p(width_p + 1)
				) hf(
					.i({i, 1'b0}),
					.bank_o(bank_o),
					.index_o({index_o, _unused})
				);
			end
			else begin : even
				localparam frac_width_lp = width_p / lg_banks_lp;
				wire [(lg_banks_lp * frac_width_lp) - 1:0] unzippered;
				wire [frac_width_lp - 1:0] one_one;
				bsg_reduce_segmented #(
					._sv2v_width_segments_p((_sv2v_width_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_width_p : 32)),
					.segments_p(frac_width_lp),
					._sv2v_width_segment_width_p(32),
					.segment_width_p(lg_banks_lp),
					.and_p(1'b1)
				) brs(
					.i(i),
					.o(one_one)
				);
				bsg_transpose #(
					._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
					.width_p(lg_banks_lp),
					._sv2v_width_els_p((_sv2v_width_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_width_p : 32)),
					.els_p(frac_width_lp)
				) unzip(
					.i(i),
					.o(unzippered)
				);
				wire [frac_width_lp - 1:0] one_one_and_scan;
				bsg_scan #(
					.width_p(frac_width_lp),
					.and_p(1)
				) scan(
					.i(one_one),
					.o(one_one_and_scan)
				);
				wire [frac_width_lp - 1:0] not_one_one_and_scan = ~one_one_and_scan;
				wire [frac_width_lp - 1:0] shifty;
				if (frac_width_lp > 1) assign shifty = {1'b1, one_one_and_scan[frac_width_lp - 1:1]};
				else assign shifty = 1'b1;
				wire [frac_width_lp - 1:0] border = not_one_one_and_scan & shifty;
				wire [(lg_banks_lp * frac_width_lp) - 1:0] bits;
				for (j = 1; j < lg_banks_lp; j = j + 1) begin : rof2
					assign bits[j * frac_width_lp+:frac_width_lp] = unzippered[j * frac_width_lp+:frac_width_lp] & ~(border | one_one_and_scan);
				end
				assign bits[0+:frac_width_lp] = one_one_and_scan | ((unzippered[0+:frac_width_lp] & ~one_one_and_scan) & ~border);
				wire [width_p - 1:0] transpose_lo;
				bsg_transpose #(
					._sv2v_width_els_p(32),
					.els_p(lg_banks_lp),
					._sv2v_width_width_p((_sv2v_width_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_width_p : 32)),
					.width_p(frac_width_lp)
				) zip(
					.i(bits),
					.o(transpose_lo)
				);
				assign index_o = transpose_lo[index_width_lp - 1:0];
				for (j = 0; j < lg_banks_lp; j = j + 1) begin : rof1
					assign bank_o[j] = |(border & unzippered[j * frac_width_lp+:frac_width_lp]);
				end
			end
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_hash_bank_reverse (
	index_i,
	bank_i,
	o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_banks_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_banks_p - 1:0] banks_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter index_width_lp = $clog2((((2 ** width_p) + banks_p) - 1) / banks_p);
	parameter lg_banks_lp = (banks_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(banks_p));
	parameter debug_lp = 0;
	input [index_width_lp - 1:0] index_i;
	input [lg_banks_lp - 1:0] bank_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] o;
	generate
		if (banks_p == 1) begin : hash1
			assign o = index_i;
		end
		else if (banks_p == 2) begin : hash2
			assign o = {bank_i, index_i};
		end
		else if (~banks_p[0]) begin : hashpow2
			assign o[width_p - 1] = bank_i[0];
			bsg_hash_bank_reverse #(
				._sv2v_width_banks_p(_sv2v_width_banks_p),
				.banks_p(banks_p >> 1),
				._sv2v_width_width_p((_sv2v_width_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_width_p : 32)),
				.width_p(width_p - 1)
			) bhbr(
				.index_i(index_i[index_width_lp - 1:0]),
				.bank_i(bank_i[lg_banks_lp - 1:1]),
				.o(o[width_p - 2:0])
			);
		end
		else if ((banks_p & (banks_p + 1)) == 0) begin : hash3
			if (width_p % lg_banks_lp) begin : odd
				wire _unused;
				bsg_hash_bank_reverse #(
					._sv2v_width_banks_p(_sv2v_width_banks_p),
					.banks_p(banks_p),
					._sv2v_width_width_p((_sv2v_width_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_width_p : 32)),
					.width_p(width_p + 1)
				) rhf(
					.index_i({index_i, 1'b0}),
					.bank_i(bank_i),
					.o({o[width_p - 1:0], _unused})
				);
			end
			else begin : even
				localparam frac_width_lp = width_p / lg_banks_lp;
				wire [(lg_banks_lp * frac_width_lp) - 1:0] unzippered;
				function automatic [width_p - 1:0] sv2v_cast_89401;
					input reg [width_p - 1:0] inp;
					sv2v_cast_89401 = inp;
				endfunction
				wire [width_p - 1:0] index_i_ext = sv2v_cast_89401(index_i);
				bsg_transpose #(
					._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
					.width_p(lg_banks_lp),
					._sv2v_width_els_p((_sv2v_width_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_width_p : 32)),
					.els_p(frac_width_lp)
				) unzip(
					.i(index_i_ext),
					.o(unzippered)
				);
				genvar j;
				wire [frac_width_lp - 1:0] zero_pair;
				bsg_reduce_segmented #(
					._sv2v_width_segments_p((_sv2v_width_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_width_p : 32)),
					.segments_p(frac_width_lp),
					._sv2v_width_segment_width_p(32),
					.segment_width_p(lg_banks_lp),
					.nor_p(1)
				) brs(
					.i(index_i_ext),
					.o(zero_pair)
				);
				wire [frac_width_lp - 1:0] zero_pair_or_scan;
				bsg_scan #(
					.width_p(frac_width_lp),
					.or_p(1)
				) scan(
					.i(zero_pair),
					.o(zero_pair_or_scan)
				);
				wire [frac_width_lp - 1:0] first_one;
				if (frac_width_lp > 1) assign first_one = zero_pair_or_scan & ~{1'b0, zero_pair_or_scan[frac_width_lp - 1:1]};
				else assign first_one = zero_pair_or_scan;
				wire [(lg_banks_lp * frac_width_lp) - 1:0] bits;
				for (j = 0; j < lg_banks_lp; j = j + 1) begin : rof2
					assign bits[j * frac_width_lp+:frac_width_lp] = (((zero_pair_or_scan & ~first_one) & unzippered[j * frac_width_lp+:frac_width_lp]) | (first_one & {frac_width_lp {bank_i[j]}})) | ~zero_pair_or_scan;
				end
				wire [width_p - 1:0] transpose_lo;
				bsg_transpose #(
					._sv2v_width_els_p(32),
					.els_p(lg_banks_lp),
					._sv2v_width_width_p((_sv2v_width_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_width_p : 32)),
					.width_p(frac_width_lp)
				) zip(
					.i(bits),
					.o(transpose_lo)
				);
				assign o = transpose_lo[width_p - 1:0];
			end
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_lfsr (
	clk,
	reset_i,
	yumi_i,
	o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter init_val_p = 1;
	parameter xor_mask_p = 0;
	input clk;
	input reset_i;
	input yumi_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] o;
	reg [width_p - 1:0] o_r;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] o_n;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] xor_mask;
	assign o = o_r;
	generate
		if (xor_mask_p == 0) begin : automask
			case (width_p)
				32: assign xor_mask = ((33'sd2147483648 | 536870912) | 67108864) | 33554432;
				60: assign xor_mask = 61'sd576460752303423488 | 60'sd288230376151711744;
				64: assign xor_mask = ((65'sd9223372036854775808 | 64'sd4611686018427387904) | 62'sd1152921504606846976) | 61'sd576460752303423488;
				default: ;
			endcase
		end
		else begin : fi
			assign xor_mask = xor_mask_p;
		end
	endgenerate
	function automatic [width_p - 1:0] sv2v_cast_89401;
		input reg [width_p - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_89401 = inp;
	endfunction
	always @(posedge clk)
		if (reset_i)
			o_r <= sv2v_cast_89401(init_val_p);
		else if (yumi_i)
			o_r <= o_n;
	assign o_n = (o_r >> 1) ^ ({width_p {o_r[0]}} & xor_mask);
endmodule
module bsg_lru_pseudo_tree_decode (
	way_id_i,
	data_o,
	mask_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_ways_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_ways_p - 1:0] ways_p = "inv";
	localparam lg_ways_lp = (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p));
	input [lg_ways_lp - 1:0] way_id_i;
	output wire [ways_p - 2:0] data_o;
	output wire [ways_p - 2:0] mask_o;
	genvar i;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < (ways_p - 1); i = i + 1) begin : rof
			if (i == 0) begin : fi
				assign mask_o[i] = 1'b1;
			end
			else if ((i % 2) == 1) begin : fi
				assign mask_o[i] = mask_o[(i - 1) / 2] & ~way_id_i[(lg_ways_lp - ((i + 2) == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(i + 2))) + 1];
			end
			else begin : fi
				assign mask_o[i] = mask_o[(i - 2) / 2] & way_id_i[(lg_ways_lp - ((i + 2) == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(i + 2))) + 1];
			end
			assign data_o[i] = mask_o[i] & ~way_id_i[lg_ways_lp - ((i + 2) == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(i + 2))];
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_lru_pseudo_tree_encode (
	lru_i,
	way_id_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_ways_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_ways_p - 1:0] ways_p = "inv";
	parameter lg_ways_lp = (ways_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(ways_p));
	input [ways_p - 2:0] lru_i;
	output wire [lg_ways_lp - 1:0] way_id_o;
	generate
		genvar i;
		for (i = 0; i < lg_ways_lp; i = i + 1) begin : rank
			if (i == 0) begin : z
				assign way_id_o[lg_ways_lp - 1] = lru_i[0];
			end
			else begin : nz
				bsg_mux #(
					._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
					.width_p(1),
					.els_p(2 ** i)
				) mux(
					.data_i(lru_i[(2 ** i) - 1+:2 ** i]),
					.sel_i(way_id_o[lg_ways_lp - 1-:i]),
					.data_o(way_id_o[(lg_ways_lp - 1) - i])
				);
			end
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_mux (
	data_i,
	sel_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter els_p = 1;
	parameter harden_p = 0;
	parameter balanced_p = 0;
	parameter lg_els_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	input [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_i;
	input [lg_els_lp - 1:0] sel_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	generate
		if (els_p == 1) begin
			assign data_o = data_i;
			wire unused = sel_i;
		end
		else assign data_o = data_i[sel_i * width_p+:width_p];
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_mux_bitwise (
	data0_i,
	data1_i,
	sel_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	input [width_p - 1:0] data0_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data1_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] sel_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	bsg_mux_segmented #(
		._sv2v_width_segments_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
		.segments_p(width_p),
		._sv2v_width_segment_width_p(32),
		.segment_width_p(1)
	) mux_segmented(
		.data0_i(data0_i),
		.data1_i(data1_i),
		.sel_i(sel_i),
		.data_o(data_o)
	);
endmodule
module bsg_mux_butterfly (
	data_i,
	sel_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_els_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_els_p - 1:0] els_p = "inv";
	localparam lg_els_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	input [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_i;
	input [lg_els_lp - 1:0] sel_i;
	output wire [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_o;
	wire [(lg_els_lp >= 0 ? ((lg_els_lp + 1) * (els_p * width_p)) - 1 : ((1 - lg_els_lp) * (els_p * width_p)) + ((lg_els_lp * (els_p * width_p)) - 1)):(lg_els_lp >= 0 ? 0 : lg_els_lp * (els_p * width_p))] data_stage;
	assign data_stage[(lg_els_lp >= 0 ? 0 : lg_els_lp) * (els_p * width_p)+:els_p * width_p] = data_i;
	generate
		genvar i;
		for (i = 0; i < lg_els_lp; i = i + 1) begin : mux_stage
			genvar j;
			for (j = 0; j < (els_p / (2 ** (i + 1))); j = j + 1) begin : mux_swap
				bsg_swap #(
					._sv2v_width_width_p((_sv2v_width_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_width_p : 32)),
					.width_p(width_p * (2 ** i))
				) swap_inst(
					.data_i(data_stage[((lg_els_lp >= 0 ? i : lg_els_lp - i) * (els_p * width_p)) + (((2 * width_p) * (2 ** i)) * j)+:(2 * width_p) * (2 ** i)]),
					.swap_i(sel_i[i]),
					.data_o(data_stage[((lg_els_lp >= 0 ? i + 1 : lg_els_lp - (i + 1)) * (els_p * width_p)) + (((2 * width_p) * (2 ** i)) * j)+:(2 * width_p) * (2 ** i)])
				);
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	assign data_o = data_stage[(lg_els_lp >= 0 ? lg_els_lp : lg_els_lp - lg_els_lp) * (els_p * width_p)+:els_p * width_p];
endmodule
module bsg_mux_one_hot (
	data_i,
	sel_one_hot_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter els_p = 1;
	parameter harden_p = 1;
	input [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_i;
	input [els_p - 1:0] sel_one_hot_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	wire [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] data_masked;
	genvar i;
	genvar j;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < els_p; i = i + 1) begin : mask
			assign data_masked[i * width_p+:width_p] = data_i[i * width_p+:width_p] & {width_p {sel_one_hot_i[i]}};
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < width_p; i = i + 1) begin : reduce
			wire [els_p - 1:0] gather;
			for (j = 0; j < els_p; j = j + 1) begin : reduce2
				assign gather[j] = data_masked[(j * width_p) + i];
			end
			assign data_o[i] = |gather;
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_mux_segmented (
	data0_i,
	data1_i,
	sel_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_segments_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_segments_p - 1:0] segments_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_segment_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_segment_width_p - 1:0] segment_width_p = "inv";
	parameter data_width_lp = segments_p * segment_width_p;
	input [data_width_lp - 1:0] data0_i;
	input [data_width_lp - 1:0] data1_i;
	input [segments_p - 1:0] sel_i;
	output wire [data_width_lp - 1:0] data_o;
	genvar i;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < segments_p; i = i + 1) assign data_o[i * segment_width_p+:segment_width_p] = (sel_i[i] ? data1_i[i * segment_width_p+:segment_width_p] : data0_i[i * segment_width_p+:segment_width_p]);
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_muxi2_gatestack (
	i0,
	i1,
	i2,
	o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter harden_p = 1;
	input [width_p - 1:0] i0;
	input [width_p - 1:0] i1;
	input [width_p - 1:0] i2;
	output [width_p - 1:0] o;
	genvar j;
	generate
		for (j = 0; j < width_p; j = j + 1) assign o[j] = ~(i2[j] ? i1[j] : i0[j]);
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_nor3 (
	a_i,
	b_i,
	c_i,
	o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter harden_p = 1;
	input [width_p - 1:0] a_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] b_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] c_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] o;
	assign o = ~((a_i | b_i) | c_i);
endmodule
module bsg_nand (
	a_i,
	b_i,
	o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter harden_p = 1;
	input [width_p - 1:0] a_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] b_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] o;
	assign o = ~(a_i & b_i);
endmodule
module bsg_priority_encode (
	i,
	addr_o,
	v_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_lo_to_hi_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_lo_to_hi_p - 1:0] lo_to_hi_p = "inv";
	input [width_p - 1:0] i;
	output [(width_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p)) - 1:0] addr_o;
	output v_o;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] enc_lo;
	wire v_o;
	bsg_priority_encode_one_hot_out #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
		.width_p(width_p),
		._sv2v_width_lo_to_hi_p(_sv2v_width_lo_to_hi_p),
		.lo_to_hi_p(lo_to_hi_p)
	) a(
		.i(i),
		.o(enc_lo),
		.v_o(v_o)
	);
	bsg_encode_one_hot #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.lo_to_hi_p(lo_to_hi_p)
	) b(
		.i(enc_lo),
		.addr_o(addr_o),
		.v_o()
	);
endmodule
module bsg_priority_encode_one_hot_out (
	i,
	o,
	v_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_lo_to_hi_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_lo_to_hi_p - 1:0] lo_to_hi_p = "inv";
	input [width_p - 1:0] i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] o;
	output v_o;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] scan_lo;
	generate
		if (width_p == 1) assign o = i;
		else begin
			bsg_scan #(
				.width_p(width_p),
				.or_p(1),
				.lo_to_hi_p(lo_to_hi_p)
			) scan(
				.i(i),
				.o(scan_lo)
			);
			if (lo_to_hi_p) begin : fi1
				assign o = scan_lo & {~scan_lo[width_p - 2:0], 1'b1};
				wire v_o;
				assign v_o = scan_lo[width_p - 1];
			end
			else begin : fi1
				assign o = scan_lo & {1'b1, ~scan_lo[width_p - 1:1]};
				wire v_o;
				assign v_o = scan_lo[0];
			end
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_reduce (
	i,
	o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter xor_p = 0;
	parameter and_p = 0;
	parameter or_p = 0;
	parameter harden_p = 0;
	input [width_p - 1:0] i;
	output o;
	generate
		if (xor_p) begin
			wire o;
			assign o = ^i;
		end
		else if (and_p) begin
			wire o;
			assign o = &i;
		end
		else if (or_p) begin
			wire o;
			assign o = |i;
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_reduce_segmented (
	i,
	o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_segments_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_segments_p - 1:0] segments_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_segment_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_segment_width_p - 1:0] segment_width_p = "inv";
	parameter xor_p = 0;
	parameter and_p = 0;
	parameter or_p = 0;
	parameter nor_p = 0;
	input [(segments_p * segment_width_p) - 1:0] i;
	output [segments_p - 1:0] o;
	genvar j;
	generate
		for (j = 0; j < segments_p; j = j + 1) begin : rof2
			if (xor_p) assign o[j] = ^i[j * segment_width_p+:segment_width_p];
			else if (and_p) assign o[j] = &i[j * segment_width_p+:segment_width_p];
			else if (or_p) assign o[j] = |i[j * segment_width_p+:segment_width_p];
			else if (nor_p) assign o[j] = ~(|i[j * segment_width_p+:segment_width_p]);
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_rotate_left (
	data_i,
	rot_i,
	o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input [(width_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p)) - 1:0] rot_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] o;
	wire [(width_p * 3) - 1:0] temp = {2 {data_i}} << rot_i;
	assign o = temp[(width_p * 2) - 1:width_p];
endmodule
module bsg_rotate_right (
	data_i,
	rot_i,
	o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	input [(width_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p)) - 1:0] rot_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] o;
	wire [(width_p * 2) - 1:0] temp = {2 {data_i}} >> rot_i;
	assign o = temp[0+:width_p];
endmodule
module bsg_round_robin_arb (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	grants_en_i,
	reqs_i,
	grants_o,
	sel_one_hot_o,
	v_o,
	tag_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter inputs_p = -1;
	parameter lg_inputs_p = (inputs_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(inputs_p));
	parameter reset_on_sr_p = 1'b0;
	parameter hold_on_sr_p = 1'b0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input grants_en_i;
	input [inputs_p - 1:0] reqs_i;
	output wire [inputs_p - 1:0] grants_o;
	output wire [inputs_p - 1:0] sel_one_hot_o;
	output v_o;
	output reg [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] tag_o;
	input yumi_i;
	wire [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] last;
	reg [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] last_n;
	reg [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] last_r;
	reg hold_on_sr;
	wire reset_on_sr;
	generate
		if (inputs_p == 1) begin : inputs_1
			reg [0:0] sel_one_hot_n;
			function automatic [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] sv2v_cast_8141E;
				input reg [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] inp;
				sv2v_cast_8141E = inp;
			endfunction
			always @(*)
				casez ({last_r, reqs_i})
					2'bz0: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 1'b0;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					2'b01: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 1'b1;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					default: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 1'bx;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
				endcase
			assign sel_one_hot_o = sel_one_hot_n;
			assign grants_o = sel_one_hot_n & grants_en_i;
			if (hold_on_sr_p) always @(*)
				casez (last_r)
					1'b0: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 1'b1;
					default: hold_on_sr = 1'b0;
				endcase
			else begin : not_hold_on_sr_p
				always @(*) hold_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
			if (reset_on_sr_p) begin : reset_on_1
				assign reset_on_sr = reqs_i == 1'b1;
			end
			else begin : not_reset_on_sr_p
				assign reset_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		if (inputs_p == 2) begin : inputs_2
			reg [1:0] sel_one_hot_n;
			function automatic [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] sv2v_cast_8141E;
				input reg [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] inp;
				sv2v_cast_8141E = inp;
			endfunction
			always @(*)
				casez ({last_r, reqs_i})
					3'bz00: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 2'b00;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					3'b01z: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 2'b10;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					3'b001: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 2'b01;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					3'b1z1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 2'b01;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					3'b110: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 2'b10;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					default: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = {2 {1'bx}};
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
				endcase
			assign sel_one_hot_o = sel_one_hot_n;
			assign grants_o = sel_one_hot_n & {2 {grants_en_i}};
			if (hold_on_sr_p) always @(*)
				casez (last_r)
					1'b0: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 2'b01;
					default: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 2'b10;
				endcase
			else begin : not_hold_on_sr_p
				always @(*) hold_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
			if (reset_on_sr_p) begin : reset_on_2
				assign reset_on_sr = (reqs_i == 2'b01) | (reqs_i == 2'b10);
			end
			else begin : not_reset_on_sr_p
				assign reset_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		if (inputs_p == 3) begin : inputs_3
			reg [2:0] sel_one_hot_n;
			function automatic [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] sv2v_cast_8141E;
				input reg [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] inp;
				sv2v_cast_8141E = inp;
			endfunction
			always @(*)
				casez ({last_r, reqs_i})
					5'bzz000: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					5'b00z1z: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					5'b0010z: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					5'b00001: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					5'b011zz: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					5'b010z1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					5'b01010: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					5'b10zz1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					5'b10z10: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					5'b10100: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					default: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = {3 {1'bx}};
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
				endcase
			assign sel_one_hot_o = sel_one_hot_n;
			assign grants_o = sel_one_hot_n & {3 {grants_en_i}};
			if (hold_on_sr_p) always @(*)
				casez (last_r)
					2'b00: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 3'b010;
					2'b01: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 3'b001;
					2'b10: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 3'b100;
					default: hold_on_sr = 1'b0;
				endcase
			else begin : not_hold_on_sr_p

					4'b0111: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 16'b0000000010000000;
					4'b1000: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 16'b0000000001000000;
					4'b1001: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 16'b0000000000100000;
					4'b1010: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 16'b0000000000010000;
					4'b1011: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 16'b0000000000001000;
					4'b1100: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 16'b0000000000000100;
					4'b1101: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 16'b0000000000000010;
					4'b1110: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 16'b0000000000000001;
					default: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 16'b1000000000000000;
				endcase
			else begin : not_hold_on_sr_p
				always @(*) hold_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
			if (reset_on_sr_p) begin : reset_on_16
				assign reset_on_sr = (((((((((((((((reqs_i == 16'b0100000000000000) | (reqs_i == 16'b0010000000000000)) | (reqs_i == 16'b0001000000000000)) | (reqs_i == 16'b0000100000000000)) | (reqs_i == 16'b0000010000000000)) | (reqs_i == 16'b0000001000000000)) | (reqs_i == 16'b0000000100000000)) | (reqs_i == 16'b0000000010000000)) | (reqs_i == 16'b0000000001000000)) | (reqs_i == 16'b0000000000100000)) | (reqs_i == 16'b0000000000010000)) | (reqs_i == 16'b0000000000001000)) | (reqs_i == 16'b0000000000000100)) | (reqs_i == 16'b0000000000000010)) | (reqs_i == 16'b0000000000000001)) | (reqs_i == 16'b1000000000000000);
			end
			else begin : not_reset_on_sr_p
				assign reset_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	wire v_o;
	assign v_o = |reqs_i;
	generate
		if (inputs_p == 1) always @(*) last_r = 1'b0;
		else begin
			always @(*)
				if (hold_on_sr_p) begin : last_n_gen
					last_n = (hold_on_sr ? last_r : (yumi_i ? tag_o : last_r));
				end
				else if (reset_on_sr_p) begin : reset_on_last_n_gen
					last_n = (reset_on_sr ? inputs_p - 2 : (yumi_i ? tag_o : last_r));
				end
				else
					last_n = (yumi_i ? tag_o : last_r);
			function automatic [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] sv2v_cast_8141E;
				input reg [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] inp;
				sv2v_cast_8141E = inp;
			endfunction
			always @(posedge clk_i) last_r <= (reset_i ? sv2v_cast_8141E(0) : last_n);
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_scan (
	i,
	o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter xor_p = 0;
	parameter and_p = 0;
	parameter or_p = 0;
	parameter lo_to_hi_p = 0;
	parameter debug_p = 0;
	input [width_p - 1:0] i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] o;
	genvar j;
	wire [($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? (($clog2(width_p) + 1) * width_p) - 1 : ((1 - $clog2(width_p)) * width_p) + (($clog2(width_p) * width_p) - 1)):($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? 0 : $clog2(width_p) * width_p)] t;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] fill;
	generate
		if (debug_p) always @(o) begin
			#(1) begin : sv2v_autoblock_13
				integer k;
				for (k = 0; k <= $clog2(width_p); k = k + 1)
					$display("%b", t[($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? k : $clog2(width_p) - k) * width_p+:width_p]);
			end
			$display("i=%b, o=%b", i, o);
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		if (lo_to_hi_p) begin
			function automatic [width_p - 1:0] _sv2v_strm_6F079;
				input reg [width_p - 1:0] inp;
				reg [width_p - 1:0] _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_inp;
				reg [width_p - 1:0] _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_out;
				integer _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_idx;
				begin
					_sv2v_strm_1E0CB_inp = inp;
					for (_sv2v_strm_1E0CB_idx = 0; _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_idx <= (width_p - 1); _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_idx = _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_idx + 1)
						_sv2v_strm_1E0CB_out[(width_p - 1) - _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_idx-:1] = _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_inp[_sv2v_strm_1E0CB_idx+:1];
					if ((width_p % 1) > 0)
						_sv2v_strm_1E0CB_out[0+:width_p % 1] = _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_inp[_sv2v_strm_1E0CB_idx+:width_p % 1];
					_sv2v_strm_6F079 = (width_p <= width_p ? _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_out << (width_p - width_p) : _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_out >> (width_p - width_p));
				end
			endfunction
			assign t[($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? 0 : $clog2(width_p)) * width_p+:width_p] = _sv2v_strm_6F079(i);
		end
		else assign t[($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? 0 : $clog2(width_p)) * width_p+:width_p] = i;
	endgenerate
	generate
		if ((width_p == 4) & and_p) begin : scand4
			assign t[($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? $clog2(width_p) : $clog2(width_p) - $clog2(width_p)) * width_p+:width_p] = {t[(($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? 0 : $clog2(width_p)) * width_p) + 3], &t[(($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? 0 : $clog2(width_p)) * width_p) + 3-:2], &t[(($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? 0 : $clog2(width_p)) * width_p) + 3-:3], &t[(($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? 0 : $clog2(width_p)) * width_p) + 3-:4]};
		end
		else if ((width_p == 3) & and_p) begin : scand3
			assign t[($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? $clog2(width_p) : $clog2(width_p) - $clog2(width_p)) * width_p+:width_p] = {t[(($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? 0 : $clog2(width_p)) * width_p) + 2], &t[(($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? 0 : $clog2(width_p)) * width_p) + 2-:2], &t[(($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? 0 : $clog2(width_p)) * width_p) + 2-:3]};
		end
		else if ((width_p == 2) & and_p) begin : scand3
			assign t[($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? $clog2(width_p) : $clog2(width_p) - $clog2(width_p)) * width_p+:width_p] = {t[(($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? 0 : $clog2(width_p)) * width_p) + 1], &t[(($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? 0 : $clog2(width_p)) * width_p) + 1-:2]};
		end
		else begin : scanN
			for (j = 0; j < $clog2(width_p); j = j + 1) begin : row
				function automatic [width_p - 1:0] sv2v_cast_89401;
					input reg [width_p - 1:0] inp;
					sv2v_cast_89401 = inp;
				endfunction
				wire [width_p - 1:0] shifted = sv2v_cast_89401({fill, t[($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? j : $clog2(width_p) - j) * width_p+:width_p]} >> (1 << j));
				if (xor_p) begin
					assign fill = {width_p {1'b0}};
					assign t[($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? j + 1 : $clog2(width_p) - (j + 1)) * width_p+:width_p] = t[($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? j : $clog2(width_p) - j) * width_p+:width_p] ^ shifted;
				end
				else if (and_p) begin
					assign fill = {width_p {1'b1}};
					assign t[($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? j + 1 : $clog2(width_p) - (j + 1)) * width_p+:width_p] = t[($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? j : $clog2(width_p) - j) * width_p+:width_p] & shifted;
				end
				else if (or_p) begin
					assign fill = {width_p {1'b0}};
					assign t[($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? j + 1 : $clog2(width_p) - (j + 1)) * width_p+:width_p] = t[($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? j : $clog2(width_p) - j) * width_p+:width_p] | shifted;
				end
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		if (lo_to_hi_p) for (j = 0; j < width_p; j = j + 1) assign o[j] = t[(($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? $clog2(width_p) : $clog2(width_p) - $clog2(width_p)) * width_p) + ((width_p - 1) - j)];
		else assign o = t[($clog2(width_p) >= 0 ? $clog2(width_p) : $clog2(width_p) - $clog2(width_p)) * width_p+:width_p];
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_strobe (
	clk_i,
	reset_r_i,
	init_val_r_i,
	strobe_r_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter harden_p = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_r_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] init_val_r_i;
	output reg strobe_r_o;
	localparam debug_lp = 0;
	wire strobe_n;
	wire strobe_n_buf;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] S_r;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] S_n;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] S_n_n;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] C_n_prereset;
	wire [width_p - 2:0] C_r;
	wire [width_p - 2:0] C_n;
	wire new_val = reset_r_i | strobe_n;
	wire clk_i;
	bsg_dff #(
		.width_p(width_p - 1),
		.harden_p(harden_p),
		.strength_p(2)
	) C_reg(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.data_i(C_n),
		.data_o(C_r)
	);
	bsg_xnor #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
		.width_p(width_p),
		.harden_p(1)
	) xnor_S_n(
		.a_i(S_r),
		.b_i({C_r, 1'b1}),
		.o(S_n)
	);
	bsg_muxi2_gatestack #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
		.width_p(width_p),
		.harden_p(1)
	) muxi2_S_n(
		.i0(S_n),
		.i1(init_val_r_i),
		.i2({width_p {new_val}}),
		.o(S_n_n)
	);
	bsg_dff #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.harden_p(harden_p),
		.strength_p(4)
	) S_reg(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.data_i(S_n_n),
		.data_o(S_r)
	);
	bsg_nand #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
		.width_p(width_p),
		.harden_p(1)
	) nand_C_n(
		.a_i(S_r),
		.b_i({C_r, 1'b1}),
		.o(C_n_prereset)
	);
	bsg_nor3 #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p((_sv2v_width_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_width_p : 32)),
		.width_p(width_p - 1),
		.harden_p(1)
	) nor3_C_n(
		.a_i({width_p - 1 {strobe_n_buf}}),
		.b_i(C_n_prereset[0+:width_p - 1]),
		.c_i({width_p - 1 {reset_r_i}}),
		.o(C_n)
	);
	bsg_reduce #(
		.and_p(1),
		.harden_p(1),
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_width_p),
		.width_p(width_p)
	) andr(
		.i(S_r),
		.o(strobe_n)
	);
	bsg_buf #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(1)
	) strobe_buf_gate(
		.i(strobe_n),
		.o(strobe_n_buf)
	);
	always @(posedge clk_i) strobe_r_o <= strobe_n_buf;
	generate
		if (debug_lp) begin : debug
			always @(negedge clk_i)
				$display("%t (C=%b,S=%b) reset_r_i=%d new_val=%b init_val=%d val(C,S)=%b C^S=%b", $time, C_r, S_r, reset_r_i, new_val, init_val_r_i, (C_r << 1) + S_r, strobe_n);
		end
	endgenerate
	always @(negedge clk_i)
		;
endmodule
module bsg_swap (
	data_i,
	swap_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	input [(2 * width_p) - 1:0] data_i;
	input swap_i;
	output wire [(2 * width_p) - 1:0] data_o;
	assign data_o = (swap_i ? {data_i[0+:width_p], data_i[width_p+:width_p]} : {data_i[width_p+:width_p], data_i[0+:width_p]});
endmodule
module bsg_thermometer_count (
	i,
	o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	input [width_p - 1:0] i;
	output [$clog2(width_p + 1) - 1:0] o;
	generate
		if (width_p == 1) assign o = i;
		else if (width_p == 2) assign o = {i[1], i[0] & ~i[1]};
		else if (width_p == 3) assign o = {i[1], i[2] | (i[0] & ~i[1])};
		else if (width_p == 4) assign o = {i[3], ~i[3] & i[1], ^i};
		else begin : big
			wire [width_p:0] one_hot = ~{1'b0, i} & {i, 1'b1};
			bsg_encode_one_hot #(.width_p(width_p + 1)) encode_one_hot(
				.i(one_hot),
				.addr_o(o),
				.v_o()
			);
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_transpose (
	i,
	o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_els_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_els_p - 1:0] els_p = "inv";
	input [(els_p * width_p) - 1:0] i;
	output [(width_p * els_p) - 1:0] o;
	genvar x;
	genvar y;
	generate
		for (x = 0; x < els_p; x = x + 1) begin : rof
			for (y = 0; y < width_p; y = y + 1) begin : rof2
				assign o[(y * els_p) + x] = i[(x * width_p) + y];
			end
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule

(((S - N) + 1) * x_max_p) + ((N * x_max_p) - 1) : (((N - S) + 1) * x_max_p) + ((S * x_max_p) - 1)) >= (S >= N ? N * x_max_p : S * x_max_p) ? ((((S >= N ? (((S - N) + 1) * x_max_p) + ((N * x_max_p) - 1) : (((N - S) + 1) * x_max_p) + ((S * x_max_p) - 1)) - (S >= N ? N * x_max_p : S * x_max_p)) + 1) * nets_p) + (((S >= N ? N * x_max_p : S * x_max_p) * nets_p) - 1) : ((((S >= N ? N * x_max_p : S * x_max_p) - (S >= N ? (((S - N) + 1) * x_max_p) + ((N * x_max_p) - 1) : (((N - S) + 1) * x_max_p) + ((S * x_max_p) - 1))) + 1) * nets_p) + (((S >= N ? (((S - N) + 1) * x_max_p) + ((N * x_max_p) - 1) : (((N - S) + 1) * x_max_p) + ((S * x_max_p) - 1)) * nets_p) - 1)))) * width_p+:width_p] = outs_i[((S >= W ? (((y_max_p * x_max_p) * nets_p) * ((S - W) + 1)) + (W - 1) : (((y_max_p * x_max_p) * nets_p) * ((W - S) + 1)) + (S - 1)) >= (S >= W ? W : S) ? (((c * nets_p) + net) * (S >= W ? (S - W) + 1 : (W - S) + 1)) + (S >= W ? N : W - (N - S)) : (S >= W ? W : S) - (((((c * nets_p) + net) * (S >= W ? (S - W) + 1 : (W - S) + 1)) + (S >= W ? N : W - (N - S))) - (S >= W ? (((y_max_p * x_max_p) * nets_p) * ((S - W) + 1)) + (W - 1) : (((y_max_p * x_max_p) * nets_p) * ((W - S) + 1)) + (S - 1)))) * width_p+:width_p];
			end
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_noc_repeater_node (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	side_A_links_i,
	side_A_links_o,
	side_B_links_i,
	side_B_links_o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp = width_p + 2;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp - 1:0] side_A_links_i;
	output [bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp - 1:0] side_A_links_o;
	input [bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp - 1:0] side_B_links_i;
	output [bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp - 1:0] side_B_links_o;
	wire [(2 + width_p) - 1:0] links_A_cast_i;
	wire [(2 + width_p) - 1:0] links_B_cast_i;
	wire [(2 + width_p) - 1:0] links_A_cast_o;
	wire [(2 + width_p) - 1:0] links_B_cast_o;
	assign links_A_cast_i = side_A_links_i;
	assign links_B_cast_i = side_B_links_i;
	assign side_A_links_o = links_A_cast_o;
	assign side_B_links_o = links_B_cast_o;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	bsg_two_fifo #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(width_p)
	) A_to_B(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.v_i(links_A_cast_i[width_p + 1]),
		.data_i(links_A_cast_i[width_p - 1-:width_p]),
		.ready_o(links_A_cast_o[width_p]),
		.v_o(links_B_cast_o[width_p + 1]),
		.data_o(links_B_cast_o[width_p - 1-:width_p]),
		.yumi_i(links_B_cast_i[width_p] & links_B_cast_o[width_p + 1])
	);
	bsg_two_fifo #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(width_p)
	) B_to_A(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.v_i(links_B_cast_i[width_p + 1]),
		.data_i(links_B_cast_i[width_p - 1-:width_p]),
		.ready_o(links_B_cast_o[width_p]),
		.v_o(links_A_cast_o[width_p + 1]),
		.data_o(links_A_cast_o[width_p - 1-:width_p]),
		.yumi_i(links_A_cast_i[width_p] & links_A_cast_o[width_p + 1])
	);
endmodule
module bsg_wormhole_concentrator (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	links_i,
	links_o,
	concentrated_link_i,
	concentrated_link_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_flit_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_flit_width_p - 1:0] flit_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_len_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_len_width_p - 1:0] len_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_cid_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_cid_width_p - 1:0] cid_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_cord_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_cord_width_p - 1:0] cord_width_p = "inv";
	parameter num_in_p = 1;
	parameter debug_lp = 0;
	parameter link_width_lp = flit_width_p + 2;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [(num_in_p * link_width_lp) - 1:0] links_i;
	output [(num_in_p * link_width_lp) - 1:0] links_o;
	input [link_width_lp - 1:0] concentrated_link_i;
	output [link_width_lp - 1:0] concentrated_link_o;
	wire [(num_in_p * (2 + flit_width_p)) - 1:0] links_i_cast;
	wire [(num_in_p * (2 + flit_width_p)) - 1:0] links_o_cast;
	wire [(num_in_p * (2 + flit_width_p)) - 1:0] links_o_stubbed_v;
	wire [(num_in_p * (2 + flit_width_p)) - 1:0] links_o_stubbed_ready;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] concentrated_link_i_cast;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] concentrated_link_o_cast;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] concentrated_link_o_stubbed_v;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] concentrated_link_o_stubbed_ready;
	assign links_i_cast = links_i;
	assign links_o = links_o_cast;
	assign concentrated_link_i_cast = concentrated_link_i;
	assign concentrated_link_o = concentrated_link_o_cast;
	generate
		genvar i;
		for (i = 0; i < num_in_p; i = i + 1) begin : cast
			assign links_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p - 1)-:flit_width_p] = links_o_stubbed_ready[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p - 1)-:flit_width_p];
			assign links_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p + 1)] = links_o_stubbed_ready[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p + 1)];
			assign links_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + flit_width_p] = links_o_stubbed_v[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + flit_width_p];
		end
	endgenerate
	assign concentrated_link_o_cast[flit_width_p - 1-:flit_width_p] = concentrated_link_o_stubbed_ready[flit_width_p - 1-:flit_width_p];
	assign concentrated_link_o_cast[flit_width_p + 1] = concentrated_link_o_stubbed_ready[flit_width_p + 1];
	assign concentrated_link_o_cast[flit_width_p] = concentrated_link_o_stubbed_v[flit_width_p];
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	bsg_wormhole_concentrator_in #(
		._sv2v_width_flit_width_p(_sv2v_width_flit_width_p),
		.flit_width_p(flit_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_len_width_p(_sv2v_width_len_width_p),
		.len_width_p(len_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_cid_width_p(_sv2v_width_cid_width_p),
		.cid_width_p(cid_width_p),
		.num_in_p(num_in_p),
		._sv2v_width_cord_width_p(_sv2v_width_cord_width_p),
		.cord_width_p(cord_width_p),
		.debug_lp(debug_lp)
	) concentrator_in(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.links_i(links_i),
		.links_o(links_o_stubbed_v),
		.concentrated_link_i(concentrated_link_i),
		.concentrated_link_o(concentrated_link_o_stubbed_ready)
	);
	bsg_wormhole_concentrator_out #(
		._sv2v_width_flit_width_p(_sv2v_width_flit_width_p),
		.flit_width_p(flit_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_len_width_p(_sv2v_width_len_width_p),
		.len_width_p(len_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_cid_width_p(_sv2v_width_cid_width_p),
		.cid_width_p(cid_width_p),
		.num_in_p(num_in_p),
		._sv2v_width_cord_width_p(_sv2v_width_cord_width_p),
		.cord_width_p(cord_width_p),
		.debug_lp(debug_lp)
	) concentrator_out(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.links_i(links_i),
		.links_o(links_o_stubbed_ready),
		.concentrated_link_i(concentrated_link_i),
		.concentrated_link_o(concentrated_link_o_stubbed_v)
	);
endmodule
module bsg_wormhole_concentrator_in (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	links_i,
	links_o,
	concentrated_link_i,
	concentrated_link_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_flit_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_flit_width_p - 1:0] flit_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_len_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_len_width_p - 1:0] len_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_cid_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_cid_width_p - 1:0] cid_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_cord_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_cord_width_p - 1:0] cord_width_p = "inv";
	parameter num_in_p = 1;
	parameter debug_lp = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [((flit_width_p + 1) >= 0 ? (num_in_p * (flit_width_p + 2)) - 1 : (num_in_p * (1 - (flit_width_p + 1))) + flit_width_p):((flit_width_p + 1) >= 0 ? 0 : flit_width_p + 1)] links_i;
	output [((flit_width_p + 1) >= 0 ? (num_in_p * (flit_width_p + 2)) - 1 : (num_in_p * (1 - (flit_width_p + 1))) + flit_width_p):((flit_width_p + 1) >= 0 ? 0 : flit_width_p + 1)] links_o;
	input [flit_width_p + 1:0] concentrated_link_i;
	output [flit_width_p + 1:0] concentrated_link_o;
	wire [(num_in_p * (2 + flit_width_p)) - 1:0] links_i_cast;
	wire [(num_in_p * (2 + flit_width_p)) - 1:0] links_o_cast;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] concentrated_link_i_cast;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] concentrated_link_o_cast;
	assign links_i_cast = links_i;
	assign links_o = links_o_cast;
	assign concentrated_link_i_cast = concentrated_link_i;
	assign concentrated_link_o = concentrated_link_o_cast;
	genvar i;
	genvar j;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < num_in_p; i = i + 1) begin : stub
			assign links_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p + 1)] = 1'b0;
			assign links_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p - 1)-:flit_width_p] = 1'b0;
		end
	endgenerate
	assign concentrated_link_o_cast[flit_width_p] = 1'b0;
	wire [(num_in_p * flit_width_p) - 1:0] fifo_data_lo;
	wire [num_in_p - 1:0] fifo_valid_lo;
	wire [num_in_p - 1:0] releases;
	wire [num_in_p - 1:0] reqs;
	wire [num_in_p - 1:0] yumis;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < num_in_p; i = i + 1) begin : in_ch
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			bsg_two_fifo #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_flit_width_p),
				.width_p(flit_width_p)
			) twofer(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.ready_o(links_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + flit_width_p]),
				.data_i(links_i_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p - 1)-:flit_width_p]),
				.v_i(links_i_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p + 1)]),
				.v_o(fifo_valid_lo[i]),
				.data_o(fifo_data_lo[i * flit_width_p+:flit_width_p]),
				.yumi_i(yumis[i])
			);
			wire [((cid_width_p + len_width_p) + cord_width_p) - 1:0] concentrated_hdr;
			assign concentrated_hdr = fifo_data_lo[(i * flit_width_p) + (((cid_width_p + len_width_p) + cord_width_p) - 1)-:(cid_width_p + len_width_p) + cord_width_p];
			bsg_wormhole_router_input_control #(
				.output_dirs_p(1),
				.payload_len_bits_p(((len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)) >= cord_width_p ? ((len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)) - cord_width_p) + 1 : (cord_width_p - (len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1))) + 1))
			) wic(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.fifo_v_i(fifo_valid_lo[i]),
				.fifo_yumi_i(yumis[i]),
				.fifo_decoded_dest_i(1'b1),
				.fifo_payload_len_i(concentrated_hdr[len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)-:((len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)) >= cord_width_p ? ((len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)) - cord_width_p) + 1 : (cord_width_p - (len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1))) + 1)]),
				.reqs_o(reqs[i]),
				.release_o(releases[i]),
				.detected_header_o()
			);
		end
	endgenerate
	wire [num_in_p - 1:0] data_sel_lo;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	bsg_wormhole_router_output_control #(.input_dirs_p(num_in_p)) woc(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.reqs_i(reqs),
		.release_i(releases),
		.valid_i(fifo_valid_lo),
		.yumi_o(yumis),
		.ready_i(concentrated_link_i_cast[flit_width_p]),
		.valid_o(concentrated_link_o_cast[flit_width_p + 1]),
		.data_sel_o(data_sel_lo)
	);
	bsg_mux_one_hot #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_flit_width_p),
		.width_p(flit_width_p),
		.els_p(num_in_p)
	) data_mux(
		.data_i(fifo_data_lo),
		.sel_one_hot_i(data_sel_lo),
		.data_o(concentrated_link_o_cast[flit_width_p - 1-:flit_width_p])
	);
endmodule
module bsg_wormhole_concentrator_out (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	links_i,
	links_o,
	concentrated_link_i,
	concentrated_link_o
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_flit_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_flit_width_p - 1:0] flit_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_len_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_len_width_p - 1:0] len_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_cid_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_cid_width_p - 1:0] cid_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_cord_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_cord_width_p - 1:0] cord_width_p = "inv";
	parameter num_in_p = 1;
	parameter debug_lp = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [((flit_width_p + 1) >= 0 ? (num_in_p * (flit_width_p + 2)) - 1 : (num_in_p * (1 - (flit_width_p + 1))) + flit_width_p):((flit_width_p + 1) >= 0 ? 0 : flit_width_p + 1)] links_i;
	output [((flit_width_p + 1) >= 0 ? (num_in_p * (flit_width_p + 2)) - 1 : (num_in_p * (1 - (flit_width_p + 1))) + flit_width_p):((flit_width_p + 1) >= 0 ? 0 : flit_width_p + 1)] links_o;
	input [flit_width_p + 1:0] concentrated_link_i;
	output [flit_width_p + 1:0] concentrated_link_o;
	wire [(num_in_p * (2 + flit_width_p)) - 1:0] links_i_cast;
	wire [(num_in_p * (2 + flit_width_p)) - 1:0] links_o_cast;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] concentrated_link_i_cast;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] concentrated_link_o_cast;
	assign links_i_cast = links_i;
	assign links_o = links_o_cast;
	assign concentrated_link_i_cast = concentrated_link_i;
	assign concentrated_link_o = concentrated_link_o_cast;
	genvar i;
	genvar j;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < num_in_p; i = i + 1) begin : stub
			assign links_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + flit_width_p] = 1'b0;
		end
	endgenerate
	assign concentrated_link_o_cast[flit_width_p + 1] = 1'b0;
	assign concentrated_link_o_cast[flit_width_p - 1-:flit_width_p] = 1'b0;
	wire [flit_width_p - 1:0] concentrated_fifo_data_lo;
	wire concentrated_fifo_valid_lo;
	wire concentrated_releases;
	wire [num_in_p - 1:0] concentrated_reqs;
	wire [num_in_p - 1:0] concentrated_yumis;
	wire concentrated_any_yumi = |concentrated_yumis;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	bsg_two_fifo #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_flit_width_p),
		.width_p(flit_width_p)
	) concentrated_twofer(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.ready_o(concentrated_link_o_cast[flit_width_p]),
		.data_i(concentrated_link_i_cast[flit_width_p - 1-:flit_width_p]),
		.v_i(concentrated_link_i_cast[flit_width_p + 1]),
		.v_o(concentrated_fifo_valid_lo),
		.data_o(concentrated_fifo_data_lo),
		.yumi_i(concentrated_any_yumi)
	);
	wire [((cid_width_p + len_width_p) + cord_width_p) - 1:0] concentrated_hdr;
	assign concentrated_hdr = concentrated_fifo_data_lo[((cid_width_p + len_width_p) + cord_width_p) - 1:0];
	wire [num_in_p - 1:0] concentrated_decoded_dest_lo;
	bsg_decode #(
		._sv2v_width_num_out_p(32),
		.num_out_p(num_in_p)
	) concentrated_decoder(
		.i(concentrated_hdr[(cid_width_p + (len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1))) - (cid_width_p - 1)+:(num_in_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(num_in_p))]),
		.o(concentrated_decoded_dest_lo)
	);
	bsg_wormhole_router_input_control #(
		.output_dirs_p(num_in_p),
		.payload_len_bits_p(((len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)) >= cord_width_p ? ((len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)) - cord_width_p) + 1 : (cord_width_p - (len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1))) + 1))
	) concentrated_wic(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.fifo_v_i(concentrated_fifo_valid_lo),
		.fifo_yumi_i(concentrated_any_yumi),
		.fifo_decoded_dest_i(concentrated_decoded_dest_lo),
		.fifo_payload_len_i(concentrated_hdr[len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)-:((len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)) >= cord_width_p ? ((len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)) - cord_width_p) + 1 : (cord_width_p - (len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1))) + 1)]),
		.reqs_o(concentrated_reqs),
		.release_o(concentrated_releases),
		.detected_header_o()
	);
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < num_in_p; i = i + 1) begin : out_ch
			bsg_wormhole_router_output_control #(.input_dirs_p(1)) concentrated_woc(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.reqs_i(concentrated_reqs[i]),
				.release_i(concentrated_releases),
				.valid_i(concentrated_fifo_valid_lo),
				.yumi_o(concentrated_yumis[i]),
				.ready_i(links_i_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + flit_width_p]),
				.valid_o(links_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p + 1)]),
				.data_sel_o()
			);
			assign links_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p - 1)-:flit_width_p] = concentrated_fifo_data_lo;
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_wormhole_router (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	link_i,
	link_o,
	my_cord_i
);
	localparam [17:0] bsg_wormhole_router_pkg_StrictX = {{3'b011, 3'b101, 3'b111}, {3'b011, 3'b101, 3'b111}};
	localparam [17:0] X_AllowLoopBack = {{3'b100, 3'b010, 3'b000}, {3'b111, 3'b111, 3'b111}};
	localparam [49:0] StrictXY = {{5'b01111, 5'b10111, 5'b00011, 5'b00101, 5'b11111}, {5'b01001, 5'b10001, 5'b11011, 5'b11101, 5'b11111}};
	localparam [49:0] StrictYX = {{5'b01001, 5'b10001, 5'b11011, 5'b11101, 5'b11111}, {5'b01111, 5'b10111, 5'b00011, 5'b00101, 5'b11111}};
	localparam [49:0] XY_Allow_S = {{5'b00000, 5'b00000, 5'b10000, 5'b10000, 5'b00000}, {5'b00110, 5'b00000, 5'b00000, 5'b00000, 5'b00000}};
	localparam [49:0] XY_Allow_N = {{5'b00000, 5'b00000, 5'b01000, 5'b01000, 5'b00000}, {5'b00000, 5'b00110, 5'b00000, 5'b00000, 5'b00000}};
	localparam [49:0] YX_Allow_W = {{5'b00010, 5'b00010, 5'b00000, 5'b00000, 5'b00000}, {5'b00000, 5'b00000, 5'b00000, 5'b11000, 5'b00000}};
	localparam [49:0] YX_Allow_E = {{5'b00100, 5'b00100, 5'b00000, 5'b00000, 5'b00000}, {5'b00000, 5'b00000, 5'b11000, 5'b00000, 5'b00000}};
	localparam [17:0] StrictX = {{3'b011, 3'b101, 3'b111}, {3'b011, 3'b101, 3'b111}};
	localparam [49:0] bsg_wormhole_router_pkg_StrictXY = {{5'b01111, 5'b10111, 5'b00011, 5'b00101, 5'b11111}, {5'b01001, 5'b10001, 5'b11011, 5'b11101, 5'b11111}};
	parameter _sv2v_width_flit_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_flit_width_p - 1:0] flit_width_p = "inv";
	parameter dims_p = 2;
	parameter dirs_lp = (dims_p * 2) + 1;
	parameter cord_dims_p = dims_p;
	parameter signed [(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? ((cord_dims_p + 1) * 32) - 1 : ((1 - cord_dims_p) * 32) + ((cord_dims_p * 32) - 1)):(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? 0 : cord_dims_p * 32)] cord_markers_pos_p = {32'sd5, 32'sd4, 32'sd0};
	parameter [((2 * dirs_lp) * dirs_lp) - 1:0] routing_matrix_p = (dims_p == 2 ? StrictXY : StrictX);
	parameter reverse_order_p = 0;
	parameter _sv2v_width_len_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_len_width_p - 1:0] len_width_p = "inv";
	parameter debug_lp = 0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [((flit_width_p + 1) >= 0 ? (dirs_lp * (flit_width_p + 2)) - 1 : (dirs_lp * (1 - (flit_width_p + 1))) + flit_width_p):((flit_width_p + 1) >= 0 ? 0 : flit_width_p + 1)] link_i;
	output [((flit_width_p + 1) >= 0 ? (dirs_lp * (flit_width_p + 2)) - 1 : (dirs_lp * (1 - (flit_width_p + 1))) + flit_width_p):((flit_width_p + 1) >= 0 ? 0 : flit_width_p + 1)] link_o;
	input [cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1:0] my_cord_i;
	localparam input_dirs_lp = dirs_lp;
	localparam output_dirs_lp = dirs_lp;
	wire [(dirs_lp * dirs_lp) - 1:0] matrix_out_in_transpose;
	bsg_transpose #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(dirs_lp),
		._sv2v_width_els_p(32),
		.els_p(dirs_lp)
	) tr(
		.i(routing_matrix_p[0+:dirs_lp * dirs_lp]),
		.o(matrix_out_in_transpose)
	);
	always @(negedge reset_i)
		;
	wire [(input_dirs_lp * flit_width_p) - 1:0] fifo_data_lo;
	wire [input_dirs_lp - 1:0] fifo_valid_lo;
	wire [dirs_lp - 1:0] releases;
	wire [(dirs_lp * dirs_lp) - 1:0] reqs;
	wire [(dirs_lp * dirs_lp) - 1:0] reqs_transpose;
	wire [(dirs_lp * dirs_lp) - 1:0] yumis;
	wire [(dirs_lp * dirs_lp) - 1:0] yumis_transpose;
	wire [(dirs_lp * (2 + flit_width_p)) - 1:0] link_i_cast;
	wire [(dirs_lp * (2 + flit_width_p)) - 1:0] link_o_cast;
	assign link_i_cast = link_i;
	assign link_o = link_o_cast;
	genvar i;
	genvar j;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < input_dirs_lp; i = i + 1) begin : in_ch
			localparam output_dirs_sparse_lp = (dirs_lp < 65 ? 1'b0 : {dirs_lp {1'sbx}}) + (((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 0) & 1'b1) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 1) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 2) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 3) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 4) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 5) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 6) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 7) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 8) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 9) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 10) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 11) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 12) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 13) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 14) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 15) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 16) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 17) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 18) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 19) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 20) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 21) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 22) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 23) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * 27) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 28) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 29) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 30) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 31) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 32) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 33) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 34) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 35) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 36) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 41) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 42) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 43) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * 47) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 48) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 49) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 50) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 51) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 52) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 53) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 61) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 62) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 63) & 1'b1));
			wire [output_dirs_lp - 1:0] decoded_dest_lo;
			wire [output_dirs_sparse_lp - 1:0] decoded_dest_sparse_lo;
			wire [output_dirs_sparse_lp - 1:0] reqs_lo;
			wire [output_dirs_sparse_lp - 1:0] yumis_li;
			bsg_concentrate_static #(
				._sv2v_width_pattern_els_p(dirs_lp),
				.pattern_els_p(routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp])
			) conc(
				.i(yumis_transpose[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp]),
				.o(yumis_li)
			);
			wire any_yumi = |yumis_li;
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			bsg_two_fifo #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_flit_width_p),
				.width_p(flit_width_p)
			) twofer(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.ready_o(link_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + flit_width_p]),
				.data_i(link_i_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p - 1)-:flit_width_p]),
				.v_i(link_i_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p + 1)]),
				.v_o(fifo_valid_lo[i]),
				.data_o(fifo_data_lo[i * flit_width_p+:flit_width_p]),
				.yumi_i(any_yumi)
			);
			wire [(len_width_p + cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32]) - 1:0] hdr;
			assign hdr = fifo_data_lo[(i * flit_width_p) + ((len_width_p + cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32]) - 1)-:len_width_p + cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32]];
			if (debug_lp) begin
				reg release_r;
				always @(posedge clk_i) release_r <= releases[i];
				always @(negedge clk_i) begin
					if (releases[i] & ~release_r)
						$display("%m in  ch%2d: packet finished last cycle", i);
					if (((reset_i === 1'b0) && link_i_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p + 1)]) && !link_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + flit_width_p])
						$display("%m in  ch%2d: nacking   packet %h", i, link_i_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p - 1)-:flit_width_p]);
					else if (((reset_i === 1'b0) && link_i_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p + 1)]) && link_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + flit_width_p])
						$display("%m in  ch%2d: accepting packet %h", i, link_i_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p - 1)-:flit_width_p]);
					if ((reset_i === 1'b0) && any_yumi)
						if (reqs_lo)
							$display("%m in  ch%2d: dequeing  header %h (outch=%b,len=%b,dest=%b)", i, fifo_data_lo[i * flit_width_p+:flit_width_p], reqs_lo, hdr[len_width_p + (cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1)-:((len_width_p + (cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1)) >= cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] ? ((len_width_p + (cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1)) - cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32]) + 1 : (cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - (len_width_p + (cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1))) + 1)], hdr[cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1-:cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32]]);
						else
							$display("%m in  ch%2d: dequeing  packet %h", i, fifo_data_lo[i * flit_width_p+:flit_width_p]);
				end
			end
			bsg_wormhole_router_decoder_dor #(
				.dims_p(dims_p),
				.cord_dims_p(cord_dims_p),
				.reverse_order_p(reverse_order_p),
				.cord_markers_pos_p(cord_markers_pos_p)
			) dor(
				.target_cord_i(hdr[cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1-:cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32]]),
				.my_cord_i(my_cord_i),
				.req_o(decoded_dest_lo)
			);
			bsg_concentrate_static #(
				._sv2v_width_pattern_els_p(dirs_lp),
				.pattern_els_p(routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp])
			) conc_dec(
				.i(decoded_dest_lo),
				.o(decoded_dest_sparse_lo)
			);
			wire detected_header_lo;
			bsg_wormhole_router_input_control #(
				.output_dirs_p(output_dirs_sparse_lp),
				.payload_len_bits_p(((len_width_p + (cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1)) >= cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] ? ((len_width_p + (cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1)) - cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32]) + 1 : (cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - (len_width_p + (cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1))) + 1))
			) wic(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.fifo_v_i(fifo_valid_lo[i]),
				.fifo_yumi_i(any_yumi),
				.fifo_decoded_dest_i(decoded_dest_sparse_lo),
				.fifo_payload_len_i(hdr[len_width_p + (cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1)-:((len_width_p + (cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1)) >= cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] ? ((len_width_p + (cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1)) - cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32]) + 1 : (cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - (len_width_p + (cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1))) + 1)]),
				.reqs_o(reqs_lo),
				.release_o(releases[i]),
				.detected_header_o(detected_header_lo)
			);
			bsg_unconcentrate_static #(
				._sv2v_width_pattern_els_p(dirs_lp),
				.pattern_els_p(routing_matrix_p[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp])
			) unc(
				.i(reqs_lo),
				.o(reqs[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp])
			);
			always @(negedge clk_i)
				if (debug_lp)
					;
		end
	endgenerate
	bsg_transpose #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(dirs_lp),
		._sv2v_width_els_p(32),
		.els_p(dirs_lp)
	) reqs_trans(
		.i(reqs),
		.o(reqs_transpose)
	);
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < output_dirs_lp; i = i + 1) begin : out_ch
			localparam input_dirs_sparse_lp = (dirs_lp < 65 ? 1'b0 : {dirs_lp {1'sbx}}) + (((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 6) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 7) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 8) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 9) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 10) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 11) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 12) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 13) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 14) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 15) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 16) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 17) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 18) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) *
