((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 22) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 23) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 24) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 25) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 26) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 27) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 28) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 29) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 30) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 31) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 32) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 33) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 34) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 35) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 36) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 37) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 38) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 39) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 40) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 41) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 42) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 43) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 44) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 45) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 46) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 47) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 48) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 49) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 50) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 51) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 52) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 53) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 54) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 55) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 56) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 57) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 58) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 59) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 60) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 61) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 62) & 1'b1)) + ((routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp] >> 63) & 1'b1));
			wire [input_dirs_sparse_lp - 1:0] reqs_li;
			wire [input_dirs_sparse_lp - 1:0] release_li;
			wire [input_dirs_sparse_lp - 1:0] valids_li;
			wire [input_dirs_sparse_lp - 1:0] yumis_lo;
			wire [input_dirs_sparse_lp - 1:0] data_sel_lo;
			wire [(input_dirs_sparse_lp * flit_width_p) - 1:0] fifo_data_sparse_lo;
			bsg_concentrate_static #(
				._sv2v_width_pattern_els_p(dirs_lp),
				.pattern_els_p(routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp])
			) conc(
				.i(reqs_transpose[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp]),
				.o(reqs_li)
			);
			bsg_concentrate_static #(
				._sv2v_width_pattern_els_p(dirs_lp),
				.pattern_els_p(routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp])
			) conc2(
				.i(releases),
				.o(release_li)
			);
			bsg_concentrate_static #(
				._sv2v_width_pattern_els_p(dirs_lp),
				.pattern_els_p(routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp])
			) conc3(
				.i(fifo_valid_lo),
				.o(valids_li)
			);
			bsg_array_concentrate_static #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_flit_width_p),
				.width_p(flit_width_p),
				._sv2v_width_pattern_els_p(dirs_lp),
				.pattern_els_p(routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp])
			) conc4(
				.i(fifo_data_lo),
				.o(fifo_data_sparse_lo)
			);
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			bsg_wormhole_router_output_control #(.input_dirs_p(input_dirs_sparse_lp)) woc(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.reqs_i(reqs_li),
				.release_i(release_li),
				.valid_i(valids_li),
				.yumi_o(yumis_lo),
				.ready_i(link_i_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + flit_width_p]),
				.valid_o(link_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p + 1)]),
				.data_sel_o(data_sel_lo)
			);
			always @(negedge clk_i)
				if (debug_lp)
					if ((reset_i === 1'b0) && link_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p + 1)])
						if (link_i_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + flit_width_p])
							$display("%m out ch%2d: sending   packet %h", i, link_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p - 1)-:flit_width_p]);
			bsg_mux_one_hot #(
				._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_flit_width_p),
				.width_p(flit_width_p),
				.els_p(input_dirs_sparse_lp)
			) data_mux(
				.data_i(fifo_data_sparse_lo),
				.sel_one_hot_i(data_sel_lo),
				.data_o(link_o_cast[(i * (2 + flit_width_p)) + (flit_width_p - 1)-:flit_width_p])
			);
			bsg_unconcentrate_static #(
				._sv2v_width_pattern_els_p(dirs_lp),
				.pattern_els_p(routing_matrix_p[(dirs_lp + i) * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp])
			) unc1(
				.i(yumis_lo),
				.o(yumis[i * dirs_lp+:dirs_lp])
			);
		end
	endgenerate
	bsg_transpose #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(dirs_lp),
		._sv2v_width_els_p(32),
		.els_p(dirs_lp)
	) yumis_trans(
		.i(yumis),
		.o(yumis_transpose)
	);
endmodule
module bsg_wormhole_router_adapter (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	packet_i,
	v_i,
	ready_o,
	link_i,
	link_o,
	packet_o,
	v_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p - 1:0] max_payload_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_len_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_len_width_p - 1:0] len_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_cord_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_cord_width_p - 1:0] cord_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_flit_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_flit_width_p - 1:0] flit_width_p = "inv";
	localparam bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp = flit_width_p + 2;
	localparam bsg_wormhole_packet_width_lp = (cord_width_p + len_width_p) + max_payload_width_p;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [bsg_wormhole_packet_width_lp - 1:0] packet_i;
	input v_i;
	output ready_o;
	input [bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp - 1:0] link_i;
	output [bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp - 1:0] link_o;
	output [bsg_wormhole_packet_width_lp - 1:0] packet_o;
	output v_o;
	input yumi_i;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] link_cast_i;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] link_cast_o;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] link_o_stubbed_v;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] link_o_stubbed_ready;
	assign link_cast_i = link_i;
	assign link_o = link_cast_o;
	assign link_cast_o[flit_width_p - 1-:flit_width_p] = link_o_stubbed_ready[flit_width_p - 1-:flit_width_p];
	assign link_cast_o[flit_width_p + 1] = link_o_stubbed_ready[flit_width_p + 1];
	assign link_cast_o[flit_width_p] = link_o_stubbed_v[flit_width_p];
	wire [((max_payload_width_p + len_width_p) + cord_width_p) - 1:0] packet_li;
	wire [((max_payload_width_p + len_width_p) + cord_width_p) - 1:0] packet_lo;
	assign packet_li = packet_i;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	wire v_i;
	wire ready_o;
	bsg_wormhole_router_adapter_in #(
		._sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p(_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p),
		.max_payload_width_p(max_payload_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_len_width_p(_sv2v_width_len_width_p),
		.len_width_p(len_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_cord_width_p(_sv2v_width_cord_width_p),
		.cord_width_p(cord_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_flit_width_p(_sv2v_width_flit_width_p),
		.flit_width_p(flit_width_p)
	) adapter_in(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.packet_i(packet_li),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.ready_o(ready_o),
		.link_i(link_i),
		.link_o(link_o_stubbed_ready)
	);
	wire v_o;
	wire yumi_i;
	bsg_wormhole_router_adapter_out #(
		._sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p(_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p),
		.max_payload_width_p(max_payload_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_len_width_p(_sv2v_width_len_width_p),
		.len_width_p(len_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_cord_width_p(_sv2v_width_cord_width_p),
		.cord_width_p(cord_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_flit_width_p(_sv2v_width_flit_width_p),
		.flit_width_p(flit_width_p)
	) adapter_out(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.link_i(link_i),
		.link_o(link_o_stubbed_v),
		.packet_o(packet_lo),
		.v_o(v_o),
		.yumi_i(yumi_i)
	);
	assign packet_o = packet_lo;
endmodule
module bsg_wormhole_router_adapter_in (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	packet_i,
	v_i,
	ready_o,
	link_o,
	link_i
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p - 1:0] max_payload_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_len_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_len_width_p - 1:0] len_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_cord_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_cord_width_p - 1:0] cord_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_flit_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_flit_width_p - 1:0] flit_width_p = "inv";
	localparam bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp = flit_width_p + 2;
	localparam bsg_wormhole_packet_width_lp = (cord_width_p + len_width_p) + max_payload_width_p;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [bsg_wormhole_packet_width_lp - 1:0] packet_i;
	input v_i;
	output ready_o;
	output [bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp - 1:0] link_o;
	input [bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp - 1:0] link_i;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] link_cast_i;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] link_cast_o;
	wire [((max_payload_width_p + len_width_p) + cord_width_p) - 1:0] packet_cast_i;
	assign packet_cast_i = packet_i;
	localparam max_num_flits_lp = ((((max_payload_width_p + len_width_p) + cord_width_p) + flit_width_p) - 1) / flit_width_p;
	localparam protocol_len_lp = (max_num_flits_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(max_num_flits_lp));
	wire [(max_num_flits_lp * flit_width_p) - 1:0] packet_padded_li = packet_i;
	assign link_cast_i = link_i;
	assign link_o = link_cast_o;
	function automatic [protocol_len_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_5BE27;
		input reg [protocol_len_lp - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_5BE27 = inp;
	endfunction
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	wire v_i;
	wire ready_o;
	bsg_parallel_in_serial_out_dynamic #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_flit_width_p),
		.width_p(flit_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_max_els_p((((((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_flit_width_p ? ((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) : _sv2v_width_flit_width_p) >= 32 ? (((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_flit_width_p ? ((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) : _sv2v_width_flit_width_p) : 32) >= _sv2v_width_flit_width_p ? ((((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_flit_width_p ? ((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) : _sv2v_width_flit_width_p) >= 32 ? (((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_flit_width_p ? ((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) : _sv2v_width_flit_width_p) : 32) : _sv2v_width_flit_width_p)),
		.max_els_p(max_num_flits_lp)
	) piso(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.len_i(sv2v_cast_5BE27(packet_cast_i[len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)-:((len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)) >= cord_width_p ? ((len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)) - cord_width_p) + 1 : (cord_width_p - (len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1))) + 1)])),
		.data_i(packet_padded_li),
		.ready_o(ready_o),
		.v_o(link_cast_o[flit_width_p + 1]),
		.len_v_o(),
		.data_o(link_cast_o[flit_width_p - 1-:flit_width_p]),
		.yumi_i(link_cast_i[flit_width_p] & link_cast_o[flit_width_p + 1])
	);
	assign link_cast_o[flit_width_p] = 1'b0;
	always @(negedge clk_i)
		;
endmodule
module bsg_wormhole_router_adapter_out (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	link_i,
	link_o,
	packet_o,
	v_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p - 1:0] max_payload_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_len_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_len_width_p - 1:0] len_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_cord_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_cord_width_p - 1:0] cord_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_flit_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_flit_width_p - 1:0] flit_width_p = "inv";
	localparam bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp = flit_width_p + 2;
	localparam bsg_wormhole_packet_width_lp = (cord_width_p + len_width_p) + max_payload_width_p;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp - 1:0] link_i;
	output [bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp - 1:0] link_o;
	output [bsg_wormhole_packet_width_lp - 1:0] packet_o;
	output v_o;
	input yumi_i;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] link_cast_i;
	wire [(2 + flit_width_p) - 1:0] link_cast_o;
	assign link_cast_i = link_i;
	assign link_o = link_cast_o;
	wire [(len_width_p + cord_width_p) - 1:0] header_li;
	assign header_li = link_cast_i[flit_width_p - 1-:flit_width_p];
	localparam max_num_flits_lp = ((((max_payload_width_p + len_width_p) + cord_width_p) + flit_width_p) - 1) / flit_width_p;
	localparam protocol_len_lp = (max_num_flits_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(max_num_flits_lp));
	wire [(max_num_flits_lp * flit_width_p) - 1:0] packet_padded_lo;
	function automatic [protocol_len_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_5BE27;
		input reg [protocol_len_lp - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_5BE27 = inp;
	endfunction
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	wire v_o;
	wire yumi_i;
	bsg_serial_in_parallel_out_dynamic #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(_sv2v_width_flit_width_p),
		.width_p(flit_width_p),
		._sv2v_width_max_els_p((((((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_flit_width_p ? ((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) : _sv2v_width_flit_width_p) >= 32 ? (((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_flit_width_p ? ((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) : _sv2v_width_flit_width_p) : 32) >= _sv2v_width_flit_width_p ? ((((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_flit_width_p ? ((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) : _sv2v_width_flit_width_p) >= 32 ? (((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_flit_width_p ? ((_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) >= _sv2v_width_cord_width_p ? (_sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p >= _sv2v_width_len_width_p ? _sv2v_width_max_payload_width_p : _sv2v_width_len_width_p) : _sv2v_width_cord_width_p) : _sv2v_width_flit_width_p) : 32) : _sv2v_width_flit_width_p)),
		.max_els_p(max_num_flits_lp)
	) sipo(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i(link_cast_i[flit_width_p - 1-:flit_width_p]),
		.len_i(sv2v_cast_5BE27(header_li[len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)-:((len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)) >= cord_width_p ? ((len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1)) - cord_width_p) + 1 : (cord_width_p - (len_width_p + (cord_width_p - 1))) + 1)])),
		.ready_o(link_cast_o[flit_width_p]),
		.len_ready_o(),
		.v_i(link_cast_i[flit_width_p + 1]),
		.v_o(v_o),
		.data_o(packet_padded_lo),
		.yumi_i(yumi_i)
	);
	assign packet_o = packet_padded_lo[0+:bsg_wormhole_packet_width_lp];
	assign link_cast_o[flit_width_p - 1-:flit_width_p] = {flit_width_p {1'sb0}};
	assign link_cast_o[flit_width_p + 1] = 1'sb0;
	wire recv_r;
	bsg_dff_reset_en #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(1)
	) recv_reg(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.en_i(link_cast_i[flit_width_p + 1] || yumi_i),
		.data_i(link_cast_i[flit_width_p + 1]),
		.data_o(recv_r)
	);
	wire new_header_li = ~recv_r & link_cast_i[flit_width_p + 1];
endmodule
module bsg_wormhole_router_decoder_dor (
	target_cord_i,
	my_cord_i,
	req_o
);
	parameter dims_p = 2;
	parameter cord_dims_p = dims_p;
	parameter reverse_order_p = 0;
	parameter signed [(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? ((cord_dims_p + 1) * 32) - 1 : ((1 - cord_dims_p) * 32) + ((cord_dims_p * 32) - 1)):(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? 0 : cord_dims_p * 32)] cord_markers_pos_p = {32'sd5, 32'sd4, 32'sd0};
	parameter output_dirs_lp = (2 * dims_p) + 1;
	input [cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1:0] target_cord_i;
	input [cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : cord_dims_p - dims_p) * 32+:32] - 1:0] my_cord_i;
	output [output_dirs_lp - 1:0] req_o;
	genvar i;
	wire [dims_p - 1:0] eq;
	wire [dims_p - 1:0] lt;
	wire [dims_p - 1:0] gt;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < dims_p; i = i + 1) begin : rof
			localparam upper_marker_lp = cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? i + 1 : cord_dims_p - (i + 1)) * 32+:32];
			localparam lower_marker_lp = cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? i : cord_dims_p - i) * 32+:32];
			localparam local_cord_width_p = upper_marker_lp - lower_marker_lp;
			wire [local_cord_width_p - 1:0] targ_cord = target_cord_i[upper_marker_lp - 1:lower_marker_lp];
			wire [local_cord_width_p - 1:0] my_cord = my_cord_i[upper_marker_lp - 1:lower_marker_lp];
			assign eq[i] = targ_cord == my_cord;
			assign lt[i] = targ_cord < my_cord;
			assign gt[i] = ~eq[i] & ~lt[i];
		end
	endgenerate
	assign req_o[0] = &eq;
	generate
		if (reverse_order_p) begin : rev
			assign req_o[((dims_p - 1) * 2) + 1] = lt[dims_p - 1];
			assign req_o[((dims_p - 1) * 2) + 2] = gt[dims_p - 1];
			if (dims_p > 1) begin : fi1
				for (i = dims_p - 2; i >= 0; i = i - 1) begin : rof3
					assign req_o[(i * 2) + 1] = &eq[dims_p - 1:i + 1] & lt[i];
					assign req_o[(i * 2) + 2] = &eq[dims_p - 1:i + 1] & gt[i];
				end
			end
		end
		else begin : fwd
			assign req_o[1] = lt[0];
			assign req_o[2] = gt[0];
			for (i = 1; i < dims_p; i = i + 1) begin : rof2
				assign req_o[(i * 2) + 1] = &eq[i - 1:0] & lt[i];
				assign req_o[(i * 2) + 2] = &eq[i - 1:0] & gt[i];
			end
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_wormhole_router_input_control (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	fifo_v_i,
	fifo_decoded_dest_i,
	fifo_payload_len_i,
	fifo_yumi_i,
	reqs_o,
	release_o,
	detected_header_o
);
	parameter output_dirs_p = -1;
	parameter payload_len_bits_p = -1;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input fifo_v_i;
	input [output_dirs_p - 1:0] fifo_decoded_dest_i;
	input [payload_len_bits_p - 1:0] fifo_payload_len_i;
	input fifo_yumi_i;
	output [output_dirs_p - 1:0] reqs_o;
	output release_o;
	output detected_header_o;
	wire [payload_len_bits_p - 1:0] payload_ctr_r;
	wire counter_expired = !payload_ctr_r;
	wire fifo_has_hdr = counter_expired & fifo_v_i;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	bsg_counter_set_down #(
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(payload_len_bits_p),
		.set_and_down_exclusive_p(1'b1)
	) ctr(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.set_i(fifo_yumi_i & counter_expired),
		.val_i(fifo_payload_len_i),
		.down_i(fifo_yumi_i & ~counter_expired),
		.count_r_o(payload_ctr_r)
	);
	assign reqs_o = (fifo_has_hdr ? fifo_decoded_dest_i : {output_dirs_p {1'sb0}});
	wire release_o;
	assign release_o = counter_expired;
	wire detected_header_o;
	assign detected_header_o = fifo_has_hdr;
endmodule
module bsg_wormhole_router_output_control (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	reqs_i,
	release_i,
	valid_i,
	yumi_o,
	ready_i,
	valid_o,
	data_sel_o
);
	parameter input_dirs_p = -1;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [input_dirs_p - 1:0] reqs_i;
	input [input_dirs_p - 1:0] release_i;
	input [input_dirs_p - 1:0] valid_i;
	output [input_dirs_p - 1:0] yumi_o;
	input ready_i;
	output valid_o;
	output [input_dirs_p - 1:0] data_sel_o;
	wire [input_dirs_p - 1:0] scheduled_r;
	wire [input_dirs_p - 1:0] scheduled_with_release;
	wire [input_dirs_p - 1:0] scheduled_n;
	wire [input_dirs_p - 1:0] grants_lo;
	wire clk_i;
	wire reset_i;
	bsg_dff_reset #(.width_p(input_dirs_p)) scheduled_reg(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i(scheduled_n),
		.data_o(scheduled_r)
	);
	assign scheduled_with_release = scheduled_r & ~release_i;
	wire free_to_schedule = !scheduled_with_release;
	bsg_round_robin_arb #(.inputs_p(input_dirs_p)) brr(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.grants_en_i(free_to_schedule),
		.reqs_i(reqs_i),
		.grants_o(grants_lo),
		.sel_one_hot_o(),
		.v_o(),
		.tag_o(),
		.yumi_i((free_to_schedule & ready_i) & valid_o)
	);
	assign scheduled_n = grants_lo | scheduled_with_release;
	assign data_sel_o = scheduled_n;
	wire valid_o;
	assign valid_o = |(scheduled_n & valid_i);
	assign yumi_o = (ready_i ? scheduled_n & valid_i : {input_dirs_p {1'sb0}});
endmodule

	localparam [1:0] e_dst_q_sel_mem_cmd = 2'b01;
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	input [width_p - 1:0] opd_a_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] opd_b_i;
	input wire [3:0] alu_op_i;
	output reg [width_p - 1:0] res_o;
	always @(*) begin : alu
		case (alu_op_i)
			e_alu_add: res_o = opd_a_i + opd_b_i;
			e_alu_sub: res_o = opd_a_i - opd_b_i;
			e_alu_lsh: res_o = opd_a_i << opd_b_i;
			e_alu_rsh: res_o = opd_a_i >> opd_b_i;
			e_alu_and: res_o = opd_a_i & opd_b_i;
			e_alu_or: res_o = opd_a_i | opd_b_i;
			e_alu_xor: res_o = opd_a_i ^ opd_b_i;
			e_alu_neg: res_o = ~opd_a_i;
			e_alu_not: res_o = !opd_a_i;
			e_alu_nand: res_o = !(opd_a_i & opd_b_i);
			e_alu_nor: res_o = !(opd_a_i | opd_b_i);
			default: res_o = {width_p {1'sb0}};
		endcase
	end
endmodule

			pending_w_addr_bypass_o = msg_pending_w_addr_bypass_i;

			pending_w_addr_o = pending_w_addr_i;
			pending_w_addr_bypass_o = pending_w_addr_bypass_i;

			spec_r_addr_o = msg_spec_r_addr_i;
			spec_r_addr_bypass_o = msg_spec_r_addr_bypass_i;
		end

			spec_r_addr_o = spec_r_addr_i;
			spec_r_addr_bypass_o = spec_r_addr_bypass_i;
		end
	end

	localparam [3:0] e_src_q_mem_resp = 4'b0010;

	localparam [1:0] e_dst_q_sel_lce_cmd = 2'b00;
	localparam [1:0] e_dst_q_sel_mem_cmd = 2'b01;
	parameter _sv2v_width_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_width_p - 1:0] width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_cce_pc_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_cce_pc_width_p - 1:0] cce_pc_width_p = "inv";
	input [width_p - 1:0] opd_a_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] opd_b_i;
	input branch_i;
	input predicted_taken_i;
	input wire [1:0] branch_op_i;
	input [cce_pc_width_p - 1:0] execute_pc_i;
	input [cce_pc_width_p - 1:0] branch_target_i;
	output reg mispredict_o;
	output reg [cce_pc_width_p - 1:0] pc_o;
	wire equal = opd_a_i == opd_b_i;
	wire not_equal = ~equal;
	wire less = opd_a_i < opd_b_i;
	function automatic [cce_pc_width_p - 1:0] sv2v_cast_A9953;
		input reg [cce_pc_width_p - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_A9953 = inp;
	endfunction
	wire [cce_pc_width_p - 1:0] execute_pc_plus_one = sv2v_cast_A9953(execute_pc_i + 'd1);
	reg branch_res;
	always @(*) begin : branch
		case (branch_op_i)
			e_branch_eq: branch_res = equal;
			e_branch_neq: branch_res = not_equal;
			e_branch_lt: branch_res = less;
			e_branch_le: branch_res = less | equal;
			default: branch_res = 1'sb0;
		endcase
		mispredict_o = ((branch_i & branch_res) & !predicted_taken_i) | (!(branch_i & branch_res) & predicted_taken_i);
		pc_o = (branch_i & branch_res ? branch_target_i : execute_pc_plus_one);
	end
endmodule

	localparam lg_num_lce_lp = (num_lce_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(num_lce_p));

	assign row = row_i;
	assign lru_v_o = row_v_i[lce_i[0]] & ((lce_i >> 1) == row_num_i);
	wire [2:0] lru_coh_state;
	assign lru_coh_state = row[((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? (((lce_i[0] * assoc_p) + lru_way_i) * ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? tag_width_p + 3 : 1 - (tag_width_p + 2))) + ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? 2 : tag_width_p) : ((((lce_i[0] * assoc_p) + lru_way_i) * ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? tag_width_p + 3 : 1 - (tag_width_p + 2))) + ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? 2 : tag_width_p)) + 2)-:3];
	assign lru_coh_state_o = lru_coh_state;
	assign lru_tag_o = row[((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? (((lce_i[0] * assoc_p) + lru_way_i) * ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? tag_width_p + 3 : 1 - (tag_width_p + 2))) + ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? tag_width_p + 2 : (tag_width_p + 2) - (tag_width_p + 2)) : (((((lce_i[0] * assoc_p) + lru_way_i) * ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? tag_width_p + 3 : 1 - (tag_width_p + 2))) + ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? tag_width_p + 2 : (tag_width_p + 2) - (tag_width_p + 2))) + ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 3 ? tag_width_p : 4 - (tag_width_p + 2))) - 1)-:((tag_width_p + 2) >= 3 ? tag_width_p : 4 - (tag_width_p + 2))];
endmodule

	reg [((tag_width_lp + 2) >= 0 ? ((tag_sets_per_row_lp * assoc_p) * (tag_width_lp + 3)) - 1 : ((tag_sets_per_row_lp * assoc_p) * (1 - (tag_width_lp + 2))) + (tag_width_lp + 1)):((tag_width_lp + 2) >= 0 ? 0 : tag_width_lp + 2)] dir_ram_w_data;
	wire [((tag_width_lp + 2) >= 0 ? ((tag_sets_per_row_lp * assoc_p) * (tag_width_lp + 3)) - 1 : ((tag_sets_per_row_lp * assoc_p) * (1 - (tag_width_lp + 2))) + (tag_width_lp + 1)):((tag_width_lp + 2) >= 0 ? 0 : tag_width_lp + 2)] dir_row_entries;
	reg cnt_clr;
	reg cnt_inc;
	wire [counter_width_lp - 1:0] cnt;
	reg [2:0] state_r;
	reg [2:0] state_n;
	reg [lg_num_lce_lp - 1:0] lce_r;
	reg [lg_num_lce_lp - 1:0] lce_n;
	reg [lg_assoc_lp - 1:0] way_r;
	reg [lg_assoc_lp - 1:0] way_n;
	reg [lg_assoc_lp - 1:0] lru_way_r;
	reg [lg_assoc_lp - 1:0] lru_way_n;
	reg [paddr_width_p - 1:0] addr_r;
	reg [paddr_width_p - 1:0] addr_n;
	wire [tag_width_lp - 1:0] addr_r_tag = addr_r[tag_offset_lp+:tag_width_lp];
	reg [tag_sets_per_row_lp - 1:0] dir_data_o_v_r;
	reg [tag_sets_per_row_lp - 1:0] dir_data_o_v_n;
	reg [3:0] addr_dst_gpr_r;
	reg [3:0] addr_dst_gpr_n;
	reg r_lru_v_r;
	reg r_lru_v_n;

	reg [num_lce_p - 1:0] sharers_hits_n;

	reg [(num_lce_p * lg_assoc_lp) - 1:0] sharers_ways_n;

	assign sharers_hits_o = sharers_hits_r;
	assign sharers_ways_o = sharers_ways_r;

	wire [(tag_sets_per_row_lp * lg_assoc_lp) - 1:0] sharers_ways;
	wire [(tag_sets_per_row_lp * 3) - 1:0] sharers_coh_states;

	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i) begin
			state_r <= RESET;
			lce_r <= {lg_num_lce_lp {1'sb0}};
			way_r <= {lg_assoc_lp {1'sb0}};
			lru_way_r <= {lg_assoc_lp {1'sb0}};
			addr_r <= {paddr_width_p {1'sb0}};

			dir_ram_addr_r <= {lg_rows_lp {1'sb0}};
			addr_dst_gpr_r <= e_opd_r0;
			r_lru_v_r <= 1'sb0;
			sharers_v_r <= 1'sb0;
			sharers_hits_r <= {num_lce_p {1'sb0}};
			sharers_ways_r <= {num_lce_p * lg_assoc_lp {1'sb0}};
			sharers_coh_states_r <= e_COH_I;
		end
		else begin
			state_r <= state_n;
			lce_r <= lce_n;
			way_r <= way_n;
			lru_way_r <= lru_way_n;

			dir_ram_addr_r <= dir_ram_addr_n;

			sharers_ways_r <= sharers_ways_n;
			sharers_coh_states_r <= sharers_coh_states_n;
		end
	function automatic [counter_width_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_531B4;
		input reg [counter_width_lp - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_531B4 = inp;
	endfunction
	function automatic [lg_rows_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_FCBAD;
		input reg [lg_rows_lp - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_FCBAD = inp;
	endfunction
	function automatic [tag_offset_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_CD5CD;
		input reg [tag_offset_lp - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_CD5CD = inp;
	endfunction
	localparam [2:0] INIT = 1;
	localparam [2:0] READY = 2;
	localparam [2:0] READ_ENTRY = 4;
	localparam [2:0] READ_FULL = 3;

		cnt_clr = 1'b0;
		cnt_inc = 1'b0;

					sharers_v_n = 1'sb0;

					if (cmd_i == e_rdw_op) begin
						state_n = READ_FULL;
						dir_ram_addr = set_id;

					end

					end
				end

					end

					end
					else if (cmd_i == e_wds_op) begin
						dir_ram_w_mask[((tag_width_lp + 2) >= 0 ? 					end
				end
			READ_FULL: begin
				busy_o = 1'b1;
				begin : sv2v_autoblock_16
					reg signed [31:0] j;
					for (j = 0; j < tag_sets_per_row_lp; j = j + 1)
						begin
							sharers_hits_n[(cnt << 1) + j] = sharers_hits[j];
							sharers_ways_n[((cnt << 1) + j) * lg_assoc_lp+:lg_assoc_lp] = sharers_ways[j * lg_assoc_lp+:lg_assoc_lp];
							sharers_coh_states_n[((cnt << 1) + j) * 3+:3] = sharers_coh_states[j * 3+:3];
						end
				end
				if (cnt < sv2v_cast_531B4(rows_per_set_lp - 1)) begin
					dir_ram_v = 1'b1;
					dir_ram_addr = dir_ram_addr_r;
					dir_ram_addr_n = dir_ram_addr_r + sv2v_cast_FCBAD(tag_sets_p);

				end

					cnt_clr = 1'b1;

				end

			end

(_sv2v_width_paddr_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_paddr_width_p : 32) : 32) : _sv2v_width_assoc_p) >= 32 ? (((_sv2v_width_paddr_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_paddr_width_p : 32) >= 32 ? (_sv2v_width_paddr_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_paddr_width_p : 32) : 32) >= _sv2v_width_assoc_p ? ((_sv2v_width_paddr_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_paddr_width_p : 32) >= 32 ? (_sv2v_width_paddr_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_paddr_width_p : 32) : 32) : _sv2v_width_assoc_p) : 32)),
		.row_width_p(row_width_lp),
		._sv2v_width_assoc_p(_sv2v_width_assoc_p),
		.assoc_p(assoc_p),
		._sv2v_width_num_lce_p(_sv2v_width_num_lce_p),
		.num_lce_p(num_lce_p),
		._sv2v_width_tag_width_p((_sv2v_width_paddr_width_p >= 32 ? _sv2v_width_paddr_width_p : 32)),
		.tag_width_p(tag_width_lp)
	) lru_extract(
		.row_i(dir_row_entries),
		.row_v_i(dir_data_o_v_r),
		.row_num_i(cnt[0+:lg_rows_per_set_lp]),
		.lce_i(lce_r),
		.lru_way_i(lru_way_r),
		.lru_v_o(lru_v_lo),
		.lru_coh_state_o(lru_coh_state_o),
		.lru_tag_o(lru_tag_lo)
	);
	wire [lg_sets_lp - 1:0] lru_set = addr_r[lg_block_size_in_bytes_lp+:lg_sets_lp];
	function automatic [lg_block_size_in_bytes_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_F7416;
		input reg [lg_block_size_in_bytes_lp - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_F7416 = inp;
	endfunction
	assign lru_addr_o = {lru_tag_lo, lru_set, sv2v_cast_F7416(0)};
	assign lru_v_o = lru_v_lo & r_lru_v_r;
endmodule

	parameter _sv2v_width_tag_sets_per_row_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_tag_sets_per_row_p - 1:0] tag_sets_per_row_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_row_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_row_width_p - 1:0] row_width_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_assoc_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_assoc_p - 1:0] assoc_p = "inv";
	parameter _sv2v_width_tag_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_tag_width_p - 1:0] tag_width_p = "inv";
	localparam lg_assoc_lp = (assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(assoc_p));
	input [row_width_p - 1:0] row_i;
	input [tag_sets_per_row_p - 1:0] row_v_i;
	input [tag_width_p - 1:0] tag_i;
	output wire [tag_sets_per_row_p - 1:0] sharers_hits_o;
	output wire [(tag_sets_per_row_p * lg_assoc_lp) - 1:0] sharers_ways_o;
	output wire [(tag_sets_per_row_p * 3) - 1:0] sharers_coh_states_o;
	wire [((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? ((tag_sets_per_row_p * assoc_p) * (tag_width_p + 3)) - 1 : ((tag_sets_per_row_p * assoc_p) * (1 - (tag_width_p + 2))) + (tag_width_p + 1)):((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? 0 : tag_width_p + 2)] row;
	assign row = row_i;
	wire [(tag_sets_per_row_p * assoc_p) - 1:0] row_hits;
	generate
		genvar i;
		for (i = 0; i < tag_sets_per_row_p; i = i + 1) begin : row_hits_tag_set
			genvar j;
			for (j = 0; j < assoc_p; j = j + 1) begin : row_hits_way
				assign row_hits[(i * assoc_p) + j] = (row_v_i[i] & (row[((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? (((i * assoc_p) + j) * ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? tag_width_p + 3 : 1 - (tag_width_p + 2))) + ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? tag_width_p + 2 : (tag_width_p + 2) - (tag_width_p + 2)) : (((((i * assoc_p) + j) * ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? tag_width_p + 3 : 1 - (tag_width_p + 2))) + ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? tag_width_p + 2 : (tag_width_p + 2) - (tag_width_p + 2))) + ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 3 ? tag_width_p : 4 - (tag_width_p + 2))) - 1)-:((tag_width_p + 2) >= 3 ? tag_width_p : 4 - (tag_width_p + 2))] == tag_i)) & |row[((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? (((i * assoc_p) + j) * ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? tag_width_p + 3 : 1 - (tag_width_p + 2))) + ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? 2 : tag_width_p) : ((((i * assoc_p) + j) * ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? tag_width_p + 3 : 1 - (tag_width_p + 2))) + ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? 2 : tag_width_p)) + 2)-:3];
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < tag_sets_per_row_p; i = i + 1) begin : sharers_ways_gen
			bsg_encode_one_hot #(.width_p(assoc_p)) row_hits_to_way_ids_and_v(
				.i(row_hits[i * assoc_p+:assoc_p]),
				.addr_o(sharers_ways_o[i * lg_assoc_lp+:lg_assoc_lp]),
				.v_o(sharers_hits_o[i])
			);
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < tag_sets_per_row_p; i = i + 1) begin : sharers_states_gen
			assign sharers_coh_states_o[i * 3+:3] = (sharers_hits_o[i] ? row[((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? (((i * assoc_p) + sharers_ways_o[i * lg_assoc_lp+:lg_assoc_lp]) * ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? tag_width_p + 3 : 1 - (tag_width_p + 2))) + ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? 2 : tag_width_p) : ((((i * assoc_p) + sharers_ways_o[i * lg_assoc_lp+:lg_assoc_lp]) * ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? tag_width_p + 3 : 1 - (tag_width_p + 2))) + ((tag_width_p + 2) >= 0 ? 2 : tag_width_p)) + 2)-:3] : e_COH_I);
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule

				.w_v_i(acache_w_v),
				.busy_o(sv2v_tmp_acache_dir_segment_busy_o),
				.sharers_v_o(sv2v_tmp_acache_dir_segment_sharers_v_o),
				.sharers_hits_o(sv2v_tmp_acache_dir_segment_sharers_hits_o),
				.sharers_ways_o(sv2v_tmp_acache_dir_segment_sharers_ways_o),
				.sharers_coh_states_o(sv2v_tmp_acache_dir_segment_sharers_coh_states_o),
				.lru_v_o(sv2v_tmp_acache_dir_segment_lru_v_o),
				.lru_coh_state_o(sv2v_tmp_acache_dir_segment_lru_coh_state_o),
				.lru_addr_o(sv2v_tmp_acache_dir_segment_lru_addr_o),
				.addr_v_o(sv2v_tmp_acache_dir_segment_addr_v_o),
				.addr_o(sv2v_tmp_acache_dir_segment_addr_o),
				.addr_dst_gpr_o(sv2v_tmp_acache_dir_segment_addr_dst_gpr_o)
			);
		end
		else always @(*) begin
			acache_busy = 1'sb0;
			acache_sharers_v = 1'b1;
			acache_sharers_hits = {num_cacc_lp {1'sb0}};
			acache_sharers_ways = {num_cacc_lp * lg_acache_assoc_lp {1'sb0}};
			acache_sharers_coh_states = e_COH_I;
			acache_lru_v = 1'sb0;
			acache_lru_coh_state_lo = e_COH_I;
			acache_lru_addr_lo = {paddr_width_p {1'sb0}};
			acache_addr_v = 1'sb0;
			acache_addr_lo = {paddr_width_p {1'sb0}};
			acache_addr_dst_gpr_lo = e_opd_r0;
		end
	endgenerate
	assign busy_o = (icache_busy | dcache_busy) | acache_busy;
	assign sharers_v_o = (icache_sharers_v & dcache_sharers_v) & acache_sharers_v;
	always @(*) begin
		sharers_hits_o = {num_lce_p {1'sb0}};
		sharers_ways_o = {num_lce_p * lce_assoc_width_p {1'sb0}};
		sharers_coh_states_o = {(2 * num_core_p) + num_cacc_p {e_COH_I}};
		begin : sv2v_autoblock_17
			reg signed [31:0] i;
			for (i = 0; i < num_core_p; i = i + 1)
				begin
					sharers_hits_o[2 * i] = icache_sharers_hits[i];
					sharers_ways_o[(2 * i) * lce_assoc_width_p+:lg_icache_assoc_lp] = icache_sharers_ways[i * lg_icache_assoc_lp+:lg_icache_assoc_lp];
					sharers_coh_states_o[(2 * i) * 3+:3] = icache_sharers_coh_states[i * 3+:3];
					sharers_hits_o[(2 * i) + 1] = dcache_sharers_hits[i];
					sharers_ways_o[((2 * i) + 1) * lce_assoc_width_p+:lg_dcache_assoc_lp] = dcache_sharers_ways[i * lg_dcache_assoc_lp+:lg_dcache_assoc_lp];
					sharers_coh_states_o[((2 * i) + 1) * 3+:3] = dcache_sharers_coh_states[i * 3+:3];
				end
		end
		begin : sv2v_autoblock_18
			reg signed [31:0] i;
			for (i = 0; i < num_cacc_p; i = i + 1)
				begin
					sharers_hits_o[i + (2 * num_core_p)] = acache_sharers_hits[i];
					sharers_ways_o[(i + (2 * num_core_p)) * lce_assoc_width_p+:lg_acache_assoc_lp] = acache_sharers_ways[i * lg_acache_assoc_lp+:lg_acache_assoc_lp];
					sharers_coh_states_o[(i + (2 * num_core_p)) * 3+:3] = acache_sharers_coh_states[i * 3+:3];
				end
		end
	end
	assign lru_v_o = (icache_lru_v | dcache_lru_v) | acache_lru_v;
	assign lru_addr_o = (icache_lru_v ? icache_lru_addr_lo : (dcache_lru_v ? dcache_lru_addr_lo : (acache_lru_v ? acache_lru_addr_lo : {paddr_width_p {1'sb0}})));
	assign lru_coh_state_o = (icache_lru_v ? icache_lru_coh_state_lo : (dcache_lru_v ? dcache_lru_coh_state_lo : (acache_lru_v ? acache_lru_coh_state_lo : e_COH_I)));
	assign addr_v_o = (icache_addr_v | dcache_addr_v) | acache_addr_v;
	assign addr_o = (icache_addr_v ? icache_addr_lo : (dcache_addr_v ? dcache_addr_lo : (acache_addr_v ? acache_addr_lo : {paddr_width_p {1'sb0}})));
	assign addr_dst_gpr_o = (icache_addr_v ? icache_addr_dst_gpr_lo : (dcache_addr_v ? dcache_addr_dst_gpr_lo : (acache_addr_v ? acache_addr_dst_gpr_lo : e_opd_r0)));
	always @(negedge clk_i)
		if (~reset_i)
			;
endmodule

	localparam cce_instr_width_p = 34;

	localparam coh_noc_len_width_p = proc_param_lp[383-:32];
	localparam coh_noc_y_cord_width_p = ((((all_cfgs_gp[(bp_params_p * 1792) + 1727-:32] + all_cfgs_gp[(bp_params_p * 1792) + 1759-:32]) + all_cfgs_gp[(bp_params_p * 1792) + 1695-:32]) + 1) == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(((all_cfgs_gp[(bp_params_p * 1792) + 1727-:32] + all_cfgs_gp[(bp_params_p * 1792) + 1759-:32]) + all_cfgs_gp[(bp_params_p * 1792) + 1695-:32]) + 1));

	localparam mem_noc_y_cord_width_p = ((((all_cfgs_gp[(bp_params_p * 1792) + 1727-:32] + all_cfgs_gp[(bp_params_p * 1792) + 1759-:32]) + all_cfgs_gp[(bp_params_p * 1792) + 1695-:32]) + 1) == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(((all_cfgs_gp[(bp_params_p * 1792) + 1727-:32] + all_cfgs_gp[(bp_params_p * 1792) + 1759-:32]) + all_cfgs_gp[(bp_params_p * 1792) + 1695-:32]) + 1));

	localparam lg_num_lce_lp = (num_lce_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(num_lce_p));
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input gad_v_i;
	input sharers_v_i;
	input [num_lce_p - 1:0] sharers_hits_i;
	input [(num_lce_p * lce_assoc_width_p) - 1:0] sharers_ways_i;
	input wire [(num_lce_p * 3) - 1:0] sharers_coh_states_i;
	input [lce_id_width_p - 1:0] req_lce_i;
	input req_type_flag_i;
	input wire [2:0] lru_coh_state_i;
	output wire [lce_assoc_width_p - 1:0] req_addr_way_o;
	output wire [lce_id_width_p - 1:0] owner_lce_o;
	output wire [lce_assoc_width_p - 1:0] owner_way_o;
	output wire replacement_flag_o;
	output wire upgrade_flag_o;
	output wire cached_shared_flag_o;
	output wire cached_exclusive_flag_o;
	output wire cached_modified_flag_o;
	output wire cached_owned_flag_o;
	output wire cached_forward_flag_o;
	wire unused = &{clk_i, reset_i, sharers_v_i};
	wire [lg_num_lce_lp - 1:0] req_lce_id = req_lce_i[0+:lg_num_lce_lp];
	wire [num_lce_p - 1:0] lce_id_one_hot;
	bsg_decode #(
		._sv2v_width_num_out_p(32),
		.num_out_p(num_lce_p)
	) lce_id_to_one_hot(
		.i(req_lce_id),
		.o(lce_id_one_hot)
	);
	wire [num_lce_p - 1:0] lce_cached;
	assign lce_cached = sharers_hits_i;
	wire [num_lce_p - 1:0] lce_cached_S;
	wire [num_lce_p - 1:0] lce_cached_E;
	wire [num_lce_p - 1:0] lce_cached_M;
	wire [num_lce_p - 1:0] lce_cached_O;
	wire [num_lce_p - 1:0] lce_cached_F;
	generate
		genvar i;
		for (i = 0; i < num_lce_p; i = i + 1) begin : lce_cached_flags
			assign lce_cached_S[i] = lce_cached[i] & (sharers_coh_states_i[i * 3+:3] == e_COH_S);
			assign lce_cached_E[i] = lce_cached[i] & (sharers_coh_states_i[i * 3+:3] == e_COH_E);
			assign lce_cached_M[i] = lce_cached[i] & (sharers_coh_states_i[i * 3+:3] == e_COH_M);
			assign lce_cached_O[i] = lce_cached[i] & (sharers_coh_states_i[i * 3+:3] == e_COH_O);
			assign lce_cached_F[i] = lce_cached[i] & (sharers_coh_states_i[i * 3+:3] == e_COH_F);
		end
	endgenerate
	assign cached_shared_flag_o = |(lce_cached_S & ~lce_id_one_hot);
	assign cached_exclusive_flag_o = |(lce_cached_E & ~lce_id_one_hot);
	assign cached_modified_flag_o = |(lce_cached_M & ~lce_id_one_hot);
	assign cached_owned_flag_o = |(lce_cached_O & ~lce_id_one_hot);
	assign cached_forward_flag_o = |(lce_cached_F & ~lce_id_one_hot);
	wire req_lce_cached;
	assign req_lce_cached = lce_cached[req_lce_id];
	wire req_lce_ro;
	assign req_lce_ro = req_lce_cached & (((sharers_coh_states_i[req_lce_id * 3+:3] == e_COH_S) | (sharers_coh_states_i[req_lce_id * 3+:3] == e_COH_F)) | (sharers_coh_states_i[req_lce_id * 3+:3] == e_COH_O));
	assign req_addr_way_o = (req_lce_cached ? sharers_ways_i[req_lce_id * lce_assoc_width_p+:lce_assoc_width_p] : {lce_assoc_width_p {1'sb0}});
	assign upgrade_flag_o = req_type_flag_i & req_lce_ro;
	assign replacement_flag_o = ~upgrade_flag_o & (((lru_coh_state_i == e_COH_E) | (lru_coh_state_i == e_COH_M)) | (lru_coh_state_i == e_COH_O));
	wire [num_lce_p - 1:0] owner_lce_one_hot;
	assign owner_lce_one_hot = (gad_v_i ? ((lce_cached_E | lce_cached_M) | lce_cached_O) | lce_cached_F : {num_lce_p {1'sb0}});
	wire [lg_num_lce_lp - 1:0] owner_lce_lo;
	wire owner_lce_v;
	bsg_encode_one_hot #(
		.width_p(num_lce_p),
		.lo_to_hi_p(1)
	) lce_cached_to_lce_id(
		.i(owner_lce_one_hot),
		.addr_o(owner_lce_lo),
		.v_o(owner_lce_v)
	);
	assign owner_lce_o = (gad_v_i & owner_lce_v ? {1'sb0, owner_lce_lo} : {lce_id_width_p {1'sb0}});
	assign owner_way_o = (gad_v_i & owner_lce_v ? {1'sb0, sharers_ways_i[owner_lce_lo * lce_assoc_width_p+:lce_assoc_width_p]} : {lce_assoc_width_p {1'sb0}});
endmodule
module bp_cce_inst_decode (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	inst_i,
	pc_i,
	inst_v_i,
	stall_i,
	mispredict_i,
	decoded_inst_o,
	pc_o
);
	localparam bp_log_none_gp = 0;
	localparam bp_log_stdout_gp = 1;
	localparam bp_log_file_gp = 2;
	localparam [0:0] e_fe_fetch = 0;
	localparam [0:0] e_fe_exception = 1;
	localparam [2:0] e_op_state_reset = 0;
	localparam [2:0] e_op_pc_redirection = 1;
	localparam [2:0] e_op_attaboy = 2;

	localparam [3:0] e_cce_mem_pre = 4'b0100;
	parameter _sv2v_width_cce_pc_width_p = 24;
	parameter [_sv2v_width_cce_pc_width_p - 1:0] cce_pc_width_p = "inv";
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input wire [33:0] inst_i;
	input [cce_pc_width_p - 1:0] pc_i;
	input inst_v_i;
	input stall_i;
	input mispredict_i;
	output reg [213:0] decoded_inst_o;
	output reg [cce_pc_width_p - 1:0] pc_o;
	reg [33:0] inst_r;
	reg [33:0] inst_n;
	reg [cce_pc_width_p - 1:0] ex_pc_r;
	reg [cce_pc_width_p - 1:0] ex_pc_n;
	reg inst_v_r;
	reg inst_v_n;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i) begin
			inst_r <= {34 {1'sb0}};
			ex_pc_r <= {cce_pc_width_p {1'sb0}};
			inst_v_r <= 1'sb0;
		end
		else begin
			inst_r <= inst_n;
			ex_pc_r <= ex_pc_n;
			inst_v_r <= inst_v_n;
		end
	reg [2:0] op;
	reg [3:0] minor_op_u;
	reg [24:0] op_type_u;
	function automatic [2:0] sv2v_cast_3;
		input reg [2:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_3 = inp;
	endfunction
	always @(*) begin
		inst_n = (stall_i ? inst_r : inst_i);
		ex_pc_n = (stall_i ? ex_pc_r : pc_i);
		inst_v_n = (stall_i ? inst_v_r : (mispredict_i ? 1'b0 : inst_v_i));
		pc_o = ex_pc_r;
		decoded_inst_o = {214 {1'sb0}};
		decoded_inst_o[213] = inst_v_r;
		op = inst_r[2-:3];
		minor_op_u = inst_r[6-:4];
		op_type_u = inst_r[31-:25];
		if (inst_v_r) begin
			decoded_inst_o[212] = inst_r[32];
			decoded_inst_o[211] = inst_r[33];
			decoded_inst_o[210-:3] = op;
			decoded_inst_o[207-:4] = minor_op_u;
			case (op)
				e_op_alu: begin
					decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
					decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
					decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
					decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
					decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
					case (minor_op_u[3-:4])
						e_add_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_add;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
						end
						e_sub_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_sub;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
						end
						e_lsh_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_lsh;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
						end
						e_rsh_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_rsh;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
						end
						e_and_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_and;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
						end
						e_or_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_or;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
						end
						e_xor_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_xor;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
						end
						e_neg_op: decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_neg;
						e_addi_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_add;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_imm;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:16] = op_type_u[24-:16];
						end
						e_subi_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_sub;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_imm;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:16] = op_type_u[24-:16];
						end
						e_lshi_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_lsh;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_imm;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:16] = op_type_u[24-:16];
						end
						e_rshi_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_rsh;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_imm;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:16] = op_type_u[24-:16];
						end
						e_not_op: decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_not;
						default:
							;
					endcase
				end
				e_op_branch: begin
					decoded_inst_o[93-:9] = op_type_u[24-:9];
					case (minor_op_u[3-:4])
						e_beq_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[95-:2] = e_branch_eq;
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
						end
						e_bne_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[95-:2] = e_branch_neq;
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
						end
						e_blt_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[95-:2] = e_branch_lt;
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
						end
						e_ble_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[95-:2] = e_branch_le;
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
						end
						e_bs_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[95-:2] = e_branch_eq;
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_special;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
						end
						e_bss_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[95-:2] = e_branch_eq;
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_special;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_special;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
						end
						e_beqi_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[95-:2] = e_branch_eq;
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_imm;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:8] = op_type_u[11-:8];
						end
						e_bsi_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[95-:2] = e_branch_eq;
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_special;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_imm;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:8] = op_type_u[11-:8];
						end
						default:
							;
					endcase
				end
				e_op_reg_data: begin
					case (minor_op_u[3-:4])
						e_mov_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
						end
						e_movsg_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_special;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
						end
						e_movgs_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_special;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
						end
						e_movfg_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_flag;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
						end
						e_movgf_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_flag;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[4 + op_type_u[7-:4]] = 1'b1;
						end
						e_movpg_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_param;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
						end
						e_movgp_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_param;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
						end
						e_movi_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_imm;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:16] = op_type_u[24-:16];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
						end
						e_movis_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_imm;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:16] = op_type_u[24-:16];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_special;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
						end
						e_movip_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_imm;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:16] = op_type_u[24-:16];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_param;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
						end
						e_clm_op: decoded_inst_o[29] = 1'b1;
						default:
							;
					endcase
					if ((minor_op_u[3-:4] == e_movgs_op) | (minor_op_u[3-:4] == e_movis_op)) begin
						if (op_type_u[7-:4] == e_opd_req_lce)
							decoded_inst_o[28] = 1'b1;
						if (op_type_u[7-:4] == e_opd_req_addr)
							decoded_inst_o[27] = 1'b1;
						if (op_type_u[7-:4] == e_opd_req_way)
							decoded_inst_o[26] = 1'b1;
						if (op_type_u[7-:4] == e_opd_lru_addr)
							decoded_inst_o[25] = 1'b1;
						if (op_type_u[7-:4] == e_opd_lru_way)
							decoded_inst_o[24] = 1'b1;
						if (op_type_u[7-:4] == e_opd_owner_lce)
							decoded_inst_o[23] = 1'b1;
						if (op_type_u[7-:4] == e_opd_owner_way)
							decoded_inst_o[22] = 1'b1;
						if (op_type_u[7-:4] == e_opd_next_coh_state)
							decoded_inst_o[21] = 1'b1;
						if (op_type_u[7-:4] == e_opd_lru_coh_state)
							decoded_inst_o[20] = 1'b1;
						if (op_type_u[7-:4] == e_opd_flags)
							decoded_inst_o[19-:16] = {16 {1'sb1}};
						if (op_type_u[7-:4] == e_opd_msg_size)
							decoded_inst_o[3] = 1'b1;
					end
					if ((minor_op_u[3-:4] == e_movgp_op) | (minor_op_u[3-:4] == e_movip_op)) begin
						if (op_type_u[7-:4] == e_opd_auto_fwd_msg)
							decoded_inst_o[1] = 1'b1;
						if (op_type_u[7-:4] == e_opd_coh_state_default)
							decoded_inst_o[2] = 1'b1;
					end
				end
				e_op_flag:
					case (minor_op_u[3-:4])
						e_sf_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_imm;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:16] = op_type_u[24-:16];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_flag;
							decoded_inst_o[4 + op_type_u[7-:4]] = 1'b1;
						end
						e_andf_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_and;
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_flag;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_flag;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
						end
						e_orf_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_or;
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_flag;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_flag;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
						end
						e_nandf_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_nand;
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_flag;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_flag;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
						end
						e_norf_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_nor;
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_flag;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_flag;
							decoded_inst_o[190-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
						end
						e_notf_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[99-:4] = e_alu_not;
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_flag;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
						end
						e_bf_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[95-:2] = e_branch_eq;
							decoded_inst_o[93-:9] = op_type_u[24-:9];
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_special;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = e_opd_flags_and_mask;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_imm;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:16] = op_type_u[15-:16];
						end
						e_bfz_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[95-:2] = e_branch_eq;
							decoded_inst_o[93-:9] = op_type_u[24-:9];
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_special;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = e_opd_flags_and_mask;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_zero;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:16] = op_type_u[15-:16];
						end
						e_bfnz_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[95-:2] = e_branch_neq;
							decoded_inst_o[93-:9] = op_type_u[24-:9];
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_special;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = e_opd_flags_and_mask;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_zero;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:16] = op_type_u[15-:16];
						end
						e_bfnot_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[95-:2] = e_branch_neq;
							decoded_inst_o[93-:9] = op_type_u[24-:9];
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_special;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = e_opd_flags_and_mask;
							decoded_inst_o[186-:3] = e_src_sel_imm;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:16] = op_type_u[15-:16];
						end
						default:
							;
					endcase
				e_op_dir:
					case (minor_op_u[3-:4])
						e_rdp_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[80] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[4 + e_opd_pf] = 1'b1;
						end
						e_rdw_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[84] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[179-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[171-:4] = op_type_u[19-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[23-:4];
						end
						e_rde_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[84] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[179-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[175-:4] = op_type_u[15-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[23-:4];
						end
						e_wdp_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[79] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[78] = op_type_u[8];
							decoded_inst_o[100] = op_type_u[8];
						end
						e_clp_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[79] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[77] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
						end
						e_clr_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[83] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[179-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
						end
						e_wde_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[83] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[179-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[175-:4] = op_type_u[15-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[167-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[100+:3] = op_type_u[18-:3];
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[22-:4];
						end
						e_wds_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[83] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = op_type_u[3-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[179-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[175-:4] = op_type_u[15-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[167-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[100+:3] = op_type_u[18-:3];
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[22-:4];
						end
						e_gad_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[82] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[26] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[23] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[22] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[4 + e_opd_rf] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[4 + e_opd_uf] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[4 + e_opd_csf] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[4 + e_opd_cef] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[4 + e_opd_cmf] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[4 + e_opd_cof] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[4 + e_opd_cff] = 1'b1;
						end
						default:
							;
					endcase
				e_op_queue:
					case (minor_op_u[3-:4])
						e_wfq_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[81] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[100+:4] = op_type_u[9+:4];
						end
						e_pushq_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[61] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[56-:2] = op_type_u[1-:2];
							case (op_type_u[1-:2])
								e_dst_q_sel_lce_cmd: begin
									decoded_inst_o[48] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[47-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
								end
								e_dst_q_sel_mem_cmd: begin
									decoded_inst_o[43] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[42-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
								end
								default:
									;
							endcase
							decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[179-:4] = op_type_u[15-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = op_type_u[19-:4];
							if (op_type_u[3]) begin
								decoded_inst_o[75] = 1'b1;
								decoded_inst_o[74] = 1'b1;
								decoded_inst_o[73] = 1'b1;
								decoded_inst_o[72] = 1'b1;
								decoded_inst_o[71] = 1'b1;
								decoded_inst_o[70] = 1'b1;
							end
							decoded_inst_o[60] = op_type_u[2];
							decoded_inst_o[59-:3] = sv2v_cast_3(op_type_u[23-:4]);
							decoded_inst_o[175-:4] = op_type_u[23-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[167-:4] = e_mux_sel_coh_next_coh_state;
							if (op_type_u[24]) begin
								decoded_inst_o[79] = 1'b1;
								decoded_inst_o[78] = 1'b1;
							end
						end
						e_popq_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[63] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[54-:2] = op_type_u[1-:2];
							case (op_type_u[1-:2])
								e_src_q_sel_lce_req: begin
									decoded_inst_o[52] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = e_mux_sel_addr_lce_req;
								end
								e_src_q_sel_lce_resp: begin
									decoded_inst_o[51] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = e_mux_sel_addr_lce_resp;
								end
								e_src_q_sel_mem_resp: begin
									decoded_inst_o[50] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = e_mux_sel_addr_mem_resp;
								end
								e_src_q_sel_pending: begin
									decoded_inst_o[49] = 1'b0;
									decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = e_mux_sel_addr_pending;
								end
								default:
									;
							endcase
							if (op_type_u[24]) begin
								decoded_inst_o[79] = 1'b1;
								if (decoded_inst_o[52] | decoded_inst_o[49])
									decoded_inst_o[78] = 1'b1;
								else
									decoded_inst_o[78] = 1'b0;
							end
						end
						e_poph_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[64] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[54-:2] = op_type_u[1-:2];
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_queue;
							case (op_type_u[1-:2])
								e_src_q_sel_lce_resp: begin
									decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = e_opd_lce_resp_type;
									decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
									decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
									decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[19-:16] = e_flag_nwbf;
								end
								e_src_q_sel_mem_resp: begin
									decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = e_opd_mem_resp_type;
									decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
									decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
									decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[19-:16] = e_flag_sf;
								end
								e_src_q_sel_lce_req: begin
									decoded_inst_o[28] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[27] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[24] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[3] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[19-:16] = (e_flag_rqf | e_flag_nerf) | e_flag_ucf;
								end
								default: decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = e_opd_lce_resp_type;
							endcase
						end
						e_popd_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[62] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[54-:2] = op_type_u[1-:2];
							decoded_inst_o[193-:3] = e_src_sel_queue;
							decoded_inst_o[199-:2] = e_dst_sel_gpr;
							decoded_inst_o[203-:4] = op_type_u[7-:4];
							decoded_inst_o[30 + op_type_u[4+:3]] = 1'b1;
							case (op_type_u[1-:2])
								e_src_q_sel_lce_resp: decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = e_opd_lce_resp_data;
								e_src_q_sel_mem_resp: decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = e_opd_mem_resp_data;
								e_src_q_sel_lce_req: decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = e_opd_lce_req_data;
								default: decoded_inst_o[197-:4] = e_opd_lce_resp_data;
							endcase
						end
						e_specq_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = op_type_u[11-:4];
							case (op_type_u[3-:4])
								e_spec_set: begin
									decoded_inst_o[75] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[74] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[73] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[72] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[71] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[70] = 1'b1;
								end
								e_spec_unset: begin
									decoded_inst_o[75] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[74] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[73] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[72] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[71] = 1'b1;
								end
								e_spec_squash: begin
									decoded_inst_o[75] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[74] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[73] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[72] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[71] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[69] = 1'b1;
								end
								e_spec_fwd_mod: begin
									decoded_inst_o[75] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[74] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[73] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[72] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[71] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[68] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[67-:3] = op_type_u[14-:3];
								end
								e_spec_rd_spec: begin
									decoded_inst_o[76] = 1'b1;
									decoded_inst_o[4 + e_opd_sf] = 1'b1;
								end
								default: decoded_inst_o[75] = 1'b0;
							endcase
						end
						e_inv_op: begin
							decoded_inst_o[38] = 1'b1;
							decoded_inst_o[183-:4] = e_mux_sel_addr_mshr_req;
						end
						default:
							;
					endcase
				default:
					;
			endcase
		end
	end
endmodule
module bp_cce_inst_predecode (
	inst_i,
	pc_i,
	predicted_next_pc_o
);
	localparam bp_log_none_gp = 0;
	localparam bp_log_stdout_gp = 1;
	localparam bp_log_file_gp = 2;
	localparam [0:0] e_fe_fetch = 0;
	localparam [0:0] e_fe_exception = 1;
	localparam [2:0] e_op_state_reset = 0;
	localparam [2:0] e_op_pc_redirection = 1;
	localparam [2:0] e_op_attaboy = 2;
	localparam [2:0] e_op_icache_fence = 3;
	localparam [2:0] e_op_itlb_fill_response = 4;
	localparam [2:0] e_op_itlb_fence = 5;
	localparam [1:0] e_not_a_branch = 0;
	localparam [1:0] e_incorrect_pred_taken = 1;
	localparam [1:0] e_incorrect_pred_ntaken = 2;
	localparam [1:0] e_itlb_miss = 0;
	localparam [1:0] e_instr_access_fault = 1;
	localparam [1:0] e_instr_page_fault = 2;
	localparam [2:0] e_subop_eret = 0;
	localparam [2:0] e_subop_interrupt = 1;
	localparam [2:0] e_subop_branch_mispredict = 2;
	localparam [2:0] e_subop_trap = 3;
	localparam [2:0] e_subop_context_switch = 4;
	localparam [2:0] e_subop_translation_switch = 5;
	localparam [2:0] e_mem_msg_size_1 = 3'b000;
	localparam [2:0] e_mem_msg_size_2 = 3'b001;
	localparam [2:0] e_mem_msg_size_4 = 3'b010;
	localparam [2:0] e_mem_msg_size_8 = 3'b011;
	localparam [2:0] e_mem_msg_size_16 = 3'b100;
	localparam [2:0] e_mem_msg_size_32 = 3'b101;
	localparam [2:0] e_mem_msg_size_64 = 3'b110;
	localparam [2:0] e_mem_msg_size_128 = 3'b111;
	localparam [2:0] e_lce_req_type_rd = 3'b000;
	localparam [2:0] e_lce_req_type_wr = 3'b001;
	localparam [2:0] e_lce_req_type_uc_rd = 3'b010;
	localparam [2:0] e_lce_req_type_uc_wr = 3'b011;
	localparam [0:0] e_lce_req_excl = 1'b0;
	localparam [0:0] e_lce_req_non_excl = 1'b1;
	localparam [2:0] e_COH_I = 3'b000;
	localparam [2:0] e_COH_S = 3'b001;

		.data_o(inst_o)
	);

	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i) begin

		end

				ram_v_li = 1'b1;
				inst_v_n = 1'b1;
			end
			FETCH: begin
				ram_v_li = 1'b1;
				fetch_pc_n = (stall_i ? fetch_pc_r : (mispredict_i ? branch_resolution_pc_i : predicted_fetch_pc_i));
				inst_v_n = 1'b1;
			end
			default: fetch_state_n = RESET;
		endcase
	end
endmodule

	input lce_req_v_i;
	input lce_resp_v_i;
	input mem_resp_v_i;
	input pending_v_i;
	input lce_cmd_ready_i;
	input mem_cmd_ready_i;
	input msg_busy_i;
	input msg_pending_w_busy_i;
	input msg_lce_cmd_busy_i;
	input msg_lce_resp_busy_i;
	input msg_mem_resp_busy_i;
	input msg_spec_r_busy_i;
	input msg_dir_w_busy_i;
	input dir_busy_i;
	output reg stall_o;
	wire lce_req_v = lce_req_v_i;
	wire lce_resp_v = lce_resp_v_i;
	wire mem_resp_v = mem_resp_v_i;
	wire pending_v = pending_v_i;
	wire lce_cmd_ready = lce_cmd_ready_i;
	wire mem_cmd_ready = mem_cmd_ready_i;
	wire [3:0] wfq_v_vec = {lce_req_v, lce_resp_v, mem_resp_v, pending_v};
	wire [3:0] wfq_mask = decoded_inst_i[100+:4];
	always @(*) begin
		stall_o = 1'b0;
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[52] & ~lce_req_v);
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[51] & ~lce_resp_v);
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[50] & ~mem_resp_v);
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[49] & ~pending_v);
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[64] & (~lce_req_v & (decoded_inst_i[54-:2] == e_src_q_sel_lce_req)));
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[64] & (~lce_resp_v & (decoded_inst_i[54-:2] == e_src_q_sel_lce_resp)));
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[64] & (~mem_resp_v & (decoded_inst_i[54-:2] == e_src_q_sel_mem_resp)));
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[62] & (~lce_req_v & (decoded_inst_i[54-:2] == e_src_q_sel_lce_req)));
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[62] & (~lce_resp_v & (decoded_inst_i[54-:2] == e_src_q_sel_lce_resp)));
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[62] & (~mem_resp_v & (decoded_inst_i[54-:2] == e_src_q_sel_mem_resp)));
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[48] & ~lce_cmd_ready);
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[43] & ~mem_cmd_ready);
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[81] & ~(|(wfq_mask & wfq_v_vec)));
		stall_o = stall_o | dir_busy_i;
		stall_o = stall_o | msg_busy_i;
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[79] & msg_pending_w_busy_i);
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[48] & msg_lce_cmd_busy_i);
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[51] & msg_lce_resp_busy_i);
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[50] & msg_mem_resp_busy_i);
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[76] & msg_spec_r_busy_i);
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[83] & msg_dir_w_busy_i);
		stall_o = stall_o | (decoded_inst_i[84] & msg_dir_w_busy_i);
	end
endmodule

						lce_cmd[(((((((((3 + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + lce_id_width_p) + 3) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + paddr_width_p) + cce_id_width_p) + 7) + lce_id_width_p) - 1) - ((((((((((3 + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + lce_id_width_p) + 3) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + paddr_width_p) + cce_id_width_p) + 7) + lce_id_width_p) - 1) - (lce_id_width_p + 3))-:((lce_id_width_p + 3) >= lce_id_width_p ? ((lce_id_width_p + 3) - lce_id_width_p) + 1 : (lce_id_width_p - (lce_id_width_p + 3)) + 1)] = e_lce_cmd_inv;
						lce_cmd[(((((((((3 + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + lce_id_width_p) + 3) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + paddr_width_p) + cce_id_width_p) + 7) + lce_id_width_p) - 1) - ((((((((((3 + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + lce_id_width_p) + 3) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + paddr_width_p) + cce_id_width_p) + 7) + lce_id_width_p) - 1) - (lce_id_width_p - 1))-:lce_id_width_p] = pe_lce_id;
						lce_cmd[(((((((((3 + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + lce_id_width_p) + 3) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + paddr_width_p) + cce_id_width_p) + 7) + lce_id_width_p) - 1) - ((((((((((3 + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + lce_id_width_p) + 3) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + paddr_width_p) + cce_id_width_p) + 7) + lce_id_width_p) - 1) - ((lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p)) + (paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (lce_id_width_p + 6)))))-:(((lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p)) + (paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (lce_id_width_p + 6)))) >= (paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (7 + lce_id_width_p))) ? (((lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p)) + (paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (lce_id_width_p + 6)))) - (paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (7 + lce_id_width_p)))) + 1 : ((paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (7 + lce_id_width_p))) - ((lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p)) + (paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (lce_id_width_p + 6))))) + 1)] = sharers_ways_r[pe_lce_id * lce_assoc_width_p+:lce_assoc_width_p];
						lce_cmd[(((((((((3 + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + lce_id_width_p) + 3) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + paddr_width_p) + cce_id_width_p) + 7) + lce_id_width_p) - 1) - ((((((((((3 + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + lce_id_width_p) + 3) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + paddr_width_p) + cce_id_width_p) + 7) + lce_id_width_p) - 1) - (cce_id_width_p + (lce_id_width_p + 6)))-:((cce_id_width_p + (lce_id_width_p + 6)) >= (7 + lce_id_width_p) ? ((cce_id_width_p + (lce_id_width_p + 6)) - (7 + lce_id_width_p)) + 1 : ((7 + lce_id_width_p) - (cce_id_width_p + (lce_id_width_p + 6))) + 1)] = cfg_bus_cast[cce_id_width_p + (3 + (cce_pc_width_p + (cce_instr_width_p + (2 + (reg_addr_width_p + (dword_width_p + (2 + (csr_addr_width_p + (dword_width_p + 3)))))))))-:((cce_id_width_p + (3 + (all_cfgs_gp[(bp_params_p * 1792) + 767-:32] + 186))) >= (3 + (all_cfgs_gp[(bp_params_p * 1792) + 767-:32] + 187)) ? ((cce_id_width_p + (3 + (cce_pc_width_p + (cce_instr_width_p + (2 + (reg_addr_width_p + (dword_width_p + (2 + (csr_addr_width_p + (dword_width_p + 3)))))))))) - (3 + (cce_pc_width_p + (cce_instr_width_p + (2 + (reg_addr_width_p + (dword_width_p + (2 + (csr_addr_width_p + (dword_width_p + 4)))))))))) + 1 : ((3 + (cce_pc_width_p + (cce_instr_width_p + (2 + (reg_addr_width_p + (dword_width_p + (2 + (csr_addr_width_p + (dword_width_p + 4))))))))) - (cce_id_width_p + (3 + (cce_pc_width_p + (cce_instr_width_p + (2 + (reg_addr_width_p + (dword_width_p + (2 + (csr_addr_width_p + (dword_width_p + 3))))))))))) + 1)];
						lce_cmd[(((((((((3 + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + lce_id_width_p) + 3) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + paddr_width_p) + cce_id_width_p) + 7) + lce_id_width_p) - 1) - ((((((((((3 + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + lce_id_width_p) + 3) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + paddr_width_p) + cce_id_width_p) + 7) + lce_id_width_p) - 1) - (paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (lce_id_width_p + 6))))-:((paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (lce_id_width_p + 6))) >= (cce_id_width_p + (7 + lce_id_width_p)) ? ((paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (lce_id_width_p + 6))) - (cce_id_width_p + (7 + lce_id_width_p))) + 1 : ((cce_id_width_p + (7 + lce_id_width_p)) - (paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (lce_id_width_p + 6)))) + 1)] = addr_r;
						dir_w_v_o = lce_cmd_ready_i;
						dir_w_cmd_o = e_wds_op;
						dir_addr_o = addr_r;
						dir_addr_bypass_o = 1'sb0;
						dir_lce_o = {1'sb0, pe_lce_id};
						dir_way_o = sharers_ways_r[pe_lce_id * lce_assoc_width_p+:lce_assoc_width_p];
						dir_coh_state_o = e_COH_I;
						cnt_inc = lce_cmd_ready_i;
						pe_sharers_n = (lce_cmd_ready_i ? pe_sharers_r & ~pe_lce_id_one_hot : pe_sharers_r);
						state_n = (lce_cmd_ready_i & (pe_sharers_n == {num_lce_p {1'sb0}}) ? e_normal_inv_resp : e_normal_inv_cmd);
					end
					if (lce_resp_v_i & (lce_resp[((((paddr_width_p + lce_id_width_p) + 6) + cce_id_width_p) - 1) - (((((paddr_width_p + lce_id_width_p) + 6) + cce_id_width_p) - 1) - (cce_id_width_p + 2))-:((cce_id_width_p + 2) >= cce_id_width_p ? ((cce_id_width_p + 2) - cce_id_width_p) + 1 : (cce_id_width_p - (cce_id_width_p + 2)) + 1)] == e_lce_cce_inv_ack)) begin
						lce_resp_yumi_o = lce_resp_v_i;
						cnt_dec = 1'b1;
					end
				end
				e_normal_inv_resp: begin
					busy_o = 1'b1;
					if (cnt == {$clog2(num_lce_p + 2) {1'sb0}})
						state_n = e_normal_ready;
					else if (lce_resp_v_i & (lce_resp[((((paddr_width_p + lce_id_width_p) + 6) + cce_id_width_p) - 1) - (((((paddr_width_p + lce_id_width_p) + 6) + cce_id_width_p) - 1) - (cce_id_width_p + 2))-:((cce_id_width_p + 2) >= cce_id_width_p ? ((cce_id_width_p + 2) - cce_id_width_p) + 1 : (cce_id_width_p - (cce_id_width_p + 2)) + 1)] == e_lce_cce_inv_ack)) begin
						lce_resp_yumi_o = lce_resp_v_i;
						if (cnt == 'd1) begin
							state_n = e_normal_ready;
							cnt_rst = 1'b1;
						end
						else
							cnt_dec = 1'b1;
					end
				end
				default: state_n = e_normal_reset;
			endcase
		end
	end
	always @(negedge clk_i)
		if (~reset_i)
			if ((state_r == e_normal_inv_cmd) & ~pe_v)
				$error("bp_cce_msg bad sharers list for invalidate command");
endmodule

			if (((addr_offset_p >= ((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1) ? (addr_offset_p - ((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1)) + 1 : (((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1) - addr_offset_p) + 1) % 1) > 0)
				_sv2v_strm_1E0CB_out[0+:(addr_offset_p >= ((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1) ? 			_sv2v_strm_r_addr_rev = ((addr_offset_p >= ((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1) ? 		end
	endfunction
	wire [lg_cce_way_groups_lp - 1:0] r_addr_rev = _sv2v_strm_r_addr_rev(r_addr_i[addr_offset_p+:lg_cce_way_groups_lp]);
	function automatic [lg_cce_way_groups_lp - 1:0] _sv2v_strm_w_addr_rev;
		input reg [(addr_offset_p >= ((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1) ? (addr_offset_p - ((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1)) + 1 : (((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1) - addr_offset_p) + 1) - 1:0] inp;
		reg [(addr_offset_p >= ((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1) ? (addr_offset_p - ((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1)) + 1 : (((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1) - addr_offset_p) + 1) - 1:0] _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_inp;
		reg [(addr_offset_p >= ((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1) ? (addr_offset_p - ((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1)) + 1 : (((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1) - addr_offset_p) + 1) - 1:0] _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_out;
		integer _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_idx;
		begin
			_sv2v_strm_1E0CB_inp = inp;
			for (_sv2v_strm_1E0CB_idx = 0; _sv2v_strm_1E0CB_idx <= ((addr_offset_p >= ((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1) ? 				_sv2v_strm_1E0CB_out[((addr_offset_p >= ((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1) ? 			if (((addr_offset_p >= ((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1) ? (addr_offset_p - ((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1)) + 1 : (((addr_offset_p + lg_cce_way_groups_lp) - 1) - addr_offset_p) + 1) % 1) > 0)
