	endfunction
	wire [lg_cce_way_groups_lp - 1:0] w_addr_rev = _sv2v_strm_w_addr_rev(w_addr_i[addr_offset_p+:lg_cce_way_groups_lp]);
	wire [lg_num_way_groups_lp - 1:0] r_wg;
	wire [lg_num_way_groups_lp - 1:0] w_wg;
	bsg_hash_bank #(
		._sv2v_width_banks_p(_sv2v_width_num_cce_p),
		.banks_p(num_cce_p),
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(lg_cce_way_groups_lp)
	) r_addr_hash(
		.i(r_addr_rev),
		.bank_o(),
		.index_o(r_wg_lo)
	);
	bsg_hash_bank #(
		._sv2v_width_banks_p(_sv2v_width_num_cce_p),
		.banks_p(num_cce_p),
		._sv2v_width_width_p(32),
		.width_p(lg_cce_way_groups_lp)
	) w_addr_hash(
		.i(w_addr_rev),
		.bank_o(),
		.index_o(w_wg_lo)
	);
	assign r_wg = (r_addr_bypass_hash_i ? r_addr_i[0+:lg_num_way_groups_lp] : r_wg_lo[0+:lg_num_way_groups_lp]);
	assign w_wg = (w_addr_bypass_hash_i ? w_addr_i[0+:lg_num_way_groups_lp] : w_wg_lo[0+:lg_num_way_groups_lp]);
	reg [(num_way_groups_p * width_p) - 1:0] pending_bits_r;
	reg [(num_way_groups_p * width_p) - 1:0] pending_bits_n;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i)
			pending_bits_r <= {num_way_groups_p * width_p {1'sb0}};
		else
			pending_bits_r <= pending_bits_n;
	always @(*) begin
		pending_bits_n = pending_bits_r;
		if (w_v_i)
			if (clear_i)
				pending_bits_n[w_wg * width_p+:width_p] = {width_p {1'sb0}};
			else if (pending_i)
				pending_bits_n[w_wg * width_p+:width_p] = pending_bits_r[w_wg * width_p+:width_p] + 'd1;
			else
				pending_bits_n[w_wg * width_p+:width_p] = pending_bits_r[w_wg * width_p+:width_p] - 'd1;
	end
	assign pending_o = ((r_v_i & w_v_i) & (w_wg == r_wg) ? ~(pending_bits_n[r_wg * width_p+:width_p] == 0) : ~(pending_bits_r[r_wg * width_p+:width_p] == 0));
endmodule

					reg signed [31:0] i;
					for (i = 0; i < 16; i = i + 1)
						if (~stall_i & decoded_inst_i[4 + i])
							mshr_r[3 + i] <= mshr_n[3 + i];
				end
				if (~stall_i & decoded_inst_i[3])
					mshr_r[2-:3] <= mshr_n[2-:3];
			end
		end
endmodule

((3 + ((lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p)) + (paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (lce_id_width_p + 6))))) - ((lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p)) + (paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (7 + lce_id_width_p))))) + 1 : (((lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p)) + (paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (7 + lce_id_width_p)))) - (3 + ((lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p)) + (paddr_width_p + (cce_id_width_p + (lce_id_width_p + 6)))))) + 1)] = mshr_r[21-:3];
					state_n = (lce_cmd_ready_i ? RESOLVE_SPECULATION : UPGRADE_STW_CMD);
				end
			RESOLVE_SPECULATION: begin
				if (transfer_flag | mshr_r[3 + e_opd_uf]) begin
					spec_w_v = 1'b1;
					spec_v_li = 1'b1;
					spec_bits_li[5] = 1'b0;
					squash_v_li = 1'b1;
					spec_bits_li[4] = 1'b1;
				end
				else if (mshr_r[3 + e_opd_rqf]) begin
					spec_w_v = 1'b1;
					spec_v_li = 1'b1;
					fwd_mod_v_li = 1'b1;
					state_v_li = 1'b1;
					spec_bits_li[5] = 1'b0;
					spec_bits_li[2-:3] = e_COH_M;
					spec_bits_li[3] = 1'b1;
				end
				else if (mshr_r[3 + e_opd_csf] | mshr_r[3 + e_opd_nerf]) begin
					spec_w_v = 1'b1;
					spec_v_li = 1'b1;
					fwd_mod_v_li = 1'b1;
					state_v_li = 1'b1;
					spec_bits_li[5] = 1'b0;
					spec_bits_li[2-:3] = e_COH_S;
					spec_bits_li[3] = 1'b1;
				end
				else begin
					spec_w_v = 1'b1;
					spec_v_li = 1'b1;
					spec_bits_li[5] = 1'b0;
				end
				state_n = READY;
			end
			ERROR: begin
				$display("oh no - error!");
				$finish(0);
			end
			default:
				;
		endcase
	end
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i) begin
			state_r <= RESET;
			mshr_r <= {(((((((((lce_id_width_p + paddr_width_p) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + paddr_width_p) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + 3) + lce_id_width_p) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + 21) >= 0 ? (((((((lce_id_width_p + paddr_width_p) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + paddr_width_p) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + 3) + lce_id_width_p) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + 22 : 1 - ((((((((lce_id_width_p + paddr_width_p) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + paddr_width_p) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + 3) + lce_id_width_p) + (lce_assoc_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(lce_assoc_p))) + 21)) {1'sb0}};
			sharers_ways_r <= {num_lce_p * lg_lce_assoc_lp {1'sb0}};
			sharers_hits_r <= {num_lce_p {1'sb0}};
			pe_sharers_r <= {num_lce_p {1'sb0}};
		end
		else begin
			state_r <= state_n;
			mshr_r <= mshr_n;
			sharers_ways_r <= sharers_ways_n;
			sharers_hits_r <= sharers_hits_n;
			pe_sharers_r <= pe_sharers_n;
		end
endmodule

				.lce_resp_yumi_o(lce_resp_yumi_o),
				.lce_cmd_o(lce_cmd_o),
				.lce_cmd_v_o(lce_cmd_v_o),
				.lce_cmd_ready_i(lce_cmd_ready_i),
				.mem_resp_i(mem_resp_i),
				.mem_resp_v_i(mem_resp_v_i),
				.mem_resp_yumi_o(mem_resp_yumi_o),
				.mem_cmd_o(mem_cmd_o),
				.mem_cmd_v_o(mem_cmd_v_o),
				.mem_cmd_ready_i(mem_cmd_ready_i)
			);
		end
		else begin : fsm
			wire clk_i;
			wire reset_i;
			wire lce_req_v_i;
			wire lce_resp_v_i;
			wire lce_cmd_ready_i;
			wire mem_resp_v_i;
			wire mem_cmd_ready_i;
			bp_cce_fsm #(.bp_params_p(bp_params_p)) cce(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.cfg_bus_i(cfg_bus_i),
				.cfg_cce_ucode_data_o(cfg_cce_ucode_data_o),
				.lce_req_i(lce_req_i),
				.lce_req_v_i(lce_req_v_i),
				.lce_req_yumi_o(lce_req_yumi_o),
				.lce_resp_i(lce_resp_i),
				.lce_resp_v_i(lce_resp_v_i),
				.lce_resp_yumi_o(lce_resp_yumi_o),
				.lce_cmd_o(lce_cmd_o),
				.lce_cmd_v_o(lce_cmd_v_o),
				.lce_cmd_ready_i(lce_cmd_ready_i),
				.mem_resp_i(mem_resp_i),
				.mem_resp_v_i(mem_resp_v_i),
				.mem_resp_yumi_o(mem_resp_yumi_o),
				.mem_cmd_o(mem_cmd_o),
				.mem_cmd_v_o(mem_cmd_v_o),
				.mem_cmd_ready_i(mem_cmd_ready_i)
			);
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule

	wire [coh_noc_y_cord_width_p - 1:0] ycord_li = cord_i[coh_noc_x_cord_width_p+:coh_noc_y_cord_width_p];
	localparam max_cc_cce_lp = num_core_p;
	localparam max_mc_cce_lp = max_cc_cce_lp + num_l2e_p;

	localparam max_sac_cce_lp = max_cac_cce_lp + num_sacc_p;
	localparam max_ic_cce_lp = max_sac_cce_lp + num_io_p;
	localparam max_cc_lce_lp = num_core_p * 2;
	localparam max_cac_lce_lp = max_cc_lce_lp + num_cacc_p;
	localparam max_mc_lce_lp = max_cac_lce_lp + num_l2e_p;
	localparam max_sac_lce_lp = max_mc_lce_lp + num_sacc_p;
	localparam max_ic_lce_lp = max_sac_lce_lp + num_io_p;
	wire cord_in_cc_li = (((xcord_li >= sac_x_dim_p) & (xcord_li < (sac_x_dim_p + cc_x_dim_p))) & (ycord_li >= ic_y_dim_p)) & (ycord_li < (ic_y_dim_p + cc_y_dim_p));
	wire cord_in_mc_li = ycord_li >= (ic_y_dim_p + cc_y_dim_p);
	wire cord_in_cac_li = xcord_li >= (cc_x_dim_p + sac_x_dim_p);
	wire cord_in_sac_li = xcord_li < sac_x_dim_p;
	wire cord_in_io_li = ycord_li < ic_y_dim_p;
	assign core_id_o = cce_id_o;
	always @(*)
		if (cord_in_cc_li) begin
			cce_id_o = (xcord_li - sac_x_dim_p) + (cc_x_dim_p * (ycord_li - ic_y_dim_p));
			lce_id0_o = (cce_id_o << 1'b1) + 1'b0;
			lce_id1_o = (cce_id_o << 1'b1) + 1'b1;
		end
		else if (cord_in_mc_li) begin
			cce_id_o = max_cc_cce_lp + (xcord_li - sac_x_dim_p);
			lce_id0_o = max_cac_lce_lp + (xcord_li - sac_x_dim_p);
			lce_id1_o = {lce_id_width_p {1'sbx}};
		end
		else if (cord_in_cac_li) begin
			cce_id_o = max_mc_cce_lp + (ycord_li - ic_y_dim_p);
			lce_id0_o = max_cc_lce_lp + (ycord_li - ic_y_dim_p);
			lce_id1_o = {lce_id_width_p {1'sbx}};
		end
		else if (cord_in_sac_li) begin
			cce_id_o = max_cac_cce_lp + (ycord_li - ic_y_dim_p);
			lce_id0_o = max_mc_lce_lp + (ycord_li - ic_y_dim_p);
			lce_id1_o = {lce_id_width_p {1'sbx}};
		end
		else begin
			cce_id_o = max_sac_cce_lp + (xcord_li - sac_x_dim_p);
			lce_id0_o = max_sac_lce_lp + (xcord_li - sac_x_dim_p);
			lce_id1_o = {lce_id_width_p {1'sbx}};
		end
endmodule
